msgid "%1% is too tall, and collisions will be caused."
msgstr "%1% 过高，将导致碰撞。"

msgid " is too close to others, there may be collisions when printing."
msgstr " 过于靠近其他模型，打印时可能会发生碰撞。"

msgid " is too close to exclusion area, there may be collisions when printing."
msgstr " 过于靠近禁排区，打印时可能会发生碰撞。"

msgid "Prime Tower"
msgstr "净化塔"

msgid " is too close to others, and collisions may be caused.\n"
msgstr " 过于靠近其他模型，可能会导致碰撞。\n"

msgid " is too close to exclusion area, and collisions will be caused.\n"
msgstr " 过于靠近禁排区，将导致碰撞。\n"

msgid ""
"Cannot print multiple filaments which have large difference of temperature "
"together. Otherwise, the extruder and nozzle may be blocked or damaged "
"during printing."
msgstr ""
"无法同时打印温差较大的多种耗材。否则，打印过程中挤出机和喷嘴可能会堵塞或损坏。"

msgid "No extrusions under current settings."
msgstr "当前设置下无挤出。"

msgid ""
"Smooth mode of timelapse is not supported when \"by object\" sequence is "
"enabled."
msgstr ""
"启用\"按对象\"打印顺序时，不支持平滑模式的延时摄影。"

msgid ""
"Please select \"By object\" print sequence to print multiple objects in "
"spiral vase mode."
msgstr ""
"请选择\"按对象\"打印顺序以在螺旋花瓶模式下打印多个对象。"

msgid ""
"The spiral vase mode does not work when an object contains more than one "
"materials."
msgstr ""
"当对象包含多种材料时，螺旋花瓶模式不适用。"

#, boost-format

msgid ""
"While the object %1% itself fits the build volume, it exceeds the maximum "
"build volume height because of material shrinkage compensation."
msgstr ""
"虽然对象 %1% 本身在构建体积范围内，但由于材料收缩补偿，其超出了最大构建体积高度。"

#, boost-format

msgid "The object %1% exceeds the maximum build volume height."
msgstr "对象 %1% 超出了最大构建体积高度。"

#, boost-format

msgid ""
"While the object %1% itself fits the build volume, its last layer exceeds "
"the maximum build volume height."
msgstr ""
"虽然对象 %1% 本身在构建体积范围内，但其最后一层超出了最大构建体积高度。"

msgid ""
"You might want to reduce the size of your model or change current print "
"settings and retry."
msgstr ""
"您可以尝试缩小模型尺寸或更改当前打印设置后重试。"

msgid "Variable layer height is not supported with Organic supports."
msgstr "有机支撑不支持可变层高。"

msgid ""
"Different nozzle diameters and different filament diameters may not work "
"well when the prime tower is enabled. It's very experimental, so please "
"proceed with caution."
msgstr ""
"启用净化塔时，不同的喷嘴直径和不同的耗材直径可能无法很好地协同工作。这属于实验性功能，请谨慎使用。"

msgid ""
"The Wipe Tower is currently only supported with the relative extruder "
"addressing (use_relative_e_distances=1)."
msgstr ""
"擦拭塔目前仅支持相对挤出机寻址模式（use_relative_e_distances=1）。"

msgid ""
"Ooze prevention is only supported with the wipe tower when "
"'single_extruder_multi_material' is off."
msgstr ""
"防流涎功能仅在关闭'single_extruder_multi_material'时与擦拭塔配合使用。"

msgid ""
"The prime tower is currently only supported for the Marlin, RepRap/Sprinter, "
"RepRapFirmware and Repetier G-code flavors."
msgstr ""
"净化塔目前仅支持 Marlin、RepRap/Sprinter、RepRapFirmware 和 Repetier G代码风格。"

msgid "The prime tower is not supported in \"By object\" print."
msgstr "净化塔不支持\"按对象\"打印。"

msgid ""
"The prime tower is not supported when adaptive layer height is on. It "
"requires that all objects have the same layer height."
msgstr ""
"启用自适应层高时不支持净化塔。它要求所有对象具有相同的层高。"

msgid ""
"The prime tower requires \"support gap\" to be multiple of layer height."
msgstr ""
"净化塔要求\"支撑间隙\"是层高的倍数。"

msgid "The prime tower requires that all objects have the same layer heights."
msgstr "净化塔要求所有对象具有相同的层高。"

msgid ""
"The prime tower requires that all objects are printed over the same number "
"of raft layers."
msgstr ""
"净化塔要求所有对象打印在相同数量的筏层上。"

msgid ""
"The prime tower is only supported for multiple objects if they are printed "
"with the same support_top_z_distance."
msgstr ""
"净化塔仅当多个对象使用相同的支撑顶部Z距离打印时才支持。"

msgid ""
"The prime tower requires that all objects are sliced with the same layer "
"heights."
msgstr ""
"净化塔要求所有对象使用相同的层高进行切片。"

msgid ""
"The prime tower is only supported if all objects have the same variable "
"layer height."
msgstr ""
"净化塔仅在所有对象具有相同的可变层高时才支持。"

msgid ""
"One or more object were assigned an extruder that the printer does not have."
msgstr ""
"一个或多个对象被分配了打印机不存在的挤出机。"

msgid "Too small line width"
msgstr "线宽过小"

msgid "Too large line width"
msgstr "线宽过大"

msgid ""
"Printing with multiple extruders of differing nozzle diameters. If support "
"is to be printed with the current filament (support_filament == 0 or "
"support_interface_filament == 0), all nozzles have to be of the same "
"diameter."
msgstr ""
"使用不同喷嘴直径的多个挤出机进行打印。如果使用当前耗材打印支撑（support_filament == 0 或 support_interface_filament == 0），则所有喷嘴必须具有相同的直径。"

msgid ""
"The prime tower requires that support has the same layer height with object."
msgstr ""
"净化塔要求支撑与对象具有相同的层高。"

msgid ""
"Organic support tree tip diameter must not be smaller than support material "
"extrusion width."
msgstr ""
"有机支撑树尖直径不得小于支撑材料挤出宽度。"

msgid ""
"Organic support branch diameter must not be smaller than 2x support material "
"extrusion width."
msgstr ""
"有机支撑分支直径不得小于支撑材料挤出宽度的2倍。"

msgid ""
"Organic support branch diameter must not be smaller than support tree tip "
"diameter."
msgstr ""
"有机支撑分支直径不得小于支撑树尖直径。"

msgid ""
"Support enforcers are used but support is not enabled. Please enable support."
msgstr ""
"已使用支撑强制区域但未启用支撑。请启用支撑。"

msgid "Layer height cannot exceed nozzle diameter."
msgstr "层高不能超过喷嘴直径。"

msgid ""
"Relative extruder addressing requires resetting the extruder position at "
"each layer to prevent loss of floating point accuracy. Add \"G92 E0\" to "
"layer_gcode."
msgstr ""
"相对挤出机寻址需要在每一层重置挤出机位置，以防止浮点精度丢失。请在 "
"layer_gcode 中添加 \"G92 E0\"。"

msgid ""
"\"G92 E0\" was found in before_layer_gcode, which is incompatible with "
"absolute extruder addressing."
msgstr ""
"在 before_layer_gcode 中发现了 \"G92 E0\"，这与绝对挤出机寻址不兼容。"

msgid ""
"\"G92 E0\" was found in layer_gcode, which is incompatible with absolute "
"extruder addressing."
msgstr ""
"在 layer_gcode 中发现了 \"G92 E0\"，这与绝对挤出机寻址不兼容。"

#, c-format, boost-format

msgid "Plate %d: %s does not support filament %s"
msgstr "打印平台 %d：%s 不支持耗材 %s"

msgid ""
"Setting the jerk speed too low could lead to artifacts on curved surfaces"
msgstr "将急动速度设置得过低可能会导致曲面出现伪影"

msgid ""
"The jerk setting exceeds the printer's maximum jerk (machine_max_jerk_x/"
"machine_max_jerk_y).\n"
"Orca will automatically cap the jerk speed to ensure it doesn't surpass the "
"printer's capabilities.\n"
"You can adjust the maximum jerk setting in your printer's configuration to "
"get higher speeds."
msgstr ""
"急动设置超过了打印机最大急动值（machine_max_jerk_x/"
"machine_max_jerk_y）。\n"
"Orca 将自动限制急动速度，以确保不超过打印机的性能。\n"
"您可以在打印机配置中调整最大急动值以获得更高的速度。"

msgid ""
"Junction deviation setting exceeds the printer's maximum value "
"(machine_max_junction_deviation).\n"
"Orca will automatically cap the junction deviation to ensure it doesn't "
"surpass the printer's capabilities.\n"
"You can adjust the machine_max_junction_deviation value in your printer's "
"configuration to get higher limits."
msgstr ""
"节点偏差设置超过了打印机最大值（machine_max_junction_deviation）。\n"
"Orca 将自动限制节点偏差，以确保不超过打印机的性能。\n"
"您可以在打印机配置中调整 machine_max_junction_deviation 值以获得更高的限制。"

msgid ""
"The acceleration setting exceeds the printer's maximum acceleration "
"(machine_max_acceleration_extruding).\n"
"Orca will automatically cap the acceleration speed to ensure it doesn't "
"surpass the printer's capabilities.\n"
"You can adjust the machine_max_acceleration_extruding value in your "
"printer's configuration to get higher speeds."
msgstr ""
"加速度设置超过了打印机最大加速度（machine_max_acceleration_extruding）。\n"
"Orca 将自动限制加速度，以确保不超过打印机的性能。\n"
"您可以在打印机配置中调整 machine_max_acceleration_extruding 值以获得更高的速度。"

msgid ""
"The travel acceleration setting exceeds the printer's maximum travel "
"acceleration (machine_max_acceleration_travel).\n"
"Orca will automatically cap the travel acceleration speed to ensure it "
"doesn't surpass the printer's capabilities.\n"
"You can adjust the machine_max_acceleration_travel value in your printer's "
"configuration to get higher speeds."
msgstr ""
"移动加速度设置超过了打印机最大移动加速度（machine_max_acceleration_travel）。\n"
"Orca 将自动限制移动加速度，以确保不超过打印机的性能。\n"
"您可以在打印机配置中调整 machine_max_acceleration_travel 值以获得更高的速度。"

msgid ""
"The precise wall option will be ignored for outer-inner or inner-outer-inner "
"wall sequences."
msgstr "对于外-内或内-外-内的壁顺序，精准壁选项将被忽略。"

msgid ""
"Filament shrinkage will not be used because filament shrinkage for the used "
"filaments differs significantly."
msgstr "将不使用耗材收缩补偿，因为所用耗材的收缩率差异显著。"

msgid "Generating skirt & brim"
msgstr "正在生成裙边和底边"

msgid "Exporting G-code"
msgstr "正在导出 G代码"

msgid "Generating G-code"
msgstr "正在生成 G代码"

msgid "Failed processing of the filename_format template."
msgstr "处理 filename_format 模板失败。"

msgid "Printer technology"
msgstr "打印机技术"

msgid "Printable area"
msgstr "可打印区域"

msgid "Bed exclude area"
msgstr "热床排除区域"

msgid ""
"Unprintable area in XY plane. For example, X1 Series printers use the front "
"left corner to cut filament during filament change. The area is expressed as "
"polygon by points in following format: \"XxY, XxY, ...\""
msgstr ""
"XY 平面中不可打印的区域。例如，X1 系列打印机在更换耗材时使用左前角切断耗材。"
"该区域通过以下格式的点表示为多边形：\"XxY, XxY, ...\""

msgid "Bed custom texture"
msgstr "热床自定义纹理"

msgid "Bed custom model"
msgstr "热床自定义模型"

msgid "Elephant foot compensation"
msgstr "大象脚补偿"

msgid ""
"Shrinks the initial layer on build plate to compensate for elephant foot "
"effect."
msgstr "收缩打印平台上的初始层以补偿大象脚效应。"

msgid "Elephant foot compensation layers"
msgstr "大象脚补偿层数"

msgid ""
"The number of layers on which the elephant foot compensation will be active. "
"The first layer will be shrunk by the elephant foot compensation value, then "
"the next layers will be linearly shrunk less, up to the layer indicated by "
"this value."
msgstr ""
"大象脚补偿将生效的层数。第一层将按大象脚补偿值收缩，"
"然后后续层将线性递减收缩量，直至此值指定的层。"

msgid "layers"
msgstr "层"

msgid ""
"Slicing height for each layer. Smaller layer height means more accurate and "
"more printing time."
msgstr "每层的切片高度。较小的层高意味着更高的精度和更长的打印时间。"

msgid "Printable height"
msgstr "可打印高度"

msgid "Maximum printable height which is limited by mechanism of printer."
msgstr "受打印机机械结构限制的最大可打印高度。"

msgid "Preferred orientation"
msgstr "首选朝向"

msgid "Automatically orient stls on the Z axis upon initial import."
msgstr "在初始导入时自动将 STL 文件沿 Z 轴定向。"

msgid "Printer preset names"
msgstr "打印机预设名称"

msgid "Use 3rd-party print host"
msgstr "使用第三方打印主机"

msgid "Allow controlling BambuLab's printer through 3rd party print hosts."
msgstr "允许通过第三方打印主机控制 BambuLab 的打印机。"

msgid "Hostname, IP or URL"
msgstr "主机名、IP 或 URL"

msgid ""
"Snapmaker Orca can upload G-code files to a printer host. This field should "
"contain the hostname, IP address or URL of the printer host instance. Print "
"host behind HAProxy with basic auth enabled can be accessed by putting the "
"user name and password into the URL in the following format: https://"
"username:password@your-octopi-address/"
msgstr ""
"Snapmaker Orca 可以将 G代码文件上传到打印主机。此字段应包含打印主机实例的主机名、"
"IP 地址或 URL。对于启用了基本认证的 HAProxy 后面的打印主机，可以通过将用户名和密码"
"放入 URL 中访问，格式如下：https://username:password@your-octopi-address/"

msgid "Device UI"
msgstr "设备界面"

msgid ""
"Specify the URL of your device user interface if it's not same as print_host."
msgstr "如果设备界面 URL 与 print_host 不同，请在此指定。"

msgid "API Key / Password"
msgstr "API 密钥 / 密码"

msgid ""
"Snapmaker Orca can upload G-code files to a printer host. This field should "
"contain the API Key or the password required for authentication."
msgstr ""
"Snapmaker Orca 可以将 G代码文件上传到打印主机。此字段应包含认证所需的 API 密钥或密码。"

msgid "Name of the printer."
msgstr "打印机名称。"

msgid "HTTPS CA File"
msgstr "HTTPS CA 证书文件"

msgid ""
"Custom CA certificate file can be specified for HTTPS OctoPrint connections, "
"in crt/pem format. If left blank, the default OS CA certificate repository "
"is used."
msgstr ""
"可以为 HTTPS OctoPrint 连接指定自定义 CA 证书文件，格式为 crt/pem。"
"如果留空，则使用操作系统默认的 CA 证书库。"

msgid "User"
msgstr "用户"

msgid "Password"
msgstr "密码"

msgid "Ignore HTTPS certificate revocation checks"
msgstr "忽略HTTPS证书吊销检查"

msgid ""
"Ignore HTTPS certificate revocation checks in case of missing or offline "
"distribution points. One may want to enable this option for self signed "
"certificates if connection fails."
msgstr ""
"当分发点缺失或离线时，忽略HTTPS证书吊销检查。如果连接失败，对于自签名证书，"
"您可能需要启用此选项。"

msgid "Names of presets related to the physical printer."
msgstr "与物理打印机相关的预设名称。"

msgid "Authorization Type"
msgstr "授权类型"

msgid "API key"
msgstr "API密钥"

msgid "HTTP digest"
msgstr "HTTP摘要认证"

msgid "Avoid crossing walls"
msgstr "避免穿越外壳"

msgid ""
"Detour to avoid traveling across walls, which may cause blobs on the surface."
msgstr ""
"绕行以避免穿越外壳，这可能会在表面造成凸起。"

msgid "Avoid crossing walls - Max detour length"
msgstr "避免穿越外壳 - 最大绕行距离"

msgid ""
"Maximum detour distance for avoiding crossing wall. Don't detour if the "
"detour distance is larger than this value. Detour length could be specified "
"either as an absolute value or as percentage (for example 50%) of a direct "
"travel path. Zero to disable."
msgstr ""
"避免穿越外壳的最大绕行距离。如果绕行距离大于此值，则不绕行。绕行距离可以指定为绝对值或"
"直接移动路径的百分比（例如50%）。设为0以禁用。"

msgid "mm or %"
msgstr "毫米或%"

msgid "Other layers"
msgstr "其他层"

msgid ""
"Bed temperature for layers except the initial one. A value of 0 means the "
"filament does not support printing on the Cool Plate SuperTack."
msgstr ""
"除首层外的热床温度。值为0表示该耗材不支持在Cool Plate SuperTack上打印。"

msgid ""
"Bed temperature for layers except the initial one. A value of 0 means the "
"filament does not support printing on the Cool Plate."
msgstr ""
"除首层外的热床温度。值为0表示该耗材不支持在Cool Plate上打印。"

msgid ""
"Bed temperature for layers except the initial one. A value of 0 means the "
"filament does not support printing on the Textured Cool Plate."
msgstr ""
"除首层外的热床温度。值为0表示该耗材不支持在Textured Cool Plate上打印。"

msgid ""
"Bed temperature for layers except the initial one. A value of 0 means the "
"filament does not support printing on the Engineering Plate."
msgstr ""
"除首层外的热床温度。值为0表示该耗材不支持在Engineering Plate上打印。"

msgid ""
"Bed temperature for layers except the initial one. A value of 0 means the "
"filament does not support printing on the High Temp Plate."
msgstr ""
"除首层外的热床温度。值为0表示该耗材不支持在High Temp Plate上打印。"

msgid ""
"Bed temperature for layers except the initial one. A value of 0 means the "
"filament does not support printing on the Textured PEI Plate."
msgstr ""
"除首层外的热床温度。值为0表示该耗材不支持在Textured PEI Plate上打印。"

msgid "Initial layer"
msgstr "初始层"

msgid "Initial layer bed temperature"
msgstr "初始层热床温度"

msgid ""
"Bed temperature of the initial layer. A value of 0 means the filament does "
"not support printing on the Cool Plate SuperTack."
msgstr ""
"首层的热床温度。值为0表示该耗材不支持在Cool Plate SuperTack上打印。"

msgid ""
"Bed temperature of the initial layer. A value of 0 means the filament does "
"not support printing on the Cool Plate."
msgstr ""
"首层的热床温度。值为0表示该耗材不支持在Cool Plate上打印。"

msgid ""
"Bed temperature of the initial layer. A value of 0 means the filament does "
"not support printing on the Textured Cool Plate."
msgstr ""
"首层的热床温度。值为0表示该耗材不支持在Textured Cool Plate上打印。"

msgid ""
"Bed temperature of the initial layer. A value of 0 means the filament does "
"not support printing on the Engineering Plate."
msgstr ""
"首层的热床温度。值为0表示该耗材不支持在Engineering Plate上打印。"

msgid ""
"Bed temperature of the initial layer. A value of 0 means the filament does "
"not support printing on the High Temp Plate."
msgstr ""
"首层的热床温度。值为0表示该耗材不支持在High Temp Plate上打印。"

msgid ""
"Bed temperature of the initial layer. A value of 0 means the filament does "
"not support printing on the Textured PEI Plate."
msgstr ""
"首层的热床温度。值为0表示该耗材不支持在Textured PEI Plate上打印。"

msgid "Bed types supported by the printer."
msgstr "打印机支持的热床类型。"

msgid "Smooth Cool Plate"
msgstr "光滑冷板"

msgid "Smooth High Temp Plate"
msgstr "光滑高温板"

msgid "Default bed type"
msgstr "默认热床类型"

msgid ""
"Default bed type for the printer (supports both numeric and string format)."
msgstr "打印机的默认热床类型（支持数字和字符串格式）。"

msgid "First layer print sequence"
msgstr "首层打印顺序"

msgid "Other layers print sequence"
msgstr "其他层打印顺序"

msgid "The number of other layers print sequence"
msgstr "其他层打印顺序数量"

msgid "Other layers filament sequence"
msgstr "其他层耗材顺序"

msgid "This G-code is inserted at every layer change before the Z lift."
msgstr "此G代码在每次层切换时、Z抬升前插入。"

msgid "Bottom shell layers"
msgstr "底部外壳层数"

msgid ""
"This is the number of solid layers of bottom shell, including the bottom "
"surface layer. When the thickness calculated by this value is thinner than "
"bottom shell thickness, the bottom shell layers will be increased."
msgstr ""
"这是底部外壳的实体层数，包括底部表面层。当由此值计算的厚度小于底部外壳厚度时，"
"底部外壳层数将增加。"

msgid "Bottom shell thickness"
msgstr "底部外壳厚度"

msgid ""
"The number of bottom solid layers is increased when slicing if the thickness "
"calculated by bottom shell layers is thinner than this value. This can avoid "
"having too thin shell when layer height is small. 0 means that this setting "
"is disabled and thickness of bottom shell is absolutely determined by bottom "
"shell layers."
msgstr ""
"切片时，如果由底部外壳层数计算的厚度小于此值，则增加底部实体层数。这可以避免"
"层高较小时外壳过薄。0表示禁用此设置，底部外壳厚度完全由底部外壳层数决定。"

msgid "Apply gap fill"
msgstr "应用间隙填充"

msgid ""
"Enables gap fill for the selected solid surfaces. The minimum gap length "
"that will be filled can be controlled from the filter out tiny gaps option "
"below.\n"
"\n"
"Options:\n"
"1. Everywhere: Applies gap fill to top, bottom and internal solid surfaces "
"for maximum strength\n"
"2. Top and Bottom surfaces: Applies gap fill to top and bottom surfaces "
"only, balancing print speed, reducing potential over extrusion in the solid "
"infill and making sure the top and bottom surfaces have no pinhole gaps\n"
"3. Nowhere: Disables gap fill for all solid infill areas\n"
"\n"
"Note that if using the classic perimeter generator, gap fill may also be "
"generated between perimeters, if a full width line cannot fit between them. "
"That perimeter gap fill is not controlled by this setting.\n"
"\n"
"If you would like all gap fill, including the classic perimeter generated "
"one, removed, set the filter out tiny gaps value to a large number, like "
"999999.\n"
"\n"
"However this is not advised, as gap fill between perimeters is contributing "
"to the model's strength. For models where excessive gap fill is generated "
"between perimeters, a better option would be to switch to the arachne wall "
"generator and use this option to control whether the cosmetic top and bottom "
"surface gap fill is generated."
msgstr ""
"为选定的实体表面启用间隙填充。可以通过下方的过滤微小间隙选项控制将被填充的最小间隙长度。\n"
"\n"
"选项：\n"
"1. 全部：对顶部、底部和内部实体表面应用间隙填充，以获得最大强度\n"
"2. 顶部和底部表面：仅对顶部和底部表面应用间隙填充，平衡打印速度，减少实体填充中潜在的过度挤压，确保顶部和底部表面没有针孔间隙\n"
"3. 无：禁用所有实体填充区域的间隙填充\n"
"\n"
"请注意，如果使用经典外壳生成器，当外壳之间无法容纳整条线宽时，也可能会在外壳之间生成间隙填充。该外壳间隙填充不受此设置控制。\n"
"\n"
"如果您希望移除所有间隙填充（包括经典外壳生成器生成的间隙填充），请将过滤微小间隙值设置为一个较大的数字，如999999。\n"
"\n"
"但不建议这样做，因为外壳之间的间隙填充有助于提高模型强度。对于外壳之间生成了过多间隙填充的模型，更好的做法是切换到Arachne外壳生成器，并使用此选项控制是否生成美化性的顶部和底部表面间隙填充。"

msgid "Everywhere"
msgstr "全部"

msgid "Top and bottom surfaces"
msgstr "顶部和底部表面"

msgid "Nowhere"
msgstr "无"

msgid "Force cooling for overhangs and bridges"
msgstr "悬垂和桥接强制冷却"

msgid ""
"Enable this option to allow adjustment of the part cooling fan speed for "
"specifically for overhangs, internal and external bridges. Setting the fan "
"speed specifically for these features can improve overall print quality and "
"reduce warping."
msgstr ""
"启用此选项可针对悬垂、内部和外部桥接单独调节模型冷却风扇转速。为此类特征单独设置风扇转速可提升整体打印质量并减少翘曲。"

msgid "Overhangs and external bridges fan speed"
msgstr "悬垂和外部桥接风扇转速"

msgid ""
"Use this part cooling fan speed when printing bridges or overhang walls with "
"an overhang threshold that exceeds the value set in the 'Overhangs cooling "
"threshold' parameter above. Increasing the cooling specifically for "
"overhangs and bridges can improve the overall print quality of these "
"features.\n"
"\n"
"Please note, this fan speed is clamped on the lower end by the minimum fan "
"speed threshold set above. It is also adjusted upwards up to the maximum fan "
"speed threshold when the minimum layer time threshold is not met."
msgstr ""
"当打印桥接或悬垂角度超过上方"悬垂冷却阈值"参数设定值的悬垂壁时，使用此模型冷却风扇转速。为悬垂和桥接增加冷却可提升这些特征的整体打印质量。\n"
"\n"
"请注意，此风扇转速的下限受上方设置的最小风扇转速阈值约束。当未达到最小层时间阈值时，风扇转速也会向上调整至最大风扇转速阈值。"

msgid "Overhang cooling activation threshold"
msgstr "悬垂冷却激活阈值"

#, no-c-format, no-boost-format

msgid ""
"When the overhang exceeds this specified threshold, force the cooling fan to "
"run at the 'Overhang Fan Speed' set below. This threshold is expressed as a "
"percentage, indicating the portion of each line's width that is unsupported "
"by the layer beneath it. Setting this value to 0% forces the cooling fan to "
"run for all outer walls, regardless of the overhang degree."
msgstr ""
"当悬垂超过此指定阈值时，强制冷却风扇以下方设置的"悬垂风扇转速"运行。此阈值以百分比表示，指示每根线宽中未被下层支撑的部分。将此值设为0%将强制冷却风扇对所有外壁运行，无论悬垂程度如何。"

msgid "External bridge infill direction"
msgstr "外部桥接填充方向"

#, no-c-format, no-boost-format

msgid ""
"Bridging angle override. If left to zero, the bridging angle will be "
"calculated automatically. Otherwise the provided angle will be used for "
"external bridges. Use 180°for zero angle."
msgstr ""
"桥接角度覆盖。若留空为0，桥接角度将自动计算。否则将使用提供的角度用于外部桥接。使用180°表示零度角。"

msgid "Internal bridge infill direction"
msgstr "内部桥接填充方向"

msgid ""
"Internal bridging angle override. If left to zero, the bridging angle will "
"be calculated automatically. Otherwise the provided angle will be used for "
"internal bridges. Use 180°for zero angle.\n"
"\n"
"It is recommended to leave it at 0 unless there is a specific model need not "
"to."
msgstr ""
"内部桥接角度覆盖。若留空为0，桥接角度将自动计算。否则将使用提供的角度用于内部桥接。使用180°表示零度角。\n"
"\n"
"建议保持为0，除非有特定模型需要更改。"

msgid "External bridge density"
msgstr "外部桥接密度"

msgid ""
"Controls the density (spacing) of external bridge lines. 100% means solid "
"bridge. Default is 100%.\n"
"\n"
"Lower density external bridges can help improve reliability as there is more "
"space for air to circulate around the extruded bridge, improving its cooling "
"speed."
msgstr ""
"控制外部桥接线段的密度（间距）。100%表示实心桥接，默认为100%。\n"
"\n"
"较低密度的外部桥接可提高可靠性，因为挤出桥接周围有更多空间让空气流通，从而改善其冷却速度。"

msgid "Internal bridge density"
msgstr "内部桥接密度"

msgid ""
"Controls the density (spacing) of internal bridge lines. 100% means solid "
"bridge. Default is 100%.\n"
"\n"
"Lower density internal bridges can help reduce top surface pillowing and "
"improve internal bridge reliability as there is more space for air to "
"circulate around the extruded bridge, improving its cooling speed.\n"
"\n"
"This option works particularly well when combined with the second internal "
"bridge over infill option, further improving internal bridging structure "
"before solid infill is extruded."
msgstr ""
"控制内部桥接线段的密度（间距）。100%表示实心桥接，默认为100%。\n"
"\n"
"较低密度的内部桥接有助于减少顶面鼓包并提高内部桥接可靠性，因为挤出桥接周围有更多空间让空气流通，从而改善其冷却速度。\n"
"\n"
"此选项与"填充上方第二内部桥接"选项结合使用时效果尤佳，可在挤出实体填充前进一步改善内部桥接结构。"

msgid "Bridge flow ratio"
msgstr "桥接流量比例"

msgid ""
"Decrease this value slightly (for example 0.9) to reduce the amount of "
"material for bridge, to improve sag.\n"
"\n"
"The actual bridge flow used is calculated by multiplying this value with the "
"filament flow ratio, and if set, the object's flow ratio."
msgstr ""
"稍微减小此值（例如0.9）可减少桥接材料用量，改善下垂。\n"
"\n"
"实际使用的桥接流量通过将此值与耗材流量比例相乘计算得出，若已设置，还需乘以模型对象的流量比例。"

msgid "Internal bridge flow ratio"
msgstr "内部桥接流量比例"

msgid ""
"This value governs the thickness of the internal bridge layer. This is the "
"first layer over sparse infill. Decrease this value slightly (for example "
"0.9) to improve surface quality over sparse infill.\n"
"\n"
"The actual internal bridge flow used is calculated by multiplying this value "
"with the bridge flow ratio, the filament flow ratio, and if set, the "
"object's flow ratio."
msgstr ""
"此值控制内部桥接层的厚度。这是稀疏填充上方的第一层。稍微减小此值（例如0.9）可改善稀疏填充上方的表面质量。\n"
"\n"
"实际使用的内部桥接流量通过将此值与桥接流量比例、耗材流量比例相乘计算得出，若已设置，还需乘以模型对象的流量比例。"

msgid "Top surface flow ratio"
msgstr "顶面流量比例"

msgid ""
"This factor affects the amount of material for top solid infill. You can "
"decrease it slightly to have smooth surface finish.\n"
"\n"
"The actual top surface flow used is calculated by multiplying this value "
"with the filament flow ratio, and if set, the object's flow ratio."
msgstr ""
"此系数影响顶部实体填充的材料用量。可稍微减小此值以获得光滑的表面效果。\n"
"\n"
"实际使用的顶面流量通过将此值与耗材流量比例相乘计算得出，若已设置，还需乘以模型对象的流量比例。"

msgid "Bottom surface flow ratio"
msgstr "底面流量比例"

msgid ""
"This factor affects the amount of material for bottom solid infill.\n"
"\n"
"The actual bottom solid infill flow used is calculated by multiplying this "
"value with the filament flow ratio, and if set, the object's flow ratio."
msgstr ""
"此系数影响底部实体填充的材料用量。\n"
"\n"
"实际使用的底部实体填充流量通过将此值与耗材流量比例相乘计算得出，若已设置，还需乘以模型对象的流量比例。"

msgid "Precise wall"
msgstr "精确外壳"

msgid ""
"Improve shell precision by adjusting outer wall spacing. This also improves "
"layer consistency. NOTE: This option will be ignored for outer-inner or "
"inner-outer-inner wall sequences."
msgstr ""
"通过调整外壁间距来改善壳体精度。这也同时改善层间一致性。注意：对于由外到内或由内到外到内的壁顺序，此选项将被忽略。"

msgid "Only one wall on top surfaces"
msgstr "顶面仅单层外壳"

msgid ""
"Use only one wall on flat top surfaces, to give more space to the top infill "
"pattern."
msgstr ""
"在平坦的顶面上仅使用单层外壳，为顶部填充图案提供更多空间。"

msgid "One wall threshold"
msgstr "单层外壳阈值"

#, no-c-format, no-boost-format

msgid ""
"If a top surface has to be printed and it's partially covered by another "
"layer, it won't be considered at a top layer where its width is below this "
"value. This can be useful to not let the 'one perimeter on top' trigger on "
"surface that should be covered only by perimeters. This value can be a mm or "
"a % of the perimeter extrusion width.\n"
"Warning: If enabled, artifacts can be created if you have some thin features "
"on the next layer, like letters. Set this setting to 0 to remove these "
"artifacts."
msgstr ""
"如果需要打印顶面且该顶面部分被另一层覆盖，则当其宽度低于此值时，将不被视为顶层。这有助于避免"顶部单层外壳"在应仅由外壳覆盖的表面上触发。此值可以是以mm为单位或外壳挤出宽度的百分比。\n"
"警告：若启用，下一层存在薄壁特征（如文字）时可能会产生伪影。将此设置设为0可消除这些伪影。"

msgid "Only one wall on first layer"
msgstr "第一层仅单层外壳"

msgid ""
"Use only one wall on first layer, to give more space to the bottom infill "
"pattern."
msgstr ""
"在第一层仅使用单层外壳，为底部填充图案提供更多空间。"

msgid "Extra perimeters on overhangs"
msgstr "悬垂处额外外壳"

msgid ""
"Create additional perimeter paths over steep overhangs and areas where "
"bridges cannot be anchored."
msgstr ""
"在陡峭悬垂以及桥接无法锚固的区域创建额外的外壳路径。"

msgid "Reverse on even"
msgstr "偶数层反转"

msgid "Overhang reversal"
msgstr "悬垂反转"

msgid ""
"Extrude perimeters that have a part over an overhang in the reverse "
"direction on even layers. This alternating pattern can drastically improve "
"steep overhangs.\n"
"\n"
"This setting can also help reduce part warping due to the reduction of "
"stresses in the part walls."
msgstr ""
"在偶数层上，对悬垂部分的外壳以相反方向挤出。这种交替模式可显著改善陡峭悬垂。\n"
"\n"
"此设置还可通过减少模型外壳中的应力来帮助减少模型翘曲。"

msgid "Reverse only internal perimeters"
msgstr "仅反转内部外壳"

msgid ""
"Apply the reverse perimeters logic only on internal perimeters.\n"
"\n"
"This setting greatly reduces part stresses as they are now distributed in "
"alternating directions. This should reduce part warping while also "
"maintaining external wall quality. This feature can be very useful for warp "
"prone material, like ABS/ASA, and also for elastic filaments, like TPU and "
"Silk PLA. It can also help reduce warping on floating regions over "
"supports.\n"
"\n"
"For this setting to be the most effective, it is recommended to set the "
"Reverse Threshold to 0 so that all internal walls print in alternating "
"directions on even layers irrespective of their overhang degree."
msgstr ""
"仅对内部外壳应用反转外壳逻辑。\n"
"\n"
"此设置大大减少了模型应力，因为应力现以交替方向分布。这应能减少模型翘曲，同时保持外壁质量。此功能对易翘曲材料（如ABS/ASA）以及弹性耗材（如TPU和丝绸PLA）非常有用。它还有助于减少支撑上方浮动区域的翘曲。\n"
"\n"
"为使此设置达到最佳效果，建议将反转阈值设为0，以便所有内部壁在偶数层上以交替方向打印，无论其悬垂程度如何。"

msgid "Bridge counterbore holes"
msgstr "桥接沉头孔"

msgid ""
"This option creates bridges for counterbore holes, allowing them to be "
"printed without support. Available modes include:\n"
"1. None: No bridge is created\n"
"2. Partially Bridged: Only a part of the unsupported area will be bridged\n"
"3. Sacrificial Layer: A full sacrificial bridge layer is created"
msgstr ""
"此选项为沉头孔创建桥接，使其无需支撑即可打印。可用模式包括：\n"
"1. 无：不创建桥接\n"
"2. 部分桥接：仅桥接部分无支撑区域\n"
"3. 牺牲层：创建完整的牺牲桥接层"

msgid "Partially bridged"
msgstr "部分桥接"

msgid "Sacrificial layer"
msgstr "牺牲层"

msgid "Reverse threshold"
msgstr "反转阈值"

msgid "Overhang reversal threshold"
msgstr "悬垂反转阈值"

#, no-c-format, no-boost-format

msgid ""
"Number of mm the overhang need to be for the reversal to be considered "
"useful. Can be a % of the perimeter width.\n"
"Value 0 enables reversal on every even layers regardless.\n"
"When Detect overhang wall is not enabled, this option is ignored and "
"reversal happens on every even layers regardless."
msgstr ""
"悬垂需要达到的毫米数，反转才被认为有用。可以是外壳宽度的百分比。\n"
"值为0时无论如何都会在每一偶数层启用反转。\n"
"当未启用"检测悬垂壁"时，此选项被忽略，反转会在每一偶数层无条件发生。"

msgid "Slow down for overhang"
msgstr "悬垂减速"

msgid "Enable this option to slow printing down for different overhang degree."
msgstr "启用此选项可根据不同的悬垂程度降低打印速度。"

msgid "Slow down for curled perimeters"
msgstr "卷曲外壁减速"

#, no-c-format, no-boost-format

msgid ""
"Enable this option to slow down printing in areas where perimeters may have "
"curled upwards. For example, additional slowdown will be applied when "
"printing overhangs on sharp corners like the front of the Benchy hull, "
"reducing curling which compounds over multiple layers.\n"
"\n"
"It is generally recommended to have this option switched on unless your "
"printer cooling is powerful enough or the print speed slow enough that "
"perimeter curling does not happen. If printing with a high external "
"perimeter speed, this parameter may introduce slight artifacts when slowing "
"down due to the large variance in print speeds. If you notice artifacts, "
"ensure your pressure advance is tuned correctly.\n"
"\n"
"Note: When this option is enabled, overhang perimeters are treated like "
"overhangs, meaning the overhang speed is applied even if the overhanging "
"perimeter is part of a bridge. For example, when the perimeters are 100% "
"overhanging, with no wall supporting them from underneath, the 100% overhang "
"speed will be applied."
msgstr ""
"启用此选项可在外壁可能向上卷曲的区域降低打印速度。例如，在打印尖锐拐角（如Benchy船头）的悬垂时，"
"会额外减速，从而减少会在多层累积的卷曲问题。\n"
"\n"
"通常建议开启此选项，除非您的打印机冷却能力足够强或打印速度足够慢，以至于不会发生外壁卷曲。"
"如果以较高的外壁速度打印，此参数在减速时可能会因打印速度差异过大而产生轻微伪影。"
"如果发现伪影，请确保压力提前已正确校准。\n"
"\n"
"注意：启用此选项后，悬垂外壁将被视为悬垂处理，"
"即使悬垂外壁是桥接的一部分，也会应用悬垂速度。"
"例如，当外壁100%悬垂且下方没有壁支撑时，将应用100%悬垂速度。"

msgid "mm/s or %"
msgstr "毫米/秒 或 %"

msgid "External"
msgstr "外部"

msgid ""
"Speed of the externally visible bridge extrusions.\n"
"\n"
"In addition, if Slow down for curled perimeters is disabled or Classic "
"overhang mode is enabled, it will be the print speed of overhang walls that "
"are supported by less than 13%, whether they are part of a bridge or an "
"overhang."
msgstr ""
"外部可见桥接挤出线的速度。\n"
"\n"
"此外，如果禁用卷曲外壁减速或启用了经典悬垂模式，"
"它将是支撑面积小于13%的悬垂壁的打印速度，无论它们是桥接还是悬垂的一部分。"

msgid "Internal"
msgstr "内部"

msgid ""
"Speed of internal bridges. If the value is expressed as a percentage, it "
"will be calculated based on the bridge_speed. Default value is 150%."
msgstr ""
"内部桥接的速度。如果该值以百分比表示，则将基于桥接速度（bridge_speed）计算。默认值为150%。"

msgid "Brim width"
msgstr "底边宽度"

msgid "Distance from model to the outermost brim line."
msgstr "从模型到最外侧底边线的距离。"

msgid "Brim type"
msgstr "底边类型"

msgid ""
"This controls the generation of the brim at outer and/or inner side of "
"models. Auto means the brim width is analyzed and calculated automatically."
msgstr ""
"控制模型外侧和/或内侧底边的生成。自动模式表示底边宽度会被分析和自动计算。"

msgid "Brim-object gap"
msgstr "底边-对象间隙"

msgid ""
"A gap between innermost brim line and object can make brim be removed more "
"easily."
msgstr ""
"在最内侧底边线与对象之间设置间隙可以使底边更容易移除。"

msgid "Brim ears"
msgstr "底边耳"

msgid "Only draw brim over the sharp edges of the model."
msgstr "仅在模型的锐利边缘绘制底边。"

msgid "Brim ear max angle"
msgstr "底边耳最大角度"

msgid ""
"Maximum angle to let a brim ear appear.\n"
"If set to 0, no brim will be created.\n"
"If set to ~180, brim will be created on everything but straight sections."
msgstr ""
"允许出现底边耳的最大角度。\n"
"如果设置为0，则不创建任何底边。\n"
"如果设置为约180，则除了直线段之外的所有位置都会创建底边。"

msgid "Brim ear detection radius"
msgstr "底边耳检测半径"

msgid ""
"The geometry will be decimated before detecting sharp angles. This parameter "
"indicates the minimum length of the deviation for the decimation.\n"
"0 to deactivate."
msgstr ""
"在检测锐角之前会对几何体进行减面处理。此参数指示减面处理的最小偏差长度。\n"
"0表示停用。"

msgid "Select printers"
msgstr "选择打印机"

msgid "upward compatible machine"
msgstr "向上兼容的机器"

msgid "Condition"
msgstr "条件"

msgid ""
"A boolean expression using the configuration values of an active printer "
"profile. If this expression evaluates to true, this profile is considered "
"compatible with the active printer profile."
msgstr ""
"使用活动打印机配置文件配置值的布尔表达式。如果此表达式求值为真，"
"则该配置文件被视为与活动打印机配置文件兼容。"

msgid "Select profiles"
msgstr "选择配置文件"

msgid ""
"A boolean expression using the configuration values of an active print "
"profile. If this expression evaluates to true, this profile is considered "
"compatible with the active print profile."
msgstr ""
"使用活动打印配置文件配置值的布尔表达式。如果此表达式求值为真，"
"则该配置文件被视为与活动打印配置文件兼容。"

msgid "Print sequence, layer by layer or object by object."
msgstr "打印顺序，逐层或逐对象。"

msgid "By layer"
msgstr "按层"

msgid "By object"
msgstr "按对象"

msgid "Intra-layer order"
msgstr "层内顺序"

msgid "Print order within a single layer."
msgstr "单层内的打印顺序。"

msgid "As object list"
msgstr "按对象列表"

msgid "Slow printing down for better layer cooling"
msgstr "降低打印速度以获得更好的层冷却"

msgid ""
"Enable this option to slow printing speed down to make the final layer time "
"not shorter than the layer time threshold in \"Max fan speed threshold\", so "
"that layer can be cooled for longer time. This can improve the cooling "
"quality for needle and small details."
msgstr ""
"启用此选项可降低打印速度，使最终层的打印时间不短于\"最大风扇速度阈值\"中的层时间阈值，"
"从而使层能够获得更长的冷却时间。这可以改善细小细节的冷却质量。"

msgid "Normal printing"
msgstr "正常打印"

msgid ""
"The default acceleration of both normal printing and travel except initial "
"layer."
msgstr ""
"正常打印和移动的默认加速度，初始层除外。"

msgid "Default filament profile"
msgstr "默认耗材配置文件"

msgid "Default filament profile when switching to this machine profile."
msgstr "切换到本机器配置文件时的默认耗材配置文件。"

msgid "Default process profile"
msgstr "默认工艺配置文件"

msgid "Default process profile when switching to this machine profile."
msgstr "切换到本机器配置文件时的默认工艺配置文件。"

msgid "Activate air filtration"
msgstr "启动空气过滤"

msgid "Activate for better air filtration. G-code command: M106 P3 S(0-255)"
msgstr "启动以获得更好的空气过滤。G代码命令：M106 P3 S(0-255)"

msgid "Fan speed"
msgstr "风扇速度"

msgid ""
"Speed of exhaust fan during printing. This speed will override the speed in "
"filament custom G-code."
msgstr ""
"打印期间排风扇的速度。此速度将覆盖耗材自定义G代码中的速度。"

msgid "Speed of exhaust fan after printing completes."
msgstr "打印完成后排气扇的速度。"

msgid "No cooling for the first"
msgstr "前几层不冷却"

msgid ""
"Turn off all cooling fans for the first few layers. This can be used to "
"improve build plate adhesion."
msgstr ""
"关闭前几层的所有冷却风扇。可用于提高热床附着力。"

msgid "Don't support bridges"
msgstr "不支撑桥接"

msgid ""
"Don't support the whole bridge area which make support very large. Bridges "
"can usually be printed directly without support if not very long."
msgstr ""
"不支撑整个桥接区域，否则支撑会变得非常大。如果桥接长度不长，通常可以直接打印而无需支撑。"

msgid "Thick external bridges"
msgstr "厚外部桥接"

msgid ""
"If enabled, bridges are more reliable, can bridge longer distances, but may "
"look worse. If disabled, bridges look better but are reliable just for "
"shorter bridged distances."
msgstr ""
"如果启用，桥接更可靠，可以跨越更长的距离，但外观可能较差。如果禁用，桥接外观更好，但仅在较短的桥接距离内可靠。"

msgid "Thick internal bridges"
msgstr "厚内部桥接"

msgid ""
"If enabled, thick internal bridges will be used. It's usually recommended to "
"have this feature turned on. However, consider turning it off if you are "
"using large nozzles."
msgstr ""
"如果启用，将使用厚内部桥接。通常建议开启此功能。但是，如果使用大型喷嘴，请考虑将其关闭。"

msgid "Extra bridge layers (beta)"
msgstr "额外桥接层（测试版）"

msgid ""
"This option enables the generation of an extra bridge layer over internal "
"and/or external bridges.\n"
"\n"
"Extra bridge layers help improve bridge appearance and reliability, as the "
"solid infill is better supported. This is especially useful in fast "
"printers, where the bridge and solid infill speeds vary greatly. The extra "
"bridge layer results in reduced pillowing on top surfaces, as well as "
"reduced separation of the external bridge layer from its surrounding "
"perimeters.\n"
"\n"
"It is generally recommended to set this to at least 'External bridge only', "
"unless specific issues with the sliced model are found.\n"
"\n"
"Options:\n"
"1. Disabled - does not generate second bridge layers. This is the default "
"and is set for compatibility purposes\n"
"2. External bridge only - generates second bridge layers for external-facing "
"bridges only. Please note that small bridges that are shorter or narrower "
"than the set number of perimeters will be skipped as they would not benefit "
"from a second bridge layer. If generated, the second bridge layer will be "
"extruded parallel to the first bridge layer to reinforce the bridge "
"strength\n"
"3. Internal bridge only - generates second bridge layers for internal "
"bridges over sparse infill only. Please note that the internal bridges count "
"towards the top shell layer count of your model. The second internal bridge "
"layer will be extruded as close to perpendicular to the first as possible. "
"If multiple regions in the same island, with varying bridge angles are "
"present, the last region of that island will be selected as the angle "
"reference\n"
"4. Apply to all - generates second bridge layers for both internal and "
"external-facing bridges\n"
msgstr ""
"此选项允许在内部和/或外部桥接上方生成额外的桥接层。\n"
"\n"
"额外桥接层有助于改善桥接外观和可靠性，因为实体填充得到更好的支撑。这在快速打印机上尤其有用，因为桥接和实体填充速度差异很大。额外的桥接层可减少顶面枕垫效应，并减少外部桥接层与其周围外壳的分离。\n"
"\n"
"通常建议至少将其设置为"仅外部桥接"，除非发现切片模型存在特定问题。\n"
"\n"
"选项：\n"
"1. 禁用 - 不生成第二桥接层。这是默认设置，出于兼容性考虑\n"
"2. 仅外部桥接 - 仅为外部桥接生成第二桥接层。请注意，比设定的外壳数量更短或更窄的小桥接将被跳过，因为它们不会从第二桥接层中受益。如果生成，第二桥接层将平行于第一桥接层挤出，以增强桥接强度\n"
"3. 仅内部桥接 - 仅对稀疏填充上方的内部桥接生成第二桥接层。请注意，内部桥接计入模型的顶部外壳层数。第二内部桥接层将尽可能垂直于第一层挤出。如果同一区域中存在多个具有不同桥接角度的区域，则将选择该区域的最后一个区域作为角度参考\n"
"4. 应用于全部 - 为内部和外部桥接均生成第二桥接层\n"

msgid "Disabled"
msgstr "禁用"

msgid "External bridge only"
msgstr "仅外部桥接"

msgid "Internal bridge only"
msgstr "仅内部桥接"

msgid "Apply to all"
msgstr "应用于全部"

msgid "Filter out small internal bridges"
msgstr "过滤小内部桥接"

msgid ""
"This option can help reduce pillowing on top surfaces in heavily slanted or "
"curved models.\n"
"By default, small internal bridges are filtered out and the internal solid "
"infill is printed directly over the sparse infill. This works well in most "
"cases, speeding up printing without too much compromise on top surface "
"quality.\n"
"However, in heavily slanted or curved models, especially where too low a "
"sparse infill density is used, this may result in curling of the unsupported "
"solid infill, causing pillowing.\n"
"Enabling limited filtering or no filtering will print internal bridge layer "
"over slightly unsupported internal solid infill. The options below control "
"the sensitivity of the filtering, i.e. they control where internal bridges "
"are created:\n"
"1. Filter - enables this option. This is the default behavior and works well "
"in most cases\n"
"2. Limited filtering - creates internal bridges on heavily slanted surfaces "
"while avoiding unnecessary bridges. This works well for most difficult "
"models\n"
"3. No filtering - creates internal bridges on every potential internal "
"overhang. This option is useful for heavily slanted top surface models; "
"however, in most cases, it creates too many unnecessary bridges"
msgstr ""
"此选项有助于减少严重倾斜或弯曲模型顶面的枕垫效应。\n"
"默认情况下，小内部桥接被过滤掉，内部实体填充直接打印在稀疏填充上方。这在大多数情况下效果良好，加快了打印速度而不会过多影响顶面质量。\n"
"然而，在严重倾斜或弯曲的模型中，特别是当稀疏填充密度过低时，可能导致未支撑的实体填充卷曲，引起枕垫效应。\n"
"启用有限过滤或不过滤将在轻微未支撑的内部实体填充上方打印内部桥接层。以下选项控制过滤的灵敏度，即控制内部桥接的创建位置：\n"
"1. 过滤 - 启用此选项。这是默认行为，在大多数情况下效果良好\n"
"2. 有限过滤 - 在严重倾斜的表面上创建内部桥接，同时避免不必要的桥接。这适用于大多数困难模型\n"
"3. 不过滤 - 在每个潜在内部悬垂处创建内部桥接。此选项适用于顶面严重倾斜的模型；但在大多数情况下会创建太多不必要的桥接"

msgid "Filter"
msgstr "过滤"

msgid "Limited filtering"
msgstr "有限过滤"

msgid "No filtering"
msgstr "不过滤"

msgid "Max bridge length"
msgstr "最大桥接长度"

msgid ""
"Max length of bridges that don't need support. Set it to 0 if you want all "
"bridges to be supported, and set it to a very large value if you don't want "
"any bridges to be supported."
msgstr ""
"不需要支撑的桥接的最大长度。如果您希望所有桥接都被支撑，请将其设置为0；如果您不希望任何桥接被支撑，请将其设置为一个非常大的值。"

msgid "End G-code"
msgstr "结束G代码"

msgid "End G-code when finishing the entire print."
msgstr "完成整个打印时的结束G代码。"

msgid "Between Object G-code"
msgstr "对象间G代码"

msgid ""
"Insert G-code between objects. This parameter will only come into effect "
"when you print your models object by object."
msgstr ""
"在对象之间插入G代码。此参数仅在逐个对象打印模型时生效。"

msgid "End G-code when finishing the printing of this filament."
msgstr "完成此耗材打印时的结束G代码。"

msgid "Ensure vertical shell thickness"
msgstr "确保垂直外壳厚度"

msgid ""
"Add solid infill near sloping surfaces to guarantee the vertical shell "
"thickness (top+bottom solid layers)\n"
"None: No solid infill will be added anywhere. Caution: Use this option "
"carefully if your model has sloped surfaces\n"
"Critical Only: Avoid adding solid infill for walls\n"
"Moderate: Add solid infill for heavily sloping surfaces only\n"
"All: Add solid infill for all suitable sloping surfaces\n"
"Default value is All."
msgstr ""
"在倾斜表面附近添加实体填充，以保证垂直外壳厚度（顶部+底部实体层）\n"
"无：不会在任何地方添加实体填充。注意：如果您的模型有倾斜表面，请谨慎使用此选项\n"
"仅关键区域：避免为墙壁添加实体填充\n"
"中等：仅为严重倾斜的表面添加实体填充\n"
"全部：为所有合适的倾斜表面添加实体填充\n"
"默认值为全部。"

msgid "Critical Only"
msgstr "仅关键区域"

msgid "Moderate"
msgstr "中等"

msgid "Top surface pattern"
msgstr "顶面图案"

msgid "Line pattern of top surface infill."
msgstr "顶面填充的线条图案。"

msgid "Monotonic"
msgstr "单调"

msgid "Monotonic line"
msgstr "单调线条"

msgid "Rectilinear"
msgstr "直线"

msgid "Aligned Rectilinear"
msgstr "对齐直线"

msgid "Concentric"
msgstr "同心"

msgid "Hilbert Curve"
msgstr "希尔伯特曲线"

msgid "Archimedean Chords"
msgstr "阿基米德弦"

msgid "Octagram Spiral"
msgstr "八角星螺旋"

msgid "Bottom surface pattern"
msgstr "底面图案"

msgid "Line pattern of bottom surface infill, not bridge infill."
msgstr "底面填充的线条图案，不包括桥接填充。"

msgid "Internal solid infill pattern"
msgstr "内部实体填充图案"

msgid ""
"Line pattern of internal solid infill. if the detect narrow internal solid "
"infill be enabled, the concentric pattern will be used for the small area."
msgstr ""
"内部实体填充的线条图案。如果启用了检测狭窄内部实体填充，则小区域将使用同心图案。"

msgid ""
"Line width of outer wall. If expressed as a %, it will be computed over the "
"nozzle diameter."
msgstr ""
"外壳线宽。若以百分比表示，则将根据喷嘴直径计算。"

msgid ""
"Speed of outer wall which is outermost and visible. It's used to be slower "
"than inner wall speed to get better quality."
msgstr ""
"最外层可见壁面的打印速度。通常比内壁速度慢以获得更好的表面质量。"

msgid "Small perimeters"
msgstr "小周长轮廓"

msgid ""
"This separate setting will affect the speed of perimeters having radius <= "
"small_perimeter_threshold (usually holes). If expressed as percentage (for "
"example: 80%) it will be calculated on the outer wall speed setting above. "
"Set to zero for auto."
msgstr ""
"此独立设置将影响半径 <= small_perimeter_threshold（通常为孔洞）的轮廓速度。"
"若以百分比表示（例如：80%），则将基于上述外壳速度计算。设置为零则自动。"

msgid "Small perimeters threshold"
msgstr "小周长轮廓阈值"

msgid ""
"This sets the threshold for small perimeter length. Default threshold is 0mm."
msgstr "设置小周长轮廓的长度阈值。默认阈值为0mm。"

msgid "Walls printing order"
msgstr "壁面打印顺序"

msgid ""
"Print sequence of the internal (inner) and external (outer) walls.\n"
"\n"
"Use Inner/Outer for best overhangs. This is because the overhanging walls "
"can adhere to a neighbouring perimeter while printing. However, this option "
"results in slightly reduced surface quality as the external perimeter is "
"deformed by being squashed to the internal perimeter.\n"
"\n"
"Use Inner/Outer/Inner for the best external surface finish and dimensional "
"accuracy as the external wall is printed undisturbed from an internal "
"perimeter. However, overhang performance will reduce as there is no internal "
"perimeter to print the external wall against. This option requires a minimum "
"of 3 walls to be effective as it prints the internal walls from the 3rd "
"perimeter onwards first, then the external perimeter and, finally, the first "
"internal perimeter. This option is recommended against the Outer/Inner "
"option in most cases.\n"
"\n"
"Use Outer/Inner for the same external wall quality and dimensional accuracy "
"benefits of Inner/Outer/Inner option. However, the z seams will appear less "
"consistent as the first extrusion of a new layer starts on a visible "
"surface.\n"
"\n"
" "
msgstr ""
"内部（内壁）和外部（外壁）的打印顺序。\n"
"\n"
"使用内/外顺序可获得最佳悬垂效果。这是因为悬垂的壁面在打印时可以附着到相邻的轮廓上。"
"但是，此选项会导致表面质量略有下降，因为外壁会被挤压到内壁而变形。\n"
"\n"
"使用内/外/内顺序可获得最佳的外表面光洁度和尺寸精度，因为外壁在打印时不受内壁干扰。"
"但是，悬垂性能会降低，因为没有内壁可供外壁附着打印。此选项需要至少3层壁面才能生效，"
"因为它先打印从第3条轮廓开始的内壁，然后打印外壁，最后打印第一条内壁。"
"在大多数情况下，建议使用此选项而非外/内顺序。\n"
"\n"
"使用外/内顺序可获得与内/外/内选项相同的外壁质量和尺寸精度。"
"但是，接缝会显得不够一致，因为新层的第一条挤出从可见表面开始。\n"
"\n"
" "

msgid "Inner/Outer"
msgstr "内/外"

msgid "Outer/Inner"
msgstr "外/内"

msgid "Inner/Outer/Inner"
msgstr "内/外/内"

msgid "Print infill first"
msgstr "先打印填充"

msgid ""
"Order of wall/infill. When the tickbox is unchecked the walls are printed "
"first, which works best in most cases.\n"
"\n"
"Printing infill first may help with extreme overhangs as the walls have the "
"neighbouring infill to adhere to. However, the infill will slightly push out "
"the printed walls where it is attached to them, resulting in a worse "
"external surface finish. It can also cause the infill to shine through the "
"external surfaces of the part."
msgstr ""
"壁面/填充的打印顺序。取消勾选时，壁面将先打印，这在大多数情况下效果最佳。\n"
"\n"
"先打印填充可能有助于处理极端悬垂，因为壁面可以附着到相邻的填充上。"
"但是，填充会在附着处轻微推挤已打印的壁面，导致外表面光洁度变差。"
"还可能导致填充在零件外表面显现出来。"

msgid "Wall loop direction"
msgstr "壁面环方向"

msgid ""
"The direction which the wall loops are extruded when looking down from the "
"top.\n"
"\n"
"By default all walls are extruded in counter-clockwise, unless Reverse on "
"even is enabled. Set this to any option other than Auto will force the wall "
"direction regardless of the Reverse on even.\n"
"\n"
"This option will be disabled if spiral vase mode is enabled."
msgstr ""
"从顶部俯瞰时壁面环的挤出方向。\n"
"\n"
"默认情况下，所有壁面均按逆时针方向挤出，除非启用了偶数层反转。"
"将此选项设置为除自动以外的任何选项将强制指定壁面方向，不受偶数层反转影响。\n"
"\n"
"如果启用了螺旋花瓶模式，此选项将被禁用。"

msgid "Counter clockwise"
msgstr "逆时针"

msgid "Clockwise"
msgstr "顺时针"

msgid "Height to rod"
msgstr "至横杆高度"

msgid ""
"Distance of the nozzle tip to the lower rod. Used for collision avoidance in "
"by-object printing."
msgstr ""
"喷嘴尖端到下横杆的距离。用于按对象打印时的碰撞避免。"

msgid "Height to lid"
msgstr "至顶盖高度"

msgid ""
"Distance of the nozzle tip to the lid. Used for collision avoidance in by-"
"object printing."
msgstr ""
"喷嘴尖端到顶盖的距离。用于按对象打印时的碰撞避免。"

msgid ""
"Clearance radius around extruder. Used for collision avoidance in by-object "
"printing."
msgstr "挤出机周围的间隙半径。用于按对象打印时的碰撞避免。"

msgid "Nozzle height"
msgstr "喷嘴高度"

msgid "The height of nozzle tip."
msgstr "喷嘴尖端的高度。"

msgid "Bed mesh min"
msgstr "热床网格最小点"

msgid ""
"This option sets the min point for the allowed bed mesh area. Due to the "
"probe's XY offset, most printers are unable to probe the entire bed. To "
"ensure the probe point does not go outside the bed area, the minimum and "
"maximum points of the bed mesh should be set appropriately. Snapmaker Orca "
"ensures that adaptive_bed_mesh_min/adaptive_bed_mesh_max values do not "
"exceed these min/max points. This information can usually be obtained from "
"your printer manufacturer. The default setting is (-99999, -99999), which "
"means there are no limits, thus allowing probing across the entire bed."
msgstr ""
"此选项设置允许的热床网格区域的最小点。由于探针的XY偏移，大多数打印机无法探测整个热床。"
"为确保探测点不超出热床区域，应适当设置热床网格的最小点和最大点。"
"Snapmaker Orca确保adaptive_bed_mesh_min/adaptive_bed_mesh_max值不超过这些最小/最大点。"
"此信息通常可从打印机制造商处获取。默认设置为(-99999, -99999)，表示没有限制，"
"从而允许在整个热床上进行探测。"

msgid "Bed mesh max"
msgstr "热床网格最大点"

msgid ""
"This option sets the max point for the allowed bed mesh area. Due to the "
"probe's XY offset, most printers are unable to probe the entire bed. To "
"ensure the probe point does not go outside the bed area, the minimum and "
"maximum points of the bed mesh should be set appropriately. Snapmaker Orca "
"ensures that adaptive_bed_mesh_min/adaptive_bed_mesh_max values do not "
"exceed these min/max points. This information can usually be obtained from "
"your printer manufacturer. The default setting is (99999, 99999), which "
"means there are no limits, thus allowing probing across the entire bed."
msgstr ""
"此选项设置允许的热床网格区域的最大点。由于探针的XY偏移，大多数打印机无法探测整个热床。"
"为确保探测点不超出热床区域，应适当设置热床网格的最小点和最大点。"
"Snapmaker Orca确保adaptive_bed_mesh_min/adaptive_bed_mesh_max值不超过这些最小/最大点。"
"此信息通常可从打印机制造商处获取。默认设置为(99999, 99999)，表示没有限制，"
"从而允许在整个热床上进行探测。"

msgid "Probe point distance"
msgstr "探测点距离"

msgid ""
"This option sets the preferred distance between probe points (grid size) for "
"the X and Y directions, with the default being 50mm for both X and Y."
msgstr ""
"此选项设置X和Y方向上探测点之间的优选距离（网格大小），X和Y的默认值均为50mm。"

msgid "Mesh margin"
msgstr "网格边距"

msgid ""
"This option determines the additional distance by which the adaptive bed "
"mesh area should be expanded in the XY directions."
msgstr "此选项决定自适应热床网格区域在XY方向上应扩展的额外距离。"

msgid "Extruder Color"
msgstr "挤出机颜色"

msgid "Only used as a visual help on UI."
msgstr "仅在界面上用作视觉辅助。"

msgid "Extruder offset"
msgstr "挤出机偏移"

msgid "Flow ratio"
msgstr "流量比例"

msgid ""
"The material may have volumetric change after switching between molten and "
"crystalline states. This setting changes all extrusion flow of this filament "
"in G-code proportionally. The recommended value range is between 0.95 and "
"1.05. You may be able to tune this value to get a nice flat surface if there "
"is slight overflow or underflow."
msgstr ""
"材料在熔融态和结晶态之间转变时可能发生体积变化。此设置按比例更改G代码中该耗材的所有挤出流量。"
"建议值范围在0.95到1.05之间。如果存在轻微溢出或欠挤，您可以通过调整此值来获得平整的表面。"

msgid ""
"The material may have volumetric change after switching between molten and "
"crystalline states. This setting changes all extrusion flow of this filament "
"in G-code proportionally. The recommended value range is between 0.95 and "
"1.05. You may be able to tune this value to get a nice flat surface if there "
"is slight overflow or underflow.\n"
"\n"
"The final object flow ratio is this value multiplied by the filament flow "
"ratio."
msgstr ""
"材料在熔融态和结晶态之间转变时可能发生体积变化。此设置按比例更改G代码中该耗材的所有挤出流量。"
"建议值范围在0.95到1.05之间。如果存在轻微溢出或欠挤，您可以通过调整此值来获得平整的表面。\n"
"\n"
"最终物体流量比例为此值乘以耗材流量比例。"

msgid "Enable pressure advance"
msgstr "启用压力提前"

msgid ""
"Enable pressure advance, auto calibration result will be overwritten once "
"enabled."
msgstr "启用压力提前，一旦启用将覆盖自动校准结果。"

msgid "Pressure advance (Klipper) AKA Linear advance factor (Marlin)."
msgstr "压力提前（Klipper）即线性提前系数（Marlin）。"

msgid "Enable adaptive pressure advance (beta)"
msgstr "启用自适应压力提前（测试版）"

#, no-c-format, no-boost-format

msgid ""
"With increasing print speeds (and hence increasing volumetric flow through "
"the nozzle) and increasing accelerations, it has been observed that the "
"effective PA value typically decreases. This means that a single PA value is "
"not always 100% optimal for all features and a compromise value is usually "
"used that does not cause too much bulging on features with lower flow speed "
"and accelerations while also not causing gaps on faster features.\n"
"\n"
"This feature aims to address this limitation by modeling the response of "
"your printer's extrusion system depending on the volumetric flow speed and "
"acceleration it is printing at. Internally, it generates a fitted model that "
"can extrapolate the needed pressure advance for any given volumetric flow "
"speed and acceleration, which is then emitted to the printer depending on "
"the current print conditions.\n"
"\n"
"When enabled, the pressure advance value above is overridden. However, a "
"reasonable default value above is strongly recommended to act as a fallback "
"and for when tool changing.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"随着打印速度的提高（因而通过喷嘴的体积流量增加）和加速度的增加，"
"实际有效的PA值通常会降低。这意味着单一的PA值并非对所有特征都是100%最优的，"
"通常使用一个折中值，使其在流量速度和加速度较低的特征上不会造成过多凸起，"
"同时在较快的特征上也不会产生间隙。\n"
"\n"
"此功能旨在根据打印时的体积流量速度和加速度对打印机挤出系统的响应进行建模，"
"来解决这一限制。在内部，它生成一个拟合模型，可以推断出任何给定体积流量速度和加速度所需的压力提前值，"
"然后根据当前打印条件将其输出到打印机。\n"
"\n"
"启用后，上述压力提前值将被覆盖。但强烈建议设置一个合理的默认值作为备用，以及在换刀时使用。\n"
"\n"

msgid "Adaptive pressure advance measurements (beta)"
msgstr "自适应压力提前测量（测试版）"

#, no-c-format, no-boost-format

msgid ""
"Add sets of pressure advance (PA) values, the volumetric flow speeds and "
"accelerations they were measured at, separated by a comma. One set of values "
"per line. For example\n"
"0.04,3.96,3000\n"
"0.033,3.96,10000\n"
"0.029,7.91,3000\n"
"0.026,7.91,10000\n"
"\n"
"How to calibrate:\n"
"1. Run the pressure advance test for at least 3 speeds per acceleration "
"value. It is recommended that the test is run for at least the speed of the "
"external perimeters, the speed of the internal perimeters and the fastest "
"feature print speed in your profile (usually its the sparse or solid "
"infill). Then run them for the same speeds for the slowest and fastest print "
"accelerations, and no faster than the recommended maximum acceleration as "
"given by the Klipper input shaper\n"
"2. Take note of the optimal PA value for each volumetric flow speed and "
"acceleration. You can find the flow number by selecting flow from the color "
"scheme drop down and move the horizontal slider over the PA pattern lines. "
"The number should be visible at the bottom of the page. The ideal PA value "
"should be decreasing the higher the volumetric flow is. If it is not, "
"confirm that your extruder is functioning correctly. The slower and with "
"less acceleration you print, the larger the range of acceptable PA values. "
"If no difference is visible, use the PA value from the faster test\n"
"3. Enter the triplets of PA values, Flow and Accelerations in the text box "
"here and save your filament profile"
msgstr ""
"添加多组压力提前（PA）值、测量时的体积流量速度和加速度，以逗号分隔。每组值占一行。例如\n"
"0.04,3.96,3000\n"
"0.033,3.96,10000\n"
"0.029,7.91,3000\n"
"0.026,7.91,10000\n"
"\n"
"校准方法：\n"
"1. 对每个加速度值，至少以3种速度运行压力提前测试。建议至少测试外壁速度、"
"内壁速度以及配置文件中最快的特征打印速度（通常为稀疏填充或实体填充）对应的速度。"
"然后对最慢和最快的打印加速度运行相同速度的测试，且不超过Klipper input shaper给出的推荐最大加速度。\n"
"2. 记录每个体积流量速度和加速度对应的最佳PA值。您可以从配色方案下拉菜单中选择流量，"
"然后将水平滑块移动到PA模式线上方来查看流量数值。该数值应显示在页面底部。"
"理想的PA值应随体积流量的增加而减小。如果不是，请确认您的挤出机工作正常。"
"打印速度越慢、加速度越小，可接受的PA值范围就越大。如果看不到差异，请使用较快测试中的PA值。\n"
"3. 在此文本框中输入PA值、流量和加速度的三元组，然后保存您的耗材配置文件。"

msgid "Enable adaptive pressure advance for overhangs (beta)"
msgstr "为悬垂启用自适应压力提前（测试版）"

msgid ""
"Enable adaptive PA for overhangs as well as when flow changes within the "
"same feature. This is an experimental option, as if the PA profile is not "
"set accurately, it will cause uniformity issues on the external surfaces "
"before and after overhangs.\n"
msgstr ""
"为悬垂以及同一特征内流量变化时启用自适应压力提前。这是一个实验选项，如果压力提前配置文件设置不准确，"
"则会导致悬垂前后外部表面出现均匀性问题。\n"

msgid "Pressure advance for bridges"
msgstr "桥接压力提前"

msgid ""
"Pressure advance value for bridges. Set to 0 to disable.\n"
"\n"
"A lower PA value when printing bridges helps reduce the appearance of slight "
"under extrusion immediately after bridges. This is caused by the pressure "
"drop in the nozzle when printing in the air and a lower PA helps counteract "
"this."
msgstr ""
"桥接的压力提前值。设置为0可禁用。\n"
"\n"
"打印桥接时使用较低的PA值有助于减少桥接后立即出现的轻微挤出不足现象。"
"这是由于在空气中打印时喷嘴内的压力下降造成的，较低的PA值有助于抵消这种情况。"

msgid ""
"Default line width if other line widths are set to 0. If expressed as a %, "
"it will be computed over the nozzle diameter."
msgstr ""
"当其他线宽设置为0时的默认线宽。如果以百分比表示，则将根据喷嘴直径计算。"

msgid "Keep fan always on"
msgstr "保持风扇始终开启"

msgid ""
"Enabling this setting means that the part cooling fan will never stop "
"completely and will run at least at minimum speed to reduce the frequency of "
"starting and stopping."
msgstr ""
"启用此设置意味着零件冷却风扇将永远不会完全停止，而是至少以最低速度运行，以减少启动和停止的频率。"

msgid "Don't slow down outer walls"
msgstr "不减速外壁"

msgid ""
"If enabled, this setting will ensure external perimeters are not slowed down "
"to meet the minimum layer time. This is particularly helpful in the below "
"scenarios:\n"
"1. To avoid changes in shine when printing glossy filaments\n"
"2. To avoid changes in external wall speed which may create slight wall "
"artifacts that appear like Z banding\n"
"3. To avoid printing at speeds which cause VFAs (fine artifacts) on the "
"external walls"
msgstr ""
"如果启用，此设置将确保外部轮廓不会为了满足最小层时间而减速。这在以下场景中特别有用：\n"
"1. 避免打印光泽耗材时光泽度的变化\n"
"2. 避免外壁速度变化可能产生的类似Z纹的轻微壁部瑕疵\n"
"3. 避免以会在外壁上引起VFAs（细微瑕疵）的速度打印"

msgid "Layer time"
msgstr "层时间"

msgid ""
"Part cooling fan will be enabled for layers of which estimated time is "
"shorter than this value. Fan speed is interpolated between the minimum and "
"maximum fan speeds according to layer printing time."
msgstr ""
"对于预估时间短于此值的层，零件冷却风扇将启用。风扇速度根据层打印时间在最小和最大风扇速度之间插值。"

msgid "Default color"
msgstr "默认颜色"

msgid ""
"Default filament color.\n"
"Right click to reset value to system default."
msgstr ""
"默认耗材颜色。\n"
"右键单击可将值重置为系统默认值。"

msgid "Filament notes"
msgstr "耗材备注"

msgid "You can put your notes regarding the filament here."
msgstr "您可以在此处添加关于耗材的备注。"

msgid "Required nozzle HRC"
msgstr "所需喷嘴HRC硬度"

msgid ""
"Minimum HRC of nozzle required to print the filament. Zero means no checking "
"of nozzle's HRC."
msgstr ""
"打印该耗材所需的最小喷嘴HRC硬度。零表示不检查喷嘴HRC硬度。"

msgid ""
"This setting stands for how much volume of filament can be melted and "
"extruded per second. Printing speed is limited by max volumetric speed, in "
"case of too high and unreasonable speed setting. Can't be zero."
msgstr ""
"此设置表示每秒可以熔化和挤出的耗材体积。在速度设置过高和不合理的情况下，"
"打印速度受最大体积速度限制。不能为零。"

msgid "Filament load time"
msgstr "耗材加载时间"

msgid ""
"Time to load new filament when switch filament. It's usually applicable for "
"single-extruder multi-material machines. For tool changers or multi-tool "
"machines, it's typically 0. For statistics only."
msgstr ""
"切换耗材时加载新耗材的时间。通常适用于单挤出机多材料机器。"
"对于工具更换器或多工具机器，通常为0。仅用于统计。"

msgid "Filament unload time"
msgstr "耗材卸载时间"

msgid ""
"Time to unload old filament when switch filament. It's usually applicable "
"for single-extruder multi-material machines. For tool changers or multi-tool "
"machines, it's typically 0. For statistics only."
msgstr ""
"切换耗材时卸载旧耗材的时间。通常适用于单挤出机多材料机器。"
"对于工具更换器或多工具机器，通常为0。仅用于统计。"

msgid "Tool change time"
msgstr "工具更换时间"

msgid ""
"Time taken to switch tools. It's usually applicable for tool changers or "
"multi-tool machines. For single-extruder multi-material machines, it's "
"typically 0. For statistics only."
msgstr ""
"切换工具所需的时间。通常适用于工具更换器或多工具机器。"
"对于单挤出机多材料机器，通常为0。仅用于统计。"

msgid ""
"Filament diameter is used to calculate extrusion in G-code, so it is "
"important and should be accurate."
msgstr ""
"耗材直径用于计算G代码中的挤出量，因此很重要且应准确。"

msgid "Pellet flow coefficient"
msgstr "颗粒流量系数"

msgid ""
"Pellet flow coefficient is empirically derived and allows for volume "
"calculation for pellet printers.\n"
"\n"
"Internally it is converted to filament_diameter. All other volume "
"calculations remain the same.\n"
"\n"
"filament_diameter = sqrt( (4 * pellet_flow_coefficient) / PI )"
msgstr ""
"颗粒流量系数是通过经验得出的，用于颗粒打印机的体积计算。\n"
"\n"
"在内部它会转换为filament_diameter（耗材直径）。所有其他体积计算保持不变。\n"
"\n"
"filament_diameter = sqrt( (4 * pellet_flow_coefficient) / PI )"

msgid "Shrinkage (XY)"
msgstr "收缩率（XY）"

#, no-c-format, no-boost-format

msgid ""
"Enter the shrinkage percentage that the filament will get after cooling (94% "
"if you measure 94mm instead of 100mm). The part will be scaled in xy to "
"compensate. Only the filament used for the perimeter is taken into account.\n"
"Be sure to allow enough space between objects, as this compensation is done "
"after the checks."
msgstr ""
"输入耗材冷却后的收缩百分比（如果测量为94mm而非100mm，则输入94%）。"
"零件将在XY方向上进行缩放以补偿。仅考虑用于外壁的耗材。\n"
"请确保在对象之间留出足够空间，因为此补偿在检查之后进行。"

msgid "Shrinkage (Z)"
msgstr "收缩率（Z）"

#, no-c-format, no-boost-format

msgid ""
"Enter the shrinkage percentage that the filament will get after cooling (94% "
"if you measure 94mm instead of 100mm). The part will be scaled in Z to "
"compensate."
msgstr ""
"输入耗材冷却后的收缩百分比（如果测量为94mm而非100mm，则输入94%）。"
"零件将在Z方向上进行缩放以补偿。"

msgid "Loading speed"
msgstr "加载速度"

msgid "Speed used for loading the filament on the wipe tower."
msgstr "用于在擦拭塔上加载耗材的速度。"

msgid "Loading speed at the start"
msgstr "起始加载速度"

msgid "Speed used at the very beginning of loading phase."
msgstr "用于加载阶段最开始时速度。"

msgid "Unloading speed"
msgstr "卸载速度"

msgid ""
"Speed used for unloading the filament on the wipe tower (does not affect "
"initial part of unloading just after ramming)."
msgstr ""
"用于在擦拭塔上卸载耗材的速度（不影响顶锻后立即卸载的初始部分）。"

msgid "Unloading speed at the start"
msgstr "起始卸载速度"

msgid ""
"Speed used for unloading the tip of the filament immediately after ramming."
msgstr "用于顶锻后立即卸载耗材尖端的速度。"

msgid "Delay after unloading"
msgstr "卸载后延迟"

msgid ""
"Time to wait after the filament is unloaded. May help to get reliable tool "
"changes with flexible materials that may need more time to shrink to "
"original dimensions."
msgstr ""
"卸载耗材后等待的时间。有助于在使用柔性材料时实现可靠的工具更换，"
"柔性材料可能需要更多时间收缩回原始尺寸。"

msgid "Number of cooling moves"
msgstr "冷却移动次数"

msgid ""
"Filament is cooled by being moved back and forth in the cooling tubes. "
"Specify desired number of these moves."
msgstr "耗材通过在冷却管中来回移动进行冷却。请指定所需的移动次数。"

msgid "Stamping loading speed"
msgstr "冲压加载速度"

msgid "Speed used for stamping."
msgstr "用于冲压的速度。"

msgid "Stamping distance measured from the center of the cooling tube"
msgstr "从冷却管中心测量的冲压距离"

msgid ""
"If set to non-zero value, filament is moved toward the nozzle between the "
"individual cooling moves (\"stamping\"). This option configures how long "
"this movement should be before the filament is retracted again."
msgstr ""
"如果设置为非零值，耗材会在各次冷却移动（"冲压"）之间向喷嘴方向移动。"
"此选项设置在进行下一次回抽前该移动应持续的时间。"

msgid "Speed of the first cooling move"
msgstr "首次冷却移动速度"

msgid "Cooling moves are gradually accelerating beginning at this speed."
msgstr "冷却移动从此速度开始逐步加速。"

msgid "Minimal purge on wipe tower"
msgstr "擦拭塔最小清洗量"

msgid ""
"After a tool change, the exact position of the newly loaded filament inside "
"the nozzle may not be known, and the filament pressure is likely not yet "
"stable. Before purging the print head into an infill or a sacrificial "
"object, Snapmaker Orca will always prime this amount of material into the wipe "
"tower to produce successive infill or sacrificial object extrusions reliably."
msgstr ""
"换刀后，喷嘴内新加载耗材的精确位置可能未知，且耗材压力可能尚未稳定。"
"在向填充或牺牲对象清洗打印头之前，Snapmaker Orca 会先将此量的材料预挤出到擦拭塔上，"
"以确保后续的填充或牺牲对象挤出可靠。"

msgid "Speed of the last cooling move"
msgstr "末次冷却移动速度"

msgid "Cooling moves are gradually accelerating towards this speed."
msgstr "冷却移动逐步加速至该速度。"

msgid "Ramming parameters"
msgstr "顶出参数"

msgid ""
"This string is edited by RammingDialog and contains ramming specific "
"parameters."
msgstr "此字符串由 RammingDialog 编辑，包含顶出相关参数。"

msgid "Enable ramming for multi-tool setups"
msgstr "为多工具设置启用顶出"

msgid ""
"Perform ramming when using multi-tool printer (i.e. when the 'Single "
"Extruder Multimaterial' in Printer Settings is unchecked). When checked, a "
"small amount of filament is rapidly extruded on the wipe tower just before "
"the tool change. This option is only used when the wipe tower is enabled."
msgstr ""
"在使用多工具打印机时执行顶出（即打印机设置中的"单挤出机多材料"未勾选时）。"
"启用后，会在换刀前快速在擦拭塔上挤出少量耗材。此选项仅在启用擦拭塔时使用。"

msgid "Multi-tool ramming volume"
msgstr "多工具顶出体积"

msgid "The volume to be rammed before the tool change."
msgstr "换刀前顶出的体积。"

msgid "Multi-tool ramming flow"
msgstr "多工具顶出流量"

msgid "Flow used for ramming the filament before the tool change."
msgstr "换刀前用于顶出耗材的流量。"

msgid "Density"
msgstr "密度"

msgid "Filament density. For statistics only."
msgstr "耗材密度。仅用于统计。"

msgid "The material type of filament."
msgstr "耗材的材料类型。"

msgid "Soluble material"
msgstr "可溶性材料"

msgid ""
"Soluble material is commonly used to print supports and support interfaces."
msgstr "可溶性材料通常用于打印支撑和支撑界面。"

msgid "Support material"
msgstr "支撑材料"

msgid ""
"Support material is commonly used to print supports and support interfaces."
msgstr "支撑材料通常用于打印支撑和支撑界面。"

msgid "Softening temperature"
msgstr "软化温度"

msgid ""
"The material softens at this temperature, so when the bed temperature is "
"equal to or greater than this, it's highly recommended to open the front "
"door and/or remove the upper glass to avoid clogging."
msgstr ""
"材料在此温度下会软化，因此当热床温度达到或超过此温度时，强烈建议打开前门"
"和/或取下上盖玻璃，以避免堵塞。"

msgid "Price"
msgstr "价格"

msgid "Filament price. For statistics only."
msgstr "耗材价格。仅用于统计。"

msgid "money/kg"
msgstr "元/千克"

msgid "Vendor"
msgstr "供应商"

msgid "Vendor of filament. For show only."
msgstr "耗材供应商。仅用于展示。"

msgid "(Undefined)"
msgstr "（未定义）"

msgid "Sparse infill direction"
msgstr "稀疏填充方向"

msgid ""
"Angle for sparse infill pattern, which controls the start or main direction "
"of line."
msgstr "稀疏填充图案的角度，控制线条的起始或主要方向。"

msgid "Solid infill direction"
msgstr "实体填充方向"

msgid ""
"Angle for solid infill pattern, which controls the start or main direction "
"of line."
msgstr "实体填充图案的角度，控制线条的起始或主要方向。"

msgid "Sparse infill density"
msgstr "稀疏填充密度"

#, no-c-format, no-boost-format

msgid ""
"Density of internal sparse infill, 100% turns all sparse infill into solid "
"infill and internal solid infill pattern will be used."
msgstr ""
"内部稀疏填充的密度，100% 会将所有稀疏填充变为实体填充，"
"并使用内部实体填充图案。"

msgid "Align infill direction to model"
msgstr "填充方向与模型对齐"

msgid ""
"Aligns infill and surface fill directions to follow the model's orientation "
"on the build plate. When enabled, fill directions rotate with the model to "
"maintain optimal strength characteristics."
msgstr ""
"使填充和表面填充方向跟随模型在打印平台上的朝向。"
"启用后，填充方向将随模型旋转，以保持最佳强度特性。"

msgid "Insert solid layers"
msgstr "插入实体层"

msgid ""
"Insert solid infill at specific layers. Use N to insert every Nth layer, N#K "
"to insert K consecutive solid layers every N layers (K is optional, e.g. "
"'5#' equals '5#1'), or a comma-separated list (e.g. 1,7,9) to insert at "
"explicit layers. Layers are 1-based."
msgstr ""
"在特定层插入实体填充。使用 N 每隔 N 层插入，使用 N#K 每隔 N 层插入 K 层连续实体层"
"（K 可选，例如 '5#' 等同于 '5#1'），或使用逗号分隔列表（例如 1,7,9）在指定层插入。"
"层号从 1 开始。"

msgid "Fill Multiline"
msgstr "填充多线"

msgid ""
"Using multiple lines for the infill pattern, if supported by infill pattern."
msgstr "对填充图案使用多线（如果填充图案支持）。"

msgid "Sparse infill pattern"
msgstr "稀疏填充图案"

msgid "Line pattern for internal sparse infill."
msgstr "内部稀疏填充的线条图案。"

msgid "Zig Zag"
msgstr "锯齿形"

msgid "Cross Zag"
msgstr "交叉锯齿形"

msgid "Locked Zag"
msgstr "锁定锯齿形"

msgid "Line"
msgstr "直线"

msgid "Grid"
msgstr "网格"

msgid "Tri-hexagon"
msgstr "三角六边形"

msgid "Cubic"
msgstr "立方体"

msgid "Adaptive Cubic"
msgstr "自适应立方体"

msgid "Quarter Cubic"
msgstr "四分之一立方体"

msgid "Support Cubic"
msgstr "支撑立方体"

msgid "Lightning"
msgstr "闪电"

msgid "Honeycomb"
msgstr "蜂窝"

msgid "3D Honeycomb"
msgstr "3D蜂窝"

msgid "Lateral Honeycomb"
msgstr "横向蜂窝"

msgid "Lateral Lattice"
msgstr "横向晶格"

msgid "Cross Hatch"
msgstr "交叉影线"

msgid "TPMS-D"
msgstr "TPMS-D"

msgid "TPMS-FK"
msgstr "TPMS-FK"

msgid "Gyroid"
msgstr "Gyroid"

msgid "Lateral lattice angle 1"
msgstr "横向晶格角度1"

msgid ""
"The angle of the first set of Lateral lattice elements in the Z direction. "
"Zero is vertical."
msgstr ""
"第一组横向晶格元素在Z方向的角度。零度为垂直。"

msgid "Lateral lattice angle 2"
msgstr "横向晶格角度2"

msgid ""
"The angle of the second set of Lateral lattice elements in the Z direction. "
"Zero is vertical."
msgstr ""
"第二组横向晶格元素在Z方向的角度。零度为垂直。"

msgid "Infill overhang angle"
msgstr "填充悬垂角度"

msgid ""
"The angle of the infill angled lines. 60° will result in a pure honeycomb."
msgstr ""
"填充倾斜线条的角度。60°将生成纯蜂窝结构。"

msgid "Sparse infill anchor length"
msgstr "稀疏填充锚点长度"

msgid ""
"Connect an infill line to an internal perimeter with a short segment of an "
"additional perimeter. If expressed as percentage (example: 15%) it is "
"calculated over infill extrusion width. Snapmaker Orca tries to connect two "
"close infill lines to a short perimeter segment. If no such perimeter "
"segment shorter than infill_anchor_max is found, the infill line is "
"connected to a perimeter segment at just one side and the length of the "
"perimeter segment taken is limited to this parameter, but no longer than "
"anchor_length_max.\n"
"Set this parameter to zero to disable anchoring perimeters connected to a "
"single infill line."
msgstr ""
"使用附加外壳的短线段将填充线与内部外壳连接。如果以百分比表示（例如：15%），则按填充挤出宽度计算。Snapmaker Orca尝试将两条相邻的填充线连接到一条短外壳线段。如果未找到短于infill_anchor_max的外壳线段，则填充线仅在一侧连接到外壳线段，所采用的外壳线段长度受限于此参数，但不超过anchor_length_max。\n"
"将此参数设置为零以禁用连接到单条填充线的锚定外壳。"

msgid "0 (no open anchors)"
msgstr "0（无开放锚点）"

msgid "1000 (unlimited)"
msgstr "1000（无限制）"

msgid "Maximum length of the infill anchor"
msgstr "填充锚点最大长度"

msgid ""
"Connect an infill line to an internal perimeter with a short segment of an "
"additional perimeter. If expressed as percentage (example: 15%) it is "
"calculated over infill extrusion width. Snapmaker Orca tries to connect two "
"close infill lines to a short perimeter segment. If no such perimeter "
"segment shorter than this parameter is found, the infill line is connected "
"to a perimeter segment at just one side and the length of the perimeter "
"segment taken is limited to infill_anchor, but no longer than this "
"parameter.\n"
"If set to 0, the old algorithm for infill connection will be used, it should "
"create the same result as with 1000 & 0."
msgstr ""
"使用附加外壳的短线段将填充线与内部外壳连接。如果以百分比表示（例如：15%），则按填充挤出宽度计算。Snapmaker Orca尝试将两条相邻的填充线连接到一条短外壳线段。如果未找到短于此参数的外壳线段，则填充线仅在一侧连接到外壳线段，所采用的外壳线段长度受限于infill_anchor，但不超过此参数。\n"
"如果设置为0，则将使用旧的填充连接算法，其结果应与1000和0的组合相同。"

msgid "0 (Simple connect)"
msgstr "0（简单连接）"

msgid "Acceleration of outer walls."
msgstr "外壁加速度。"

msgid "Acceleration of inner walls."
msgstr "内壁加速度。"

msgid "Acceleration of travel moves."
msgstr "空移加速度。"

msgid ""
"Acceleration of top surface infill. Using a lower value may improve top "
"surface quality."
msgstr ""
"顶部表面填充加速度。使用较低值可改善顶部表面质量。"

msgid "Acceleration of outer wall. Using a lower value can improve quality."
msgstr "外壁加速度。使用较低值可改善质量。"

msgid ""
"Acceleration of bridges. If the value is expressed as a percentage (e.g. "
"50%), it will be calculated based on the outer wall acceleration."
msgstr ""
"桥接加速度。如果该值以百分比表示（例如：50%），则将基于外壁加速度计算。"

msgid "mm/s² or %"
msgstr "mm/s² 或 %"

msgid ""
"Acceleration of sparse infill. If the value is expressed as a percentage "
"(e.g. 100%), it will be calculated based on the default acceleration."
msgstr ""
"稀疏填充加速度。如果该值以百分比表示（例如：100%），则将基于默认加速度计算。"

msgid ""
"Acceleration of internal solid infill. If the value is expressed as a "
"percentage (e.g. 100%), it will be calculated based on the default "
"acceleration."
msgstr ""
"内部实体填充加速度。如果该值以百分比表示（例如：100%），则将基于默认加速度计算。"

msgid ""
"Acceleration of initial layer. Using a lower value can improve build plate "
"adhesion."
msgstr ""
"初始层加速度。使用较低值可改善打印平台附着力。"

msgid "Enable accel_to_decel"
msgstr "启用accel_to_decel"

msgid "Klipper's max_accel_to_decel will be adjusted automatically."
msgstr "Klipper的max_accel_to_decel将自动调整。"

msgid "accel_to_decel"
msgstr "accel_to_decel"

#, c-format, boost-format

msgid ""
"Klipper's max_accel_to_decel will be adjusted to this %% of acceleration."
msgstr "Klipper的max_accel_to_decel将根据加速度的此百分比进行调整。"

msgid "Default jerk."
msgstr "默认Jerk值。"

msgid ""
"Marlin Firmware Junction Deviation (replaces the traditional XY Jerk "
"setting)."
msgstr "Marlin固件Junction Deviation（取代传统的XY Jerk设置）。"

msgid "Jerk of outer walls."
msgstr "外壳Jerk值。"

msgid "Jerk of inner walls."
msgstr "内壁Jerk值。"

msgid "Jerk for top surface."
msgstr "顶面Jerk值。"

msgid "Jerk for infill."
msgstr "填充Jerk值。"

msgid "Jerk for initial layer."
msgstr "首层Jerk值。"

msgid "Jerk for travel."
msgstr "空移Jerk值。"

msgid ""
"Line width of initial layer. If expressed as a %, it will be computed over "
"the nozzle diameter."
msgstr "首层线宽。如果以%表示，则将根据喷嘴直径计算。"

msgid "Initial layer height"
msgstr "首层高度"

msgid ""
"Height of initial layer. Making initial layer height to be thick slightly "
"can improve build plate adhesion."
msgstr "首层的高度。适当增加首层高度可以提高热床附着力。"

msgid "Speed of initial layer except the solid infill part."
msgstr "除实体填充部分外的首层打印速度。"

msgid "Initial layer infill"
msgstr "首层填充"

msgid "Speed of solid infill part of initial layer."
msgstr "首层实体填充部分的打印速度。"

msgid "Initial layer travel speed"
msgstr "首层空移速度"

msgid "Travel speed of initial layer."
msgstr "首层的空移速度。"

#, fuzzy

msgid "Number of slow layers"
msgstr "慢速层数"

msgid ""
"The first few layers are printed slower than normal. The speed is gradually "
"increased in a linear fashion over the specified number of layers."
msgstr "前几层的打印速度比正常慢。速度在指定的层数内线性逐渐增加。"

msgid "Initial layer nozzle temperature"
msgstr "首层喷嘴温度"

msgid "Nozzle temperature for printing initial layer when using this filament."
msgstr "使用此耗材打印首层时的喷嘴温度。"

msgid "Full fan speed at layer"
msgstr "风扇全速层"

msgid ""
"Fan speed will be ramped up linearly from zero at layer "
"\"close_fan_the_first_x_layers\" to maximum at layer "
"\"full_fan_speed_layer\". \"full_fan_speed_layer\" will be ignored if lower "
"than \"close_fan_the_first_x_layers\", in which case the fan will be running "
"at maximum allowed speed at layer \"close_fan_the_first_x_layers\" + 1."
msgstr ""
"风扇速度将从\"close_fan_the_first_x_layers\"层的零开始线性增加到"
"\"full_fan_speed_layer\"层的最大值。如果\"full_fan_speed_layer\"低于"
"\"close_fan_the_first_x_layers\"，则将被忽略，此时风扇将在"
"\"close_fan_the_first_x_layers\" + 1层以允许的最大速度运行。"

msgid "layer"
msgstr "层"

msgid "Support interface fan speed"
msgstr "支撑界面风扇速度"

msgid ""
"This part cooling fan speed is applied when printing support interfaces. "
"Setting this parameter to a higher than regular speed reduces the layer "
"binding strength between supports and the supported part, making them easier "
"to separate.\n"
"Set to -1 to disable it.\n"
"This setting is overridden by disable_fan_first_layers."
msgstr ""
"打印支撑界面时应用此部件冷却风扇速度。将此参数设置为高于常规速度会降低"
"支撑与被支撑部件之间的层结合强度，使其更易分离。\n"
"设置为-1以禁用。\n"
"此设置会被disable_fan_first_layers覆盖。"

msgid "Internal bridges fan speed"
msgstr "内部桥接风扇速度"

msgid ""
"The part cooling fan speed used for all internal bridges. Set to -1 to use "
"the overhang fan speed settings instead.\n"
"\n"
"Reducing the internal bridges fan speed, compared to your regular fan speed, "
"can help reduce part warping due to excessive cooling applied over a large "
"surface for a prolonged period of time."
msgstr ""
"所有内部桥接使用的部件冷却风扇速度。设置为-1则改用悬垂风扇速度设置。\n"
"\n"
"与常规风扇速度相比，降低内部桥接风扇速度有助于减少因长时间大面积过度冷却"
"导致的部件翘曲。"

msgid "Ironing fan speed"
msgstr "熨烫风扇速度"

msgid ""
"This part cooling fan speed is applied when ironing. Setting this parameter "
"to a lower than regular speed reduces possible nozzle clogging due to the "
"low volumetric flow rate, making the interface smoother.\n"
"Set to -1 to disable it."
msgstr ""
"熨烫时应用此部件冷却风扇速度。将此参数设置为低于常规速度可减少因低体积"
"流量率可能导致的喷嘴堵塞，使表面更光滑。\n"
"设置为-1以禁用。"

msgid ""
"Randomly jitter while printing the wall, so that the surface has a rough "
"look. This setting controls the fuzzy position."
msgstr "打印壁时随机抖动，使表面呈现粗糙外观。此设置控制毛茸位置。"

msgid "Contour"
msgstr "轮廓"

msgid "Contour and hole"
msgstr "轮廓和孔"

msgid "All walls"
msgstr "所有壁"

msgid "Fuzzy skin thickness"
msgstr "毛茸厚度"

msgid ""
"The width within which to jitter. It's advised to be below outer wall line "
"width."
msgstr "抖动的宽度范围。建议低于外壳线宽。"

msgid "Fuzzy skin point distance"
msgstr "毛茸点间距"

msgid ""
"The average distance between the random points introduced on each line "
"segment."
msgstr "每个线段上引入的随机点之间的平均距离。"

msgid "Apply fuzzy skin to first layer"
msgstr "对首层应用毛茸效果"

msgid "Whether to apply fuzzy skin on the first layer."
msgstr "是否在首层应用毛茸效果。"

msgid "Fuzzy skin generator mode"
msgstr "毛茸生成模式"

#, c-format, boost-format

msgid ""
"Fuzzy skin generation mode. Works only with Arachne!\n"
"Displacement: Сlassic mode when the pattern is formed by shifting the nozzle "
"sideways from the original path.\n"
"Extrusion: The mode when the pattern formed by the amount of extruded "
"plastic. This is the fast and straight algorithm without unnecessary nozzle "
"shake that gives a smooth pattern. But it is more useful for forming loose "
"walls in the entire they array.\n"
"Combined: Joint mode [Displacement] + [Extrusion]. The appearance of the "
"walls is similar to [Displacement] Mode, but it leaves no pores between the "
"perimeters.\n"
"\n"
"Attention! The [Extrusion] and [Combined] modes works only the "
"fuzzy_skin_thickness parameter not more than the thickness of printed loop. "
"At the same time, the width of the extrusion for a particular layer should "
"also not be below a certain level. It is usually equal 15-25%% of a layer "
"height. Therefore, the maximum fuzzy skin thickness with a perimeter width "
"of 0.4 mm and a layer height of 0.2 mm will be 0.4-(0.2*0.25)=±0.35mm! If "
"you enter a higher parameter than this, the error Flow::spacing() will "
"displayed, and the model will not be sliced. You can choose this number "
"until this error is repeated."
msgstr ""
"毛茸生成模式。仅适用于Arachne！\n"
"位移：经典模式，通过将喷嘴从原始路径侧向移动形成图案。\n"
"挤出：通过挤出塑料量形成图案的模式。这是一种快速直接的算法，无需不必要的"
"喷嘴抖动，即可产生平滑图案。但它更适合在整个阵列中形成松散壁。\n"
"组合：合并模式[位移] + [挤出]。壁的外观类似于[位移]模式，但在外壳之间"
"不留孔隙。\n"
"\n"
"注意！[挤出]和[组合]模式仅在fuzzy_skin_thickness参数不超过打印环厚度时"
"有效。同时，特定层的挤出宽度也不应低于一定水平。通常等于层高的15-25%%。"
"因此，在外壳宽度为0.4mm、层高为0.2mm的情况下，最大毛茸厚度为"
"0.4-(0.2*0.25)=±0.35mm！如果输入高于此值，将显示错误Flow::spacing()，"
"模型将无法切片。您可以调整此数值直到错误消失。"

msgid "Displacement"
msgstr "位移"

msgid "Extrusion"
msgstr "挤出"

msgid "Combined"
msgstr "组合"

msgid "Fuzzy skin noise type"
msgstr "模糊表皮噪声类型"

msgid ""
"Noise type to use for fuzzy skin generation:\n"
"Classic: Classic uniform random noise.\n"
"Perlin: Perlin noise, which gives a more consistent texture.\n"
"Billow: Similar to perlin noise, but clumpier.\n"
"Ridged Multifractal: Ridged noise with sharp, jagged features. Creates "
"marble-like textures.\n"
"Voronoi: Divides the surface into voronoi cells, and displaces each one by a "
"random amount. Creates a patchwork texture."
msgstr ""
"用于生成模糊表皮的噪声类型：\n"
"经典：经典均匀随机噪声。\n"
"柏林：柏林噪声，提供更一致的纹理。\n"
"翻滚：类似于柏林噪声，但更块状。\n"
"脊状多重分形：具有尖锐锯齿特征的脊状噪声，产生大"
"理石般的纹理。\n"
"沃罗诺伊：将表面分割成沃罗诺伊单元格，并对每个单元格进行随机位移，产生"
"拼布纹理。"

msgid "Classic"
msgstr "经典"

msgid "Perlin"
msgstr "柏林"

msgid "Billow"
msgstr "翻滚"

msgid "Ridged Multifractal"
msgstr "脊状多重分形"

msgid "Voronoi"
msgstr "沃罗诺伊"

msgid "Fuzzy skin feature size"
msgstr "模糊表皮特征尺寸"

msgid ""
"The base size of the coherent noise features, in mm. Higher values will "
"result in larger features."
msgstr ""
"相干噪声特征的基础尺寸，单位为毫米。值越大，特征越大。"

msgid "Fuzzy Skin Noise Octaves"
msgstr "模糊表皮噪声倍频程"

msgid ""
"The number of octaves of coherent noise to use. Higher values increase the "
"detail of the noise, but also increase computation time."
msgstr ""
"要使用的相干噪声倍频程数。值越大，噪声细节越丰富，但计算时间也会增加。"

msgid "Fuzzy skin noise persistence"
msgstr "模糊表皮噪声持久性"

msgid ""
"The decay rate for higher octaves of the coherent noise. Lower values will "
"result in smoother noise."
msgstr ""
"相干噪声较高倍频程的衰减率。值越低，噪声越平滑。"

msgid "Filter out tiny gaps"
msgstr "过滤微小间隙"

msgid "Layers and Perimeters"
msgstr "层与外壳"

msgid ""
"Don't print gap fill with a length is smaller than the threshold specified "
"(in mm). This setting applies to top, bottom and solid infill and, if using "
"the classic perimeter generator, to wall gap fill."
msgstr ""
"不打印长度小于指定阈值（毫米）的间隙填充。此设置适用于顶部、底部和实体填充，"
"如果使用经典外壳生成器，也适用于壁间隙填充。"

msgid ""
"Speed of gap infill. Gap usually has irregular line width and should be "
"printed more slowly."
msgstr ""
"间隙填充的速度。间隙通常具有不规则的线宽，应更慢地打印。"

msgid "Precise Z height"
msgstr "精确Z高度"

msgid ""
"Enable this to get precise z height of object after slicing. It will get the "
"precise object height by fine-tuning the layer heights of the last few "
"layers. Note that this is an experimental parameter."
msgstr ""
"启用此选项可在切片后获取物体的精确Z高度。它通过微调最后几层的层高来获取精确"
"的物体高度。请注意，这是一个实验性参数。"

msgid "Arc fitting"
msgstr "弧线拟合"

msgid ""
"Enable this to get a G-code file which has G2 and G3 moves. The fitting "
"tolerance is same as the resolution.\n"
"\n"
"Note: For Klipper machines, this option is recommended to be disabled. "
"Klipper does not benefit from arc commands as these are split again into "
"line segments by the firmware. This results in a reduction in surface "
"quality as line segments are converted to arcs by the slicer and then back "
"to line segments by the firmware."
msgstr ""
"启用此选项可生成包含G2和G3移动的G代码文件。拟合公差与分辨率相同。\n"
"\n"
"注意：对于Klipper机器，建议禁用此选项。Klipper不会从圆弧命令中受益，"
"因为这些命令会被固件再次分割成线段。这会导致表面质量下降，因为线段被切片"
"软件转换为圆弧，然后又被固件转换回线段。"

msgid "Add line number"
msgstr "添加行号"

msgid ""
"Enable this to add line number(Nx) at the beginning of each G-code line."
msgstr ""
"启用此选项可在每行G代码的开头添加行号(Nx)。"

msgid "Scan first layer"
msgstr "扫描第一层"

msgid ""
"Enable this to enable the camera on printer to check the quality of first "
"layer."
msgstr ""
"启用此选项可使用打印机上的摄像头检查第一层的质量。"

msgid "Nozzle type"
msgstr "喷嘴类型"

msgid ""
"The metallic material of nozzle. This determines the abrasive resistance of "
"nozzle, and what kind of filament can be printed."
msgstr ""
"喷嘴的金属材料。这决定了喷嘴的耐磨性以及可以打印的耗材类型。"

msgid "Undefine"
msgstr "未定义"

msgid "Hardened steel"
msgstr "硬化钢"

msgid "Stainless steel"
msgstr "不锈钢"

msgid "Brass"
msgstr "黄铜"

msgid "Nozzle HRC"
msgstr "喷嘴HRC硬度"

msgid ""
"The nozzle's hardness. Zero means no checking for nozzle's hardness during "
"slicing."
msgstr ""
"喷嘴的硬度。零表示切片时不检查喷嘴硬度。"

msgid "HRC"
msgstr "HRC"

msgid "Printer structure"
msgstr "打印机结构"

msgid "The physical arrangement and components of a printing device."
msgstr "打印设备的物理布局和组件。"

msgid "CoreXY"
msgstr "CoreXY"

msgid "I3"
msgstr "I3"

msgid "Hbot"
msgstr "Hbot"

msgid "Delta"
msgstr "Delta"

msgid "Best object position"
msgstr "最佳物体位置"

msgid "Best auto arranging position in range [0,1] w.r.t. bed shape."
msgstr "相对于热床形状的[0,1]范围内最佳自动排列位置。"

msgid ""
"Enable this option if machine has auxiliary part cooling fan. G-code "
"command: M106 P2 S(0-255)."
msgstr ""
"如果机器有辅助零件冷却风扇，请启用此选项。G代码命令：M106 P2 S(0-255)。"

msgid ""
"Start the fan this number of seconds earlier than its target start time (you "
"can use fractional seconds). It assumes infinite acceleration for this time "
"estimation, and will only take into account G1 and G0 moves (arc fitting is "
"unsupported).\n"
"It won't move fan commands from custom G-code (they act as a sort of "
"'barrier').\n"
"It won't move fan commands into the start G-code if the 'only custom start G-"
"code' is activated.\n"
"Use 0 to deactivate."
msgstr ""
"比目标启动时间提前这么多秒启动风扇（可以使用小数秒）。此时间估算假设无限加速"
"度，并且仅考虑G1和G0移动（不支持弧线拟合）。\n"
"它不会移动自定义G代码中的风扇命令（这些命令起到一种'屏障'作用）。\n"
"如果启用了'仅自定义启动G代码'，它不会将风扇命令移入启动G代码。\n"
"输入0以禁用。"

msgid "Only overhangs"
msgstr "仅悬垂"

msgid "Will only take into account the delay for the cooling of overhangs."
msgstr "仅考虑悬垂冷却的延迟。"

msgid "Fan kick-start time"
msgstr "风扇启动时间"

msgid ""
"Emit a max fan speed command for this amount of seconds before reducing to "
"target speed to kick-start the cooling fan.\n"
"This is useful for fans where a low PWM/power may be insufficient to get the "
"fan started spinning from a stop, or to get the fan up to speed faster.\n"
"Set to 0 to deactivate."
msgstr ""
"在此秒数内发出最大风扇转速指令，然后降低至目标转速，以启动冷却风扇。\n"
"这对于某些风扇很有用，因为较低的PWM/功率可能不足以让风扇从停止状态开始旋"
"转，或者有助于风扇更快达到转速。\n"
"设置为0以禁用。"

msgid "Time cost"
msgstr "时间成本"

msgid "The printer cost per hour."
msgstr "打印机每小时成本。"

msgid "money/h"
msgstr "元/小时"

msgid "Support control chamber temperature"
msgstr "支持控制腔室温度"

msgid ""
"This option is enabled if machine support controlling chamber temperature\n"
"G-code command: M141 S(0-255)"
msgstr ""
"如果机器支持控制腔室温度，则启用此选项\n"
"G代码命令：M141 S(0-255)"

msgid "Support air filtration"
msgstr "支持空气过滤"

msgid ""
"Enable this if printer support air filtration\n"
"G-code command: M106 P3 S(0-255)"
msgstr ""
"如果打印机支持空气过滤，则启用此选项\n"
"G代码命令：M106 P3 S(0-255)"

msgid "G-code flavor"
msgstr "G代码风格"

msgid "What kind of G-code the printer is compatible with."
msgstr "打印机兼容的G代码类型。"

msgid "Klipper"
msgstr "Klipper"

msgid "Pellet Modded Printer"
msgstr "颗粒料改装打印机"

msgid "Enable this option if your printer uses pellets instead of filaments."
msgstr "如果您的打印机使用颗粒料而不是耗材，请启用此选项。"

msgid "Support multi bed types"
msgstr "支持多种热床类型"

msgid "Enable this option if you want to use multiple bed types."
msgstr "如果您想使用多种热床类型，请启用此选项。"

msgid "Label objects"
msgstr "标记对象"

msgid ""
"Enable this to add comments into the G-code labeling print moves with what "
"object they belong to, which is useful for the Octoprint CancelObject "
"plugin. This settings is NOT compatible with Single Extruder Multi Material "
"setup and Wipe into Object / Wipe into Infill."
msgstr ""
"启用此选项可在G代码中添加注释，标记打印移动属于哪个对象，这对于"
"Octoprint CancelObject插件很有用。此设置与单挤出机多材料设置以及擦拭到对象"
"/擦拭到填充不兼容。"

msgid "Exclude objects"
msgstr "排除对象"

msgid "Enable this option to add EXCLUDE OBJECT command in G-code."
msgstr "启用此选项可在G代码中添加EXCLUDE OBJECT命令。"

msgid "Verbose G-code"
msgstr "详细G代码"

msgid ""
"Enable this to get a commented G-code file, with each line explained by a "
"descriptive text. If you print from SD card, the additional weight of the "
"file could make your firmware slow down."
msgstr ""
"启用此选项可生成带有注释的G代码文件，每行都有描述性文本解释。"
"如果从SD卡打印，文件体积增大会导致固件运行变慢。"

msgid "Infill combination"
msgstr "填充组合"

msgid ""
"Automatically Combine sparse infill of several layers to print together to "
"reduce time. Wall is still printed with original layer height."
msgstr ""
"自动将多层的稀疏填充组合在一起打印，以减少时间。外壳仍以原始层高打印。"

msgid "Infill shift step"
msgstr "填充偏移步长"

msgid ""
"This parameter adds a slight displacement to each layer of infill to create "
"a cross texture."
msgstr ""
"此参数为每层填充添加轻微偏移，以创建交叉纹理。"

msgid "Sparse infill rotation template"
msgstr "稀疏填充旋转模板"

msgid ""
"Rotate the sparse infill direction per layer using a template of angles. "
"Enter comma-separated degrees (e.g., '0,30,60,90'). Angles are applied in "
"order by layer and repeat when the list ends. Advanced syntax is supported: "
"'+5' rotates +5° every layer; '+5#5' rotates +5° every 5 layers. See the "
"Wiki for details. When a template is set, the standard infill direction "
"setting is ignored. Note: some infill patterns (e.g., Gyroid) control "
"rotation themselves; use with care."
msgstr ""
"使用角度模板逐层旋转稀疏填充方向。输入以逗号分隔的角度值（例如"
"'0,30,60,90'）。角度按层顺序应用，列表结束后重复。支持高级语法："
"'+5'表示每层旋转+5°；'+5#5'表示每5层旋转+5°。详情请参阅Wiki。"
"设置模板后，标准填充方向设置将被忽略。注意：某些填充图案"
"（如Gyroid）自身控制旋转；请谨慎使用。"

msgid "°"
msgstr "°"

msgid "Solid infill rotation template"
msgstr "实体填充旋转模板"

msgid ""
"This parameter adds a rotation of solid infill direction to each layer "
"according to the specified template. The template is a comma-separated list "
"of angles in degrees, e.g. '0,90'. The first angle is applied to the first "
"layer, the second angle to the second layer, and so on. If there are more "
"layers than angles, the angles will be repeated. Note that not all solid "
"infill patterns support rotation."
msgstr ""
"此参数根据指定模板为每层实体填充方向添加旋转。模板是以逗号分隔的角度值"
"（度），例如'0,90'。第一个角度应用于第一层，第二个角度应用于第二层，"
"以此类推。如果层数多于角度数，角度将重复。请注意，并非所有实体填充"
"图案都支持旋转。"

msgid "Skeleton infill density"
msgstr "骨架填充密度"

msgid ""
"The remaining part of the model contour after removing a certain depth from "
"the surface is called the skeleton. This parameter is used to adjust the "
"density of this section. When two regions have the same sparse infill "
"settings but different skeleton densities, their skeleton areas will develop "
"overlapping sections. Default is as same as infill density."
msgstr ""
"从表面移除一定深度后剩下的模型轮廓部分称为骨架。此参数用于调整该区域的"
"密度。当两个区域具有相同的稀疏填充设置但骨架密度不同时，它们的骨架区域"
"将产生重叠部分。默认值与填充密度相同。"

msgid "Skin infill density"
msgstr "表层填充密度"

msgid ""
"The portion of the model's outer surface within a certain depth range is "
"called the skin. This parameter is used to adjust the density of this "
"section. When two regions have the same sparse infill settings but different "
"skin densities, this area will not be split into two separate regions. "
"Default is as same as infill density."
msgstr ""
"模型外表面在一定深度范围内的部分称为表层。此参数用于调整该区域的密度。"
"当两个区域具有相同的稀疏填充设置但表层密度不同时，该区域不会分割成"
"两个独立区域。默认值与填充密度相同。"

msgid "Skin infill depth"
msgstr "表层填充深度"

msgid "The parameter sets the depth of skin."
msgstr "此参数设置表层的深度。"

msgid "Infill lock depth"
msgstr "填充锁定深度"

msgid "The parameter sets the overlapping depth between the interior and skin."
msgstr "此参数设置内部与表层之间的重叠深度。"

msgid "Skin line width"
msgstr "表层线宽"

msgid "Adjust the line width of the selected skin paths."
msgstr "调整所选表层路径的线宽。"

msgid "Skeleton line width"
msgstr "骨架线宽"

msgid "Adjust the line width of the selected skeleton paths."
msgstr "调整所选骨架路径的线宽。"

msgid "Symmetric infill Y axis"
msgstr "对称填充Y轴"

msgid ""
"If the model has two parts that are symmetric about the Y axis, and you want "
"these parts to have symmetric textures, please click this option on one of "
"the parts."
msgstr ""
"如果模型有两个关于Y轴对称的部分，并且您希望这些部分具有对称的纹理，请点"
"击其中一个部分的此选项。"

msgid "Infill combination - Max layer height"
msgstr "填充组合 - 最大层高"

msgid ""
"Maximum layer height for the combined sparse infill.\n"
"\n"
"Set it to 0 or 100% to use the nozzle diameter (for maximum reduction in "
"print time) or a value of ~80% to maximize sparse infill strength.\n"
"\n"
"The number of layers over which infill is combined is derived by dividing "
"this value with the layer height and rounded down to the nearest decimal.\n"
"\n"
"Use either absolute mm values (eg. 0.32mm for a 0.4mm nozzle) or % values "
"(eg 80%). This value must not be larger than the nozzle diameter."
msgstr ""
"组合稀疏填充的最大层高。\n"
"\n"
"设置为0或100%则使用喷嘴直径（最大程度减少打印时间），或设置为约80%以最大"
"化稀疏填充强度。\n"
"\n"
"填充组合的层数通过将该值除以层高并向下舍入到最接近的小数位得出。\n"
"\n"
"可使用绝对毫米值（例如0.4mm喷嘴的0.32mm）或百分比值（例如80%）。该值不得"
"大于喷嘴直径。"

msgid "Filament to print internal sparse infill."
msgstr "打印内部稀疏填充的耗材。"

msgid ""
"Line width of internal sparse infill. If expressed as a %, it will be "
"computed over the nozzle diameter."
msgstr ""
"内部稀疏填充的线宽。如果以百分比表示，将基于喷嘴直径计算。"

msgid "Infill/Wall overlap"
msgstr "填充/外壳重叠"

#, no-c-format, no-boost-format

msgid ""
"Infill area is enlarged slightly to overlap with wall for better bonding. "
"The percentage value is relative to line width of sparse infill. Set this "
"value to ~10-15% to minimize potential over extrusion and accumulation of "
"material resulting in rough top surfaces."
msgstr ""
"填充区域略微扩大以与外壳重叠，实现更好的结合。百分比值相对于稀疏填充的线"
"宽。设置该值为约10-15%以最大程度减少潜在的过度挤出和材料堆积，避免导致顶"
"部表面粗糙。"

msgid "Top/Bottom solid infill/wall overlap"
msgstr "顶部/底部实体填充/外壳重叠"

#, no-c-format, no-boost-format

msgid ""
"Top solid infill area is enlarged slightly to overlap with wall for better "
"bonding and to minimize the appearance of pinholes where the top infill "
"meets the walls. A value of 25-30% is a good starting point, minimizing the "
"appearance of pinholes. The percentage value is relative to line width of "
"sparse infill."
msgstr ""
"顶部实体填充区域略微扩大以与外壳重叠，实现更好的结合并最大程度减少顶部填"
"充与外壳交接处出现针孔。25-30%是一个良好的起始值，可最大程度减少针孔出"
"现。百分比值相对于稀疏填充的线宽。"

msgid "Speed of internal sparse infill."
msgstr "内部稀疏填充速度。"

msgid "Inherits profile"
msgstr "继承配置文件"

msgid "Name of parent profile."
msgstr "父配置文件的名称。"

msgid "Interface shells"
msgstr "界面外壳"

msgid ""
"Force the generation of solid shells between adjacent materials/volumes. "
"Useful for multi-extruder prints with translucent materials or manual "
"soluble support material."
msgstr ""
"强制在相邻材料/体积之间生成实体外壳。适用于使用半透明材料的多挤出机打印或"
"手动可溶性支撑材料。"

msgid "Maximum width of a segmented region"
msgstr "分段区域的最大宽度"

msgid ""
"Maximum width of a segmented region. Zero disables this feature."
msgstr ""
"分段区域的最大宽度。设置为零将禁用此功能。"

msgid "Interlocking depth of a segmented region"
msgstr "分段区域的互锁深度"

msgid ""
"Interlocking depth of a segmented region. It will be ignored if "
"\"mmu_segmented_region_max_width\" is zero or if "
"\"mmu_segmented_region_interlocking_depth\" is bigger than "
"\"mmu_segmented_region_max_width\". Zero disables this feature."
msgstr ""
"分段区域的互锁深度。如果\"mmu_segmented_region_max_width\"为零或"
"\"mmu_segmented_region_interlocking_depth\"大于"
"\"mmu_segmented_region_max_width\"，则此值将被忽略。设置为零将禁用此功能。"

msgid "Use beam interlocking"
msgstr "使用梁式互锁"

msgid ""
"Generate interlocking beam structure at the locations where different "
"filaments touch. This improves the adhesion between filaments, especially "
"models printed in different materials."
msgstr ""
"在不同耗材接触的位置生成互锁梁结构。这有助于改善耗材之间的粘附力，特别是"
"在使用不同材料打印的模型中。"

msgid "Interlocking beam width"
msgstr "互锁梁宽度"

msgid "The width of the interlocking structure beams."
msgstr "互锁结构梁的宽度。"

msgid "Interlocking direction"
msgstr "互锁方向"

msgid "Orientation of interlock beams."
msgstr "互锁梁的方向。"

msgid "Interlocking beam layers"
msgstr "互锁梁层数"

msgid ""
"The height of the beams of the interlocking structure, measured in number of "
"layers. Less layers is stronger, but more prone to defects."
msgstr ""
"互锁结构梁的高度，以层数计。层数越少越牢固，但更容易出现缺陷。"

msgid "Interlocking depth"
msgstr "互锁深度"

msgid ""
"The distance from the boundary between filaments to generate interlocking "
"structure, measured in cells. Too few cells will result in poor adhesion."
msgstr ""
"从耗材之间边界生成互锁结构的距离，以单元格数计。单元格过少会导致粘附不"
"良。"

msgid "Interlocking boundary avoidance"
msgstr "互锁边界回避"

msgid ""
"The distance from the outside of a model where interlocking structures will "
"not be generated, measured in cells."
msgstr ""
"从模型外部开始不生成互锁结构的距离，以单元格数计。"

msgid "Ironing Type"
msgstr "熨烫类型"

msgid ""
"Ironing is using small flow to print on same height of surface again to make "
"flat surface more smooth. This setting controls which layer being ironed"
msgstr ""
"熨烫是通过小流量在同一高度表面上再次打印，使平坦表面更加光滑。此设置控制"
"哪些层会被熨烫。"

msgid "No ironing"
msgstr "不熨烫"

msgid "Top surfaces"
msgstr "顶部表面"

msgid "Topmost surface"
msgstr "最顶层表面"

msgid "All solid layer"
msgstr "所有实体层"

msgid "Ironing Pattern"
msgstr "熨烫图案"

msgid "The pattern that will be used when ironing."
msgstr "熨烫时使用的图案。"

msgid "Ironing flow"
msgstr "熨烫流量"

msgid ""
"The amount of material to extrude during ironing. Relative to flow of normal "
"layer height. Too high value results in overextrusion on the surface."
msgstr ""
"熨烫期间挤出的材料量。相对于正常层高的流量。值过高会导致表面过度挤出。"

msgid "Ironing line spacing"
msgstr "熨烫线间距"

msgid "The distance between the lines of ironing."
msgstr "熨烫线之间的距离。"

msgid "Ironing inset"
msgstr "熨烫内缩"

msgid ""
"The distance to keep from the edges. A value of 0 sets this to half of the "
"nozzle diameter."
msgstr ""
"距边缘保持的距离。设置为0则将该值设为喷嘴直径的一半。"

msgid "Ironing speed"
msgstr "熨烫速度"

msgid "Print speed of ironing lines."
msgstr "熨烫线条的打印速度。"

msgid "Ironing angle"
msgstr "熨烫角度"

msgid ""
"The angle ironing is done at. A negative number disables this function and "
"uses the default method."
msgstr ""
"熨烫角度。负数将禁用此功能并使用默认方法。"

msgid "This G-code is inserted at every layer change after the Z lift."
msgstr "此G代码将在每次层切换且Z轴抬升后插入。"

msgid "Supports silent mode"
msgstr "支持静音模式"

msgid ""
"Whether the machine supports silent mode in which machine use lower "
"acceleration to print."
msgstr ""
"机器是否支持静音模式，在静音模式下机器使用较低的加速度进行打印。"

msgid "Emit limits to G-code"
msgstr "将限制输出到G代码"

msgid "Machine limits"
msgstr "机器限制"

msgid ""
"If enabled, the machine limits will be emitted to G-code file.\n"
"This option will be ignored if the G-code flavor is set to Klipper."
msgstr ""
"如果启用，机器限制将输出到G代码文件中。\n"
"如果G代码风格设置为Klipper，则此选项将被忽略。"

msgid ""
"This G-code will be used as a code for the pause print. Users can insert "
"pause G-code in the G-code viewer."
msgstr ""
"此G代码将用作暂停打印的代码。用户可以在G代码查看器中插入暂停G代码。"

msgid "This G-code will be used as a custom code."
msgstr "此G代码将用作自定义代码。"

msgid "Small area flow compensation (beta)"
msgstr "小面积流量补偿（测试版）"

msgid "Enable flow compensation for small infill areas."
msgstr "为小面积填充区域启用流量补偿。"

msgid "Flow Compensation Model"
msgstr "流量补偿模型"

msgid ""
"Flow Compensation Model, used to adjust the flow for small infill areas. The "
"model is expressed as a comma separated pair of values for extrusion length "
"and flow correction factor. Each pair is on a separate line, followed by a "
"semicolon, in the following format: \"1.234, 5.678;\""
msgstr ""
"流量补偿模型，用于调整小面积填充区域的流量。该模型以逗号分隔的值对表示，分别对应挤出长度"
"和流量修正系数。每对值独占一行，后跟分号，格式如下：\"1.234, 5.678;\""

msgid "Maximum speed X"
msgstr "最大速度 X"

msgid "Maximum speed Y"
msgstr "最大速度 Y"

msgid "Maximum speed Z"
msgstr "最大速度 Z"

msgid "Maximum speed E"
msgstr "最大速度 E"

msgid "Maximum X speed"
msgstr "最大X速度"

msgid "Maximum Y speed"
msgstr "最大Y速度"

msgid "Maximum Z speed"
msgstr "最大Z速度"

msgid "Maximum E speed"
msgstr "最大E速度"

msgid "Maximum acceleration X"
msgstr "最大加速度 X"

msgid "Maximum acceleration Y"
msgstr "最大加速度 Y"

msgid "Maximum acceleration Z"
msgstr "最大加速度 Z"

msgid "Maximum acceleration E"
msgstr "最大加速度 E"

msgid "Maximum acceleration of the X axis"
msgstr "X轴最大加速度"

msgid "Maximum acceleration of the Y axis"
msgstr "Y轴最大加速度"

msgid "Maximum acceleration of the Z axis"
msgstr "Z轴最大加速度"

msgid "Maximum acceleration of the E axis"
msgstr "E轴最大加速度"

msgid "Maximum jerk X"
msgstr "最大瞬时速度变化率 X"

msgid "Maximum jerk Y"
msgstr "最大瞬时速度变化率 Y"

msgid "Maximum jerk Z"
msgstr "最大瞬时速度变化率 Z"

msgid "Maximum jerk E"
msgstr "最大瞬时速度变化率 E"

msgid "Maximum jerk of the X axis"
msgstr "X轴最大瞬时速度变化率"

msgid "Maximum jerk of the Y axis"
msgstr "Y轴最大瞬时速度变化率"

msgid "Maximum jerk of the Z axis"
msgstr "Z轴最大瞬时速度变化率"

msgid "Maximum jerk of the E axis"
msgstr "E轴最大瞬时速度变化率"

msgid "Maximum Junction Deviation"
msgstr "最大节点偏差"

msgid ""
"Maximum junction deviation (M205 J, only apply if JD > 0 for Marlin Firmware)"
msgstr ""
"最大节点偏差（M205 J，仅当JD > 0时适用于Marlin固件）"

msgid "Minimum speed for extruding"
msgstr "最小挤出速度"

msgid "Minimum speed for extruding (M205 S)"
msgstr "最小挤出速度（M205 S）"

msgid "Minimum travel speed"
msgstr "最小移动速度"

msgid "Minimum travel speed (M205 T)"
msgstr "最小移动速度 (M205 T)"

msgid "Maximum acceleration for extruding"
msgstr "挤出最大加速度"

msgid "Maximum acceleration for extruding (M204 P)"
msgstr "挤出最大加速度 (M204 P)"

msgid "Maximum acceleration for retracting"
msgstr "回抽最大加速度"

msgid "Maximum acceleration for retracting (M204 R)"
msgstr "回抽最大加速度 (M204 R)"

msgid "Maximum acceleration for travel"
msgstr "移动最大加速度"

msgid "Maximum acceleration for travel (M204 T), it only applies to Marlin 2."
msgstr "移动最大加速度 (M204 T)，仅适用于 Marlin 2。"

msgid "Resonance avoidance"
msgstr "共振规避"

msgid ""
"By reducing the speed of the outer wall to avoid the resonance zone of the "
"printer, ringing on the surface of the model are avoided.\n"
"Please turn this option off when testing ringing."
msgstr ""
"通过降低外壳速度以避免打印机的共振区域，从而避免模型表面的振纹。\n"
"测试振纹时请关闭此选项。"

msgid "Min"
msgstr "最小"

msgid "Minimum speed of resonance avoidance."
msgstr "共振规避的最小速度。"

msgid "Max"
msgstr "最大"

msgid "Maximum speed of resonance avoidance."
msgstr "共振规避的最大速度。"

msgid ""
"Part cooling fan speed may be increased when auto cooling is enabled. This "
"is the maximum speed for the part cooling fan."
msgstr ""
"启用自动冷却时，部件冷却风扇速度可能会增加。这是部件冷却风扇的最大速度。"

msgid ""
"The highest printable layer height for the extruder. Used to limit the "
"maximum layer height when enable adaptive layer height."
msgstr ""
"挤出机的最高可打印层高。用于在启用自适应层高时限制最大层高。"

msgid "Extrusion rate smoothing"
msgstr "挤出速率平滑"

msgid ""
"This parameter smooths out sudden extrusion rate changes that happen when "
"the printer transitions from printing a high flow (high speed/larger width) "
"extrusion to a lower flow (lower speed/smaller width) extrusion and vice "
"versa.\n"
"\n"
"It defines the maximum rate by which the extruded volumetric flow in mm³/s "
"can change over time. Higher values mean higher extrusion rate changes are "
"allowed, resulting in faster speed transitions.\n"
"\n"
"A value of 0 disables the feature.\n"
"\n"
"For a high speed, high flow direct drive printer (like the Bambu lab or "
"Voron) this value is usually not needed. However it can provide some "
"marginal benefit in certain cases where feature speeds vary greatly. For "
"example, when there are aggressive slowdowns due to overhangs. In these "
"cases a high value of around 300-350 mm³/s² is recommended as this allows "
"for just enough smoothing to assist pressure advance achieve a smoother flow "
"transition.\n"
"\n"
"For slower printers without pressure advance, the value should be set much "
"lower. A value of 10-15 mm³/s² is a good starting point for direct drive "
"extruders and 5-10 mm³/s² for Bowden style.\n"
"\n"
"This feature is known as Pressure Equalizer in Prusa slicer.\n"
"\n"
"Note: this parameter disables arc fitting."
msgstr ""
"此参数平滑打印机从打印高流量（高速度/大宽度）挤出过渡到低流量（低速度/小宽度）挤出（反之亦然）时发生的突然挤出速率变化。\n"
"\n"
"它定义了挤出体积流量（mm³/s）随时间变化的最大速率。数值越高，允许的挤出速率变化越大，从而速度过渡越快。\n"
"\n"
"值为 0 时禁用此功能。\n"
"\n"
"对于高速、高流量的直接驱动打印机（如 Bambu Lab 或 Voron），通常不需要此值。但在某些特征速度变化很大的情况下，它可能提供一些边际效益。例如，当悬垂导致激进减速时。在这种情况下，建议使用 300-350 mm³/s² 左右的高值，这可以提供足够的平滑效果，帮助压力提前实现更平滑的流量过渡。\n"
"\n"
"对于没有压力提前的较慢打印机，该值应设置得低得多。对于直接驱动挤出机，10-15 mm³/s² 是一个良好的起点；对于 Bowden 类型，5-10 mm³/s² 是一个良好的起点。\n"
"\n"
"此功能在 Prusa Slicer 中称为压力均衡器（Pressure Equalizer）。\n"
"\n"
"注意：此参数会禁用圆弧拟合。"

msgid "Smoothing segment length"
msgstr "平滑段长度"

msgid ""
"A lower value results in smoother extrusion rate transitions. However, this "
"results in a significantly larger G-code file and more instructions for the "
"printer to process.\n"
"\n"
"Default value of 3 works well for most cases. If your printer is stuttering, "
"increase this value to reduce the number of adjustments made.\n"
"\n"
"Allowed values: 0.5-5"
msgstr ""
"较低的值可实现更平滑的挤出速率过渡。但这会导致 G代码 文件显著增大，并增加打印机需要处理的指令数量。\n"
"\n"
"默认值 3 在大多数情况下效果良好。如果打印机出现卡顿，请增大此值以减少调整次数。\n"
"\n"
"允许值：0.5-5"

msgid "Apply only on external features"
msgstr "仅应用于外部特征"

msgid ""
"Applies extrusion rate smoothing only on external perimeters and overhangs. "
"This can help reduce artefacts due to sharp speed transitions on externally "
"visible overhangs without impacting the print speed of features that will "
"not be visible to the user."
msgstr ""
"仅在外部轮廓和悬垂上应用挤出速率平滑。这有助于减少外部可见悬垂上因速度急剧变化而产生的伪影，同时不影响用户不可见特征的打印速度。"

msgid "Minimum speed for part cooling fan."
msgstr "部件冷却风扇的最小速度。"

msgid ""
"Speed of auxiliary part cooling fan. Auxiliary fan will run at this speed "
"during printing except the first several layers which is defined by no "
"cooling layers.\n"
"Please enable auxiliary_fan in printer settings to use this feature. G-code "
"command: M106 P2 S(0-255)"
msgstr ""
"辅助部件冷却风扇的速度。除前几层（由无冷却层数定义）外，辅助风扇将在打印期间以此速度运行。\n"
"请先在打印机设置中启用 auxiliary_fan 以使用此功能。G代码 命令：M106 P2 S(0-255)"

msgid ""
"The lowest printable layer height for the extruder. Used to limit the "
"minimum layer height when enable adaptive layer height."
msgstr ""
"挤出机的最低可打印层高。用于在启用自适应层高时限制最小层高。"

msgid "Min print speed"
msgstr "最小打印速度"

msgid ""
"The minimum print speed to which the printer slows down to maintain the "
"minimum layer time defined above when the slowdown for better layer cooling "
"is enabled."
msgstr ""
"当启用减速以获得更好的层冷却时，打印机减慢到的最小打印速度，以维持上述定义的最短层时间。"

msgid "The diameter of nozzle."
msgstr "喷嘴直径。"

msgid "Configuration notes"
msgstr "配置注释"

msgid ""
"You can put here your personal notes. This text will be added to the G-code "
"header comments."
msgstr ""
"您可以在此处填写个人备注。此文本将添加到 G代码 文件头注释中。"

msgid "Host Type"
msgstr "主机类型"

msgid ""
"Snapmaker Orca can upload G-code files to a printer host. This field must "
"contain the kind of the host."
msgstr ""
"Snapmaker Orca 可以将 G代码 文件上传到打印机主机。此字段必须包含主机类型。"

msgid "Nozzle volume"
msgstr "喷嘴容积"

msgid "Volume of nozzle between the cutter and the end of nozzle."
msgstr "喷嘴切割器与喷嘴末端之间的容积。"

msgid "Cooling tube position"
msgstr "冷却管位置"

msgid "Distance of the center-point of the cooling tube from the extruder tip."
msgstr "冷却管中心点到挤出机喷嘴尖端的距离。"

msgid "Cooling tube length"
msgstr "冷却管长度"

msgid "Length of the cooling tube to limit space for cooling moves inside it."
msgstr "冷却管长度，用于限制其内部冷却移动的空间。"

msgid "High extruder current on filament swap"
msgstr "换丝时挤出机高电流"

msgid ""
"It may be beneficial to increase the extruder motor current during the "
"filament exchange sequence to allow for rapid ramming feed rates and to "
"overcome resistance when loading a filament with an ugly shaped tip."
msgstr ""
"在耗材交换过程中增加挤出电机电流可能是有益的，这样可以实现快速顶入送料速率，并在加载形状不规则的耗材尖端时克服阻力。"

msgid "Filament parking position"
msgstr "耗材暂停位置"

msgid ""
"Distance of the extruder tip from the position where the filament is parked "
"when unloaded. This should match the value in printer firmware."
msgstr ""
"挤出机喷嘴尖端到卸载时耗材暂停位置的距离。此值应与打印机固件中的值匹配。"

msgid "Extra loading distance"
msgstr "额外加载距离"

msgid ""
"When set to zero, the distance the filament is moved from parking position "
"during load is exactly the same as it was moved back during unload. When "
"positive, it is loaded further, if negative, the loading move is shorter "
"than unloading."
msgstr ""
"设置为零时，加载过程中耗材从暂停位置移动的距离与卸载过程中回退的距离完全相同。当为正值时，加载距离更长；如果为负值，则加载移动距离比卸载更短。"

msgid "Start end points"
msgstr "起点端点"

msgid "The start and end points which is from cutter area to garbage can."
msgstr "从切割区域到废料槽的起点和终点。"

msgid "Reduce infill retraction"
msgstr "减少填充回抽"

msgid ""
"Don't retract when the travel is in infill area absolutely. That means the "
"oozing can't been seen. This can reduce times of retraction for complex "
"model and save printing time, but make slicing and G-code generating slower."
msgstr ""
"当移动路径完全在填充区域内时不回抽。这意味着溢料不可见。这可以减少复杂模型的回抽次数并节省打印时间，但会使切片和G代码生成变慢。"

msgid ""
"This option will drop the temperature of the inactive extruders to prevent "
"oozing."
msgstr "此选项将降低非活动挤出机的温度以防止溢料。"

msgid "Filename format"
msgstr "文件名格式"

msgid "Users can define the project file name when exporting."
msgstr "用户可以在导出时定义项目文件名。"

msgid "Make overhangs printable"
msgstr "使悬垂可打印"

msgid "Modify the geometry to print overhangs without support material."
msgstr "修改几何体以在无支撑材料的情况下打印悬垂。"

msgid "Make overhangs printable - Maximum angle"
msgstr "使悬垂可打印 - 最大角度"

msgid ""
"Maximum angle of overhangs to allow after making more steep overhangs "
"printable.90° will not change the model at all and allow any overhang, while "
"0 will replace all overhangs with conical material."
msgstr ""
"在使较陡的悬垂可打印后允许的最大悬垂角度。90°将完全不改变模型并允许任何悬垂，而0将用锥形材料替换所有悬垂。"

msgid "Make overhangs printable - Hole area"
msgstr "使悬垂可打印 - 孔区域"

msgid ""
"Maximum area of a hole in the base of the model before it's filled by "
"conical material. A value of 0 will fill all the holes in the model base."
msgstr "模型底部在被锥形材料填充前的最大孔面积。值为0将填充模型底部的所有孔。"

msgid "Detect overhang wall"
msgstr "检测悬垂壁"

#, c-format, boost-format

msgid ""
"Detect the overhang percentage relative to line width and use different "
"speed to print. For 100%% overhang, bridge speed is used."
msgstr ""
"检测相对于线宽的悬垂百分比并使用不同速度打印。对于100%%悬垂，使用桥接速度。"

msgid "Filament to print walls."
msgstr "打印壁的耗材。"

msgid ""
"Line width of inner wall. If expressed as a %, it will be computed over the "
"nozzle diameter."
msgstr "内壁线宽。如果以%表示，将根据喷嘴直径计算。"

msgid "Speed of inner wall."
msgstr "内壁速度。"

msgid "Number of walls of every layer."
msgstr "每层壁数。"

msgid "Alternate extra wall"
msgstr "交替额外壁"

msgid ""
"This setting adds an extra wall to every other layer. This way the infill "
"gets wedged vertically between the walls, resulting in stronger prints.\n"
"\n"
"When this option is enabled, the ensure vertical shell thickness option "
"needs to be disabled.\n"
"\n"
"Using lightning infill together with this option is not recommended as there "
"is limited infill to anchor the extra perimeters to."
msgstr ""
"此设置每隔一层添加一个额外壁。这样填充物在垂直方向被楔入壁之间，从而产生更坚固的打印件。\n"
"\n"
"启用此选项时，需要禁用确保垂直外壳厚度选项。\n"
"\n"
"不建议将此选项与闪电填充一起使用，因为可用于锚定额外周长的填充物有限。"

msgid ""
"If you want to process the output G-code through custom scripts, just list "
"their absolute paths here. Separate multiple scripts with a semicolon. "
"Scripts will be passed the absolute path to the G-code file as the first "
"argument, and they can access the Snapmaker Orca config settings by reading "
"environment variables."
msgstr ""
"如果希望通过自定义脚本处理输出的G代码，请在此列出其绝对路径。多个脚本之间用分号分隔。脚本将接收G代码文件的绝对路径作为第一个参数，并且可以通过读取环境变量来访问Snapmaker Orca配置设置。"

msgid "Printer type"
msgstr "打印机类型"

msgid "Type of the printer."
msgstr "打印机的类型。"

msgid "Printer notes"
msgstr "打印机备注"

msgid "You can put your notes regarding the printer here."
msgstr "您可以在此处放置关于打印机的备注。"

msgid "Printer variant"
msgstr "打印机变体"

msgid "Raft contact Z distance"
msgstr "筏层接触Z距离"

msgid "Z gap between object and raft. Ignored for soluble interface."
msgstr "模型与筏层之间的Z间隙。对于可溶性界面忽略。"

msgid "Raft expansion"
msgstr "筏层扩展"

msgid "Expand all raft layers in XY plane."
msgstr "在XY平面上扩展所有筏层。"

msgid "Initial layer density"
msgstr "初始层密度"

msgid "Density of the first raft or support layer."
msgstr "第一筏层或支撑层的密度。"

msgid "Initial layer expansion"
msgstr "初始层扩展"

msgid "Expand the first raft or support layer to improve bed plate adhesion."
msgstr "扩展第一筏层或支撑层以改善热床附着力。"

msgid "Raft layers"
msgstr "筏层层数"

msgid ""
"Object will be raised by this number of support layers. Use this function to "
"avoid warping when printing ABS."
msgstr "模型将以此支撑层数抬升。使用此功能可避免打印ABS时的翘曲。"

msgid ""
"The G-code path is generated after simplifying the contour of models to "
"avoid too many points and G-code lines. Smaller value means higher "
"resolution and more time to slice."
msgstr "G代码路径是在简化模型轮廓后生成的，以避免过多的点和G代码行。值越小意味着分辨率越高，切片时间越长。"

msgid "Travel distance threshold"
msgstr "移动距离阈值"

msgid ""
"Only trigger retraction when the travel distance is longer than this "
"threshold."
msgstr "仅在移动距离超过此阈值时才触发回抽。"

msgid "Retract amount before wipe"
msgstr "擦拭前回抽量"

msgid ""
"The length of fast retraction before wipe, relative to retraction length."
msgstr "擦拭前快速回抽的长度，相对于回抽长度。"

msgid "Retract when change layer"
msgstr "换层时回抽"

msgid "Force a retraction when changes layer."
msgstr "在换层时强制回抽。"

msgid "Retraction Length"
msgstr "回抽长度"

msgid ""
"Some amount of material in extruder is pulled back to avoid ooze during long "
"travel. Set zero to disable retraction."
msgstr ""
"在长距离移动时，挤出机中的部分耗材会被拉回以避免渗出。设为零可禁用"
"回抽。"

msgid "Long retraction when cut (beta)"
msgstr "切割时长回抽（测试版）"

msgid ""
"Experimental feature: Retracting and cutting off the filament at a longer "
"distance during changes to minimize purge. While this reduces flush "
"significantly, it may also raise the risk of nozzle clogs or other printing "
"problems."
msgstr ""
"实验性功能：在换料时以更长距离回抽并切断耗材，以最小化清洗量。虽然这"
"能显著减少冲洗量，但也可能增加喷嘴堵塞或其他打印问题的风险。"

msgid "Retraction distance when cut"
msgstr "切割回抽距离"

msgid ""
"Experimental feature: Retraction length before cutting off during filament "
"change."
msgstr "实验性功能：换料时切断前的回抽长度。"

msgid "Z-hop height"
msgstr "Z轴抬升高度"

msgid ""
"Whenever the retraction is done, the nozzle is lifted a little to create "
"clearance between nozzle and the print. It prevents nozzle from hitting the "
"print when travel move. Using spiral lines to lift Z can prevent stringing."
msgstr ""
"每当进行回抽时，喷嘴会略微抬升以在喷嘴和打印件之间创造间隙。这可以防止"
"喷嘴在移动时碰撞打印件。使用螺旋线抬升Z轴可以防止拉丝。"

msgid "Z-hop lower boundary"
msgstr "Z轴抬升下限"

msgid ""
"Z-hop will only come into effect when Z is above this value and is below the "
"parameter: \"Z-hop upper boundary\"."
msgstr ""
"Z轴抬升仅在Z值高于此值且低于\"Z轴抬升上限\"参数时生效。"

msgid "Z-hop upper boundary"
msgstr "Z轴抬升上限"

msgid ""
"If this value is positive, Z-hop will only come into effect when Z is above "
"the parameter: \"Z-hop lower boundary\" and is below this value."
msgstr ""
"如果此值为正数，Z轴抬升仅在Z值高于\"Z轴抬升下限\"参数且低于此值时"
"生效。"

msgid "Z-hop type"
msgstr "Z轴抬升类型"

msgid "Type of Z-hop."
msgstr "Z轴抬升的类型。"

msgid "Slope"
msgstr "斜坡"

msgid "Spiral"
msgstr "螺旋"

msgid "Traveling angle"
msgstr "移动角度"

msgid ""
"Traveling angle for Slope and Spiral Z-hop type. Setting it to 90° results "
"in Normal Lift."
msgstr ""
"斜坡和螺旋Z轴抬升类型的移动角度。设置为90°则为正常抬升。"

msgid "Only lift Z above"
msgstr "仅在Z高于时抬升"

msgid ""
"If you set this to a positive value, Z lift will only take place above the "
"specified absolute Z."
msgstr "如果将此值设置为正数，Z轴抬升仅在高于指定绝对Z值时发生。"

msgid "Only lift Z below"
msgstr "仅在Z低于时抬升"

msgid ""
"If you set this to a positive value, Z lift will only take place below the "
"specified absolute Z."
msgstr "如果将此值设置为正数，Z轴抬升仅在低于指定绝对Z值时发生。"

msgid "On surfaces"
msgstr "在表面上"

msgid ""
"Enforce Z-Hop behavior. This setting is impacted by the above settings (Only "
"lift Z above/below)."
msgstr ""
"强制执行Z轴抬升行为。此设置受上述设置（仅在Z高于/低于时抬升）影响。"

msgid "All Surfaces"
msgstr "所有表面"

msgid "Top Only"
msgstr "仅顶部"

msgid "Bottom Only"
msgstr "仅底部"

msgid "Top and Bottom"
msgstr "顶部和底部"

msgid "Extra length on restart"
msgstr "重启额外长度"

msgid ""
"When the retraction is compensated after the travel move, the extruder will "
"push this additional amount of filament. This setting is rarely needed."
msgstr ""
"当回抽在移动后得到补偿时，挤出机会额外推送此数量的耗材。此设置很少需"
"要调整。"

msgid ""
"When the retraction is compensated after changing tool, the extruder will "
"push this additional amount of filament."
msgstr "当回抽在切换工具后得到补偿时，挤出机会额外推送此数量的耗材。"

msgid "Retraction Speed"
msgstr "回抽速度"

msgid "Speed for retracting filament from the nozzle."
msgstr "从喷嘴回抽耗材的速度。"

msgid "De-retraction Speed"
msgstr "取消回抽速度"

msgid ""
"Speed for reloading filament into the nozzle. Zero means same speed of "
"retraction."
msgstr "将耗材重新送入喷嘴的速度。设为零表示与回抽速度相同。"

msgid "Use firmware retraction"
msgstr "使用固件回抽"

msgid ""
"This experimental setting uses G10 and G11 commands to have the firmware "
"handle the retraction. This is only supported in recent Marlin."
msgstr ""
"此实验性设置使用G10和G11命令让固件处理回抽。仅在新版Marlin固件中支"
"持。"

msgid "Show auto-calibration marks"
msgstr "显示自动校准标记"

msgid "Disable set remaining print time"
msgstr "禁用设置剩余打印时间"

msgid ""
"Disable generating of the M73: Set remaining print time in the final G-code."
msgstr "禁用在最终G代码中生成M73：设置剩余打印时间。"

msgid "Seam position"
msgstr "接缝位置"

msgid "The start position to print each part of outer wall."
msgstr "打印每部分外壳的起始位置。"

msgid "Nearest"
msgstr "最近"

msgid "Aligned"
msgstr "对齐"

msgid "Aligned back"
msgstr "后部对齐"

msgid "Back"
msgstr "返回"

msgid "Random"
msgstr "随机"

msgid "Staggered inner seams"
msgstr "交错内部接缝"

msgid ""
"This option causes the inner seams to be shifted backwards based on their "
"depth, forming a zigzag pattern."
msgstr ""
"此选项使内部接缝根据其深度向后偏移，形成锯齿状图案。"

msgid "Seam gap"
msgstr "接缝间隙"

msgid ""
"In order to reduce the visibility of the seam in a closed loop extrusion, "
"the loop is interrupted and shortened by a specified amount.\n"
"This amount can be specified in millimeters or as a percentage of the "
"current extruder diameter. The default value for this parameter is 10%."
msgstr ""
"为了减少封闭回圈挤出中接缝的可见性，回圈被中断并按指定量缩短。\n"
"该量可以毫米或当前挤出机直径的百分比指定。此参数的默认值为10%。"

msgid "Scarf joint seam (beta)"
msgstr "斜接接缝（测试版）"

msgid "Use scarf joint to minimize seam visibility and increase seam strength."
msgstr "使用斜接以最小化接缝可见性并提高接缝强度。"

msgid "Conditional scarf joint"
msgstr "条件斜接"

msgid ""
"Apply scarf joints only to smooth perimeters where traditional seams do not "
"conceal the seams at sharp corners effectively."
msgstr ""
"仅在光滑外壳上应用斜接，传统接缝无法在尖角处有效隐藏接缝的情况下使用。"

msgid "Conditional angle threshold"
msgstr "条件角度阈值"

msgid ""
"This option sets the threshold angle for applying a conditional scarf joint "
"seam.\n"
"If the maximum angle within the perimeter loop exceeds this value "
"(indicating the absence of sharp corners), a scarf joint seam will be used. "
"The default value is 155°."
msgstr ""
"此选项设置应用条件斜接接缝的阈值角度。\n"
"如果外壳回圈内的最大角度超过此值（表明没有尖角），则将使用斜接接缝。"
"默认值为155°。"

msgid "Conditional overhang threshold"
msgstr "条件悬垂阈值"

#, no-c-format, no-boost-format

msgid ""
"This option determines the overhang threshold for the application of scarf "
"joint seams. If the unsupported portion of the perimeter is less than this "
"threshold, scarf joint seams will be applied. The default threshold is set "
"at 40% of the external wall's width. Due to performance considerations, the "
"degree of overhang is estimated."
msgstr ""
"此选项决定应用斜接接缝的悬垂阈值。如果外壳的未支撑部分小于此阈值，"
"则将应用斜接接缝。默认阈值设置为外部壁宽的40%。出于性能考虑，"
"悬垂程度为估算值。"

msgid "Scarf joint speed"
msgstr "斜接速度"

msgid ""
"This option sets the printing speed for scarf joints. It is recommended to "
"print scarf joints at a slow speed (less than 100 mm/s). It's also advisable "
"to enable 'Extrusion rate smoothing' if the set speed varies significantly "
"from the speed of the outer or inner walls. If the speed specified here is "
"higher than the speed of the outer or inner walls, the printer will default "
"to the slower of the two speeds. When specified as a percentage (e.g., 80%), "
"the speed is calculated based on the respective outer or inner wall speed. "
"The default value is set to 100%."
msgstr ""
"此选项设置斜接的打印速度。建议以较慢的速度（小于100 mm/s）打印斜接。"
"如果设定的速度与外部或内部壁的速度差异较大，"
"建议启用"挤出速率平滑"。如果此处指定的速度高于外部或内部壁的速度，"
"打印机将默认使用两者中较慢的速度。当以百分比（例如80%）指定时，"
"速度将基于相应的外部或内部壁速度计算。默认值为100%。"

msgid "Scarf joint flow ratio"
msgstr "斜接流量比"

msgid "This factor affects the amount of material for scarf joints."
msgstr "此系数影响斜接的材料用量。"

msgid "Scarf start height"
msgstr "斜接起始高度"

msgid ""
"Start height of the scarf.\n"
"This amount can be specified in millimeters or as a percentage of the "
"current layer height. The default value for this parameter is 0."
msgstr ""
"斜接的起始高度。\n"
"该量可以毫米或当前层高的百分比指定。此参数的默认值为0。"

msgid "Scarf around entire wall"
msgstr "环绕整个壁的斜接"

msgid "The scarf extends to the entire length of the wall."
msgstr "斜接延伸至整个壁的长度。"

msgid "Scarf length"
msgstr "斜接长度"

msgid ""
"Length of the scarf. Setting this parameter to zero effectively disables the "
"scarf."
msgstr ""
"斜接的长度。将此参数设置为零将有效禁用斜接。"

msgid "Scarf steps"
msgstr "斜接段数"

msgid "Minimum number of segments of each scarf."
msgstr "每个斜接的最小段数。"

msgid "Scarf joint for inner walls"
msgstr "内部壁斜接"

msgid "Use scarf joint for inner walls as well."
msgstr "同时也对内部壁使用斜接。"

msgid "Role base wipe speed"
msgstr "基于角色的擦拭速度"

msgid ""
"The wipe speed is determined by the speed of the current extrusion role. "
"e.g. if a wipe action is executed immediately following an outer wall "
"extrusion, the speed of the outer wall extrusion will be utilized for the "
"wipe action."
msgstr ""
"擦拭速度由当前挤出角色的速度决定。"
"例如，如果在外部壁挤出后立即执行擦拭动作，"
"则将使用外部壁挤出的速度进行擦拭动作。"

msgid "Wipe on loops"
msgstr "回圈擦拭"

msgid ""
"To minimize the visibility of the seam in a closed loop extrusion, a small "
"inward movement is executed before the extruder leaves the loop."
msgstr ""
"为最小化封闭回圈挤出中接缝的可见性，在挤出机离开回圈前"
"执行一个向内的微小移动。"

msgid "Wipe before external loop"
msgstr "外部回圈前擦拭"

msgid ""
"To minimize visibility of potential overextrusion at the start of an "
"external perimeter when printing with Outer/Inner or Inner/Outer/Inner wall "
"print order, the de-retraction is performed slightly on the inside from the "
"start of the external perimeter. That way any potential over extrusion is "
"hidden from the outside surface.\n"
"\n"
"This is useful when printing with Outer/Inner or Inner/Outer/Inner wall "
"print order as in these modes it is more likely an external perimeter is "
"printed immediately after a de-retraction move."
msgstr ""
"为最小化在以外/内或内/外/内壁打印顺序打印时外部外壳起始处"
"可能出现的过度挤出的可见性，回抽解除在外部外壳起点略微内侧执行。"
"这样任何潜在的过度挤出都会被隐藏在外表面之外。\n"
"\n"
"这在以外/内或内/外/内壁打印顺序打印时很有用，"
"因为在这些模式下，外部外壳更可能在回抽解除移动后立即打印。"

msgid "Wipe speed"
msgstr "擦拭速度"

msgid ""
"The wipe speed is determined by the speed setting specified in this "
"configuration. If the value is expressed as a percentage (e.g. 80%), it will "
"be calculated based on the travel speed setting above. The default value for "
"this parameter is 80%."
msgstr ""
"擦拭速度由此配置中指定的速度设置决定。如果该值以百分比（例如80%）表示，"
"则将基于上述移动速度设置进行计算。此参数的默认值为80%。"

msgid "Skirt distance"
msgstr "裙边距离"

msgid "The distance from the skirt to the brim or the object."
msgstr "裙边到底边或对象的距离。"

msgid "Skirt start point"
msgstr "裙边起始点"

msgid ""
"Angle from the object center to skirt start point. Zero is the most right "
"position, counter clockwise is positive angle."
msgstr ""
"从对象中心到裙边起始点的角度。零为最右侧位置，逆时针为正角度。"

msgid "Skirt height"
msgstr "裙边层数"

msgid "How many layers of skirt. Usually only one layer."
msgstr "裙边层数。通常只有一层。"

msgid "Single loop after first layer"
msgstr "第一层后单回圈"

msgid ""
"Limits the skirt/draft shield loops to one wall after the first layer. This "
"is useful, on occasion, to conserve filament but may cause the draft shield/"
"skirt to warp / crack."
msgstr ""
"将第一层后的裙边/防风罩回圈限制为一层壁。这有时有助于节省耗材，"
"但可能导致防风罩/裙边翘曲或开裂。"

msgid "Draft shield"
msgstr "防风罩"

msgid ""
"A draft shield is useful to protect an ABS or ASA print from warping and "
"detaching from print bed due to wind draft. It is usually needed only with "
"open frame printers, i.e. without an enclosure.\n"
"\n"
"Enabled = skirt is as tall as the highest printed object. Otherwise 'Skirt "
"height' is used.\n"
"Note: With the draft shield active, the skirt will be printed at skirt "
"distance from the object. Therefore, if brims are active it may intersect "
"with them. To avoid this, increase the skirt distance value.\n"
msgstr ""
"防风罩用于保护ABS或ASA打印件，防止因气流导致翘曲和从热床上脱落。"
"通常仅在开放式框架打印机（即没有外壳的打印机）上需要。\n"
"\n"
"已启用 = 裙边与最高打印对象同高。否则使用\"裙边高度\"。\n"
"注意：启用防风罩后，裙边将按照与对象的裙边距离进行打印。"
"因此，如果启用了底边，可能会与底边相交。"
"为避免这种情况，请增加裙边距离值。\n"

msgid "Enabled"
msgstr "已启用"

msgid "Skirt type"
msgstr "裙边类型"

msgid ""
"Combined - single skirt for all objects, Per object - individual object "
"skirt."
msgstr ""
"组合式 - 所有对象共用一个裙边，按对象 - 每个对象单独的裙边。"

msgid "Per object"
msgstr "按对象"

msgid "Skirt loops"
msgstr "裙边圈数"

msgid "Number of loops for the skirt. Zero means disabling skirt."
msgstr "裙边的圈数。零表示禁用裙边。"

msgid "Skirt speed"
msgstr "裙边速度"

msgid "Speed of skirt, in mm/s. Zero means use default layer extrusion speed."
msgstr "裙边速度，单位为mm/s。零表示使用默认的层挤出速度。"

msgid "Skirt minimum extrusion length"
msgstr "裙边最小挤出长度"

msgid ""
"Minimum filament extrusion length in mm when printing the skirt. Zero means "
"this feature is disabled.\n"
"\n"
"Using a non-zero value is useful if the printer is set up to print without a "
"prime line.\n"
"Final number of loops is not taking into account while arranging or "
"validating objects distance. Increase loop number in such case."
msgstr ""
"打印裙边时的最小耗材挤出长度（mm）。零表示禁用此功能。\n"
"\n"
"如果打印机设置为无净化线打印，使用非零值会很有用。\n"
"在排列或验证对象距离时，最终圈数不会被考虑在内。在这种情况下请增加圈数。"

msgid ""
"The printing speed in exported G-code will be slowed down when the estimated "
"layer time is shorter than this value in order to get better cooling for "
"these layers."
msgstr ""
"当估计的层打印时间短于该值时，导出的G代码中的打印速度将会降低，"
"以便为这些层获得更好的冷却效果。"

msgid "Minimum sparse infill threshold"
msgstr "最小稀疏填充阈值"

msgid ""
"Sparse infill area which is smaller than threshold value is replaced by "
"internal solid infill."
msgstr ""
"面积小于阈值的稀疏填充区域将被内部实心填充替代。"

msgid "Solid infill"
msgstr "实心填充"

msgid "Filament to print solid infill."
msgstr "打印实心填充的耗材。"

msgid ""
"Line width of internal solid infill. If expressed as a %, it will be "
"computed over the nozzle diameter."
msgstr ""
"内部实心填充的线宽。如果以%表示，将根据喷嘴直径计算。"

msgid "Speed of internal solid infill, not the top and bottom surface."
msgstr "内部实心填充的速度，不包括顶部和底部表面。"

msgid ""
"Spiralize smooths out the z moves of the outer contour. And turns a solid "
"model into a single walled print with solid bottom layers. The final "
"generated model has no seam."
msgstr ""
"螺旋化平滑了外轮廓的Z轴移动，将实体模型转化为只有底部实心层的"
"单壁打印件。最终生成的模型没有接缝。"

msgid "Smooth Spiral"
msgstr "平滑螺旋"

msgid ""
"Smooth Spiral smooths out X and Y moves as well, resulting in no visible "
"seam at all, even in the XY directions on walls that are not vertical."
msgstr ""
"平滑螺旋也平滑了X和Y轴移动，从而完全看不到接缝，"
"即使在非垂直壁面的XY方向上也是如此。"

msgid "Max XY Smoothing"
msgstr "最大XY平滑"

#, no-c-format, no-boost-format

msgid ""
"Maximum distance to move points in XY to try to achieve a smooth spiral. If "
"expressed as a %, it will be computed over nozzle diameter."
msgstr ""
"为实现平滑螺旋而移动点的最大XY距离。如果以%表示，将根据喷嘴直径计算。"

msgid "Spiral starting flow ratio"
msgstr "螺旋起始流量比"

#, no-c-format, no-boost-format

msgid ""
"Sets the starting flow ratio while transitioning from the last bottom layer "
"to the spiral. Normally the spiral transition scales the flow ratio from 0% "
"to 100% during the first loop which can in some cases lead to under "
"extrusion at the start of the spiral."
msgstr ""
"设置从最后一层底部层过渡到螺旋时的起始流量比。"
"通常螺旋过渡在第一个圈中将流量比从0%逐渐增加到100%，"
"这在某些情况下可能会导致螺旋起始处挤出不足。"

msgid "Spiral finishing flow ratio"
msgstr "螺旋结束流量比"

#, no-c-format, no-boost-format

msgid ""
"Sets the finishing flow ratio while ending the spiral. Normally the spiral "
"transition scales the flow ratio from 100% to 0% during the last loop which "
"can in some cases lead to under extrusion at the end of the spiral."
msgstr ""
"设置结束螺旋时的结束流量比。"
"通常螺旋过渡在最后一个圈中将流量比从100%逐渐减少到0%，"
"这在某些情况下可能会导致螺旋结束处挤出不足。"

msgid ""
"If smooth or traditional mode is selected, a timelapse video will be "
"generated for each print. After each layer is printed, a snapshot is taken "
"with the chamber camera. All of these snapshots are composed into a "
"timelapse video when printing completes. If smooth mode is selected, the "
"toolhead will move to the excess chute after each layer is printed and then "
"take a snapshot. Since the melt filament may leak from the nozzle during the "
"process of taking a snapshot, prime tower is required for smooth mode to "
"wipe nozzle."
msgstr ""
"如果选择了平滑或传统模式，将为每次打印生成延时摄影视频。"
"每打印完一层后，使用舱内摄像头拍摄快照。"
"打印完成时，所有快照将被合成为延时摄影视频。"
"如果选择了平滑模式，打印头每完成一层后会移动到排料槽，然后拍摄快照。"
"由于拍摄快照过程中熔化的耗材可能会从喷嘴漏出，"
"平滑模式需要净化塔来擦拭喷嘴。"

msgid "Traditional"
msgstr "传统"

msgid "Temperature variation"
msgstr "温度变化"

#. TRN PrintSettings : "Ooze prevention" > "Temperature variation"

msgid ""
"Temperature difference to be applied when an extruder is not active. The "
"value is not used when 'idle_temperature' in filament settings is set to non-"
"zero value."
msgstr ""
"挤出机非活动时应用的温差。"
"当耗材设置中的'idle_temperature'设置为非零值时，不使用此值。"

msgid "Preheat time"
msgstr "预热时间"

msgid ""
"To reduce the waiting time after tool change, Orca can preheat the next tool "
"while the current tool is still in use. This setting specifies the time in "
"seconds to preheat the next tool. Orca will insert a M104 command to preheat "
"the tool in advance."
msgstr ""
"为了减少工具更换后的等待时间，Orca可以在当前工具仍在使用时预热下一个工具。"
"此设置指定预热下一个工具的时间（秒）。"
"Orca将插入M104命令以提前预热工具。"

msgid "Preheat steps"
msgstr "预热步数"

msgid ""
"Insert multiple preheat commands (e.g. M104.1). Only useful for Prusa XL. "
"For other printers, please set it to 1."
msgstr ""
"插入多个预热命令（例如M104.1）。仅对Prusa XL有用。"
"对于其他打印机，请将其设置为1。"

msgid "Start G-code"
msgstr "起始G代码"

msgid "Start G-code when starting the entire print."
msgstr "开始整个打印时的起始G代码。"

msgid "Start G-code when starting the printing of this filament."
msgstr "开始打印该耗材时的起始G代码。"

msgid "Single Extruder Multi Material"
msgstr "单挤出机多材料"

msgid "Use single nozzle to print multi filament."
msgstr "使用单个喷嘴打印多种耗材。"

msgid "Manual Filament Change"
msgstr "手动更换耗材"

msgid ""
"Enable this option to omit the custom Change filament G-code only at the "
"beginning of the print. The tool change command (e.g., T0) will be skipped "
"throughout the entire print. This is useful for manual multi-material "
"printing, where we use M600/PAUSE to trigger the manual filament change "
"action."
msgstr ""
"启用此选项以仅在打印开始时省略自定义的更换耗材G代码。"
"整个打印过程中将跳过工具更换命令（例如T0）。"
"这对于手动多材料打印非常有用，我们使用M600/PAUSE来触发手动更换耗材操作。"

msgid "Purge in prime tower"
msgstr "在净化塔中清洗"

msgid "Purge remaining filament into prime tower."
msgstr "将剩余耗材清洗到净化塔中。"

msgid "Enable filament ramming"
msgstr "启用耗材顶入"

msgid "No sparse layers (beta)"
msgstr "无稀疏层（测试版）"

msgid ""
"If enabled, the wipe tower will not be printed on layers with no tool "
"changes. On layers with a tool change, extruder will travel downward to "
"print the wipe tower. User is responsible for ensuring there is no collision "
"with the print."
msgstr ""
"如果启用，擦拭塔将不会在无工具更换的层上打印。在有工具更换的层上，挤出机将向下移动以打印擦拭塔。"
"用户需负责确保不与打印模型发生碰撞。"

msgid "Prime all printing extruders"
msgstr "初始化所有打印挤出机"

msgid ""
"If enabled, all printing extruders will be primed at the front edge of the "
"print bed at the start of the print."
msgstr ""
"如果启用，所有打印挤出机将在打印开始时在打印平台前缘进行初始化。"

msgid "Slice gap closing radius"
msgstr "切片缝隙闭合半径"

msgid ""
"Cracks smaller than 2x gap closing radius are being filled during the "
"triangle mesh slicing. The gap closing operation may reduce the final print "
"resolution, therefore it is advisable to keep the value reasonably low."
msgstr ""
"在三角网格切片过程中，小于2倍缝隙闭合半径的裂缝将被填充。"
"缝隙闭合操作可能会降低最终打印分辨率，因此建议将该值保持在合理较低的水平。"

msgid "Slicing Mode"
msgstr "切片模式"

msgid ""
"Use \"Even-odd\" for 3DLabPrint airplane models. Use \"Close holes\" to "
"close all holes in the model."
msgstr ""
"对于3DLabPrint飞机模型，请使用\"奇偶\"模式。使用\"闭合孔洞\"可闭合模型中的所有孔洞。"

msgid "Regular"
msgstr "常规"

msgid "Even-odd"
msgstr "奇偶"

msgid "Close holes"
msgstr "闭合孔洞"

msgid "Z offset"
msgstr "Z轴偏移"

msgid ""
"This value will be added (or subtracted) from all the Z coordinates in the "
"output G-code. It is used to compensate for bad Z endstop position: for "
"example, if your endstop zero actually leaves the nozzle 0.3mm far from the "
"print bed, set this to -0.3 (or fix your endstop)."
msgstr ""
"该值将从输出G代码中的所有Z坐标中增加（或减去）。"
"用于补偿Z轴限位开关位置不准：例如，如果您的限位开关零点实际上使喷嘴距离打印平台0.3mm，"
"请将此值设置为-0.3（或修复您的限位开关）。"

msgid "Enable support"
msgstr "启用支撑"

msgid "Enable support generation."
msgstr "启用支撑生成。"

msgid ""
"Normal (auto) and Tree (auto) are used to generate support automatically. If "
"Normal (manual) or Tree (manual) is selected, only support enforcers are "
"generated."
msgstr ""
"正常（自动）和树状（自动）用于自动生成支撑。"
"如果选择正常（手动）或树状（手动），则仅生成支撑强制区域。"

msgid "Normal (auto)"
msgstr "正常（自动）"

msgid "Tree (auto)"
msgstr "树状（自动）"

msgid "Normal (manual)"
msgstr "正常（手动）"

msgid "Tree (manual)"
msgstr "树状（手动）"

msgid "Support/object xy distance"
msgstr "支撑/模型XY距离"

msgid "XY separation between an object and its support."
msgstr "模型与其支撑之间的XY间距。"

msgid "Support/object first layer gap"
msgstr "支撑/模型首层间隙"

msgid "XY separation between an object and its support at the first layer."
msgstr "首层模型与其支撑之间的XY间距。"

msgid "Pattern angle"
msgstr "图案角度"

msgid "Use this setting to rotate the support pattern on the horizontal plane."
msgstr "使用此设置可在水平面上旋转支撑图案。"

msgid "On build plate only"
msgstr "仅在打印平台上"

msgid "Don't create support on model surface, only on build plate."
msgstr "不在模型表面创建支撑，仅在打印平台上创建。"

msgid "Support critical regions only"
msgstr "仅支撑关键区域"

msgid ""
"Only create support for critical regions including sharp tail, cantilever, "
"etc."
msgstr "仅对尖锐尾部、悬臂等关键区域创建支撑。"

msgid "Remove small overhangs"
msgstr "移除小悬垂"

msgid "Remove small overhangs that possibly need no supports."
msgstr "移除可能不需要支撑的小悬垂。"

msgid "Top Z distance"
msgstr "顶部Z距离"

msgid "The Z gap between the top support interface and object."
msgstr "顶部支撑界面与模型之间的Z间隙。"

msgid "Bottom Z distance"
msgstr "底部Z距离"

msgid "The Z gap between the bottom support interface and object."
msgstr "底部支撑界面与模型之间的Z间隙。"

msgid "Support/raft base"
msgstr "支撑/筏层基底"

msgid ""
"Filament to print support base and raft. \"Default\" means no specific "
"filament for support and current filament is used."
msgstr ""
"用于打印支撑基底和筏层的耗材。\"默认\"表示不指定特定支撑耗材，使用当前耗材。"

msgid "Avoid interface filament for base"
msgstr "避免使用界面耗材作为基底"

msgid ""
"Avoid using support interface filament to print support base if possible."
msgstr "尽可能避免使用支撑界面耗材来打印支撑基底。"

msgid ""
"Line width of support. If expressed as a %, it will be computed over the "
"nozzle diameter."
msgstr ""
"支撑的线宽。如果以百分比表示，将根据喷嘴直径计算。"

msgid "Interface use loop pattern"
msgstr "界面使用环形图案"

msgid ""
"Cover the top contact layer of the supports with loops. Disabled by default."
msgstr ""
"用环覆盖支撑的顶部接触层。默认禁用。"

msgid "Support/raft interface"
msgstr "支撑/筏层界面"

msgid ""
"Filament to print support interface. \"Default\" means no specific filament "
"for support interface and current filament is used."
msgstr ""
"用于打印支撑界面的耗材。\"默认\"表示没有指定支撑界面的耗材，使用当前耗材。"

msgid "Top interface layers"
msgstr "顶部界面层数"

msgid "Number of top interface layers."
msgstr "顶部界面层数。"

msgid "Bottom interface layers"
msgstr "底部界面层数"

msgid "Number of bottom interface layers."
msgstr "底部界面层数。"

msgid "Same as top"
msgstr "与顶部相同"

msgid "Top interface spacing"
msgstr "顶部界面间距"

msgid ""
"Spacing of interface lines. Zero means solid interface.\n"
"Force using solid interface when support ironing is enabled."
msgstr ""
"界面线的间距。零表示实心界面。\n"
"启用支撑熨平时强制使用实心界面。"

msgid "Bottom interface spacing"
msgstr "底部界面间距"

msgid "Spacing of bottom interface lines. Zero means solid interface."
msgstr "底部界面线的间距。零表示实心界面。"

msgid "Speed of support interface."
msgstr "支撑界面的速度。"

msgid "Base pattern"
msgstr "基础图案"

msgid "Line pattern of support."
msgstr "支撑的线条图案。"

msgid "Rectilinear grid"
msgstr "直线网格"

msgid "Hollow"
msgstr "空心"

msgid "Interface pattern"
msgstr "界面图案"

msgid ""
"Line pattern of support interface. Default pattern for non-soluble support "
"interface is Rectilinear, while default pattern for soluble support "
"interface is Concentric."
msgstr ""
"支撑界面的线条图案。非溶性支撑界面的默认图案为直线，而溶性支撑界面的默认图案为同心圆。"

msgid "Rectilinear Interlaced"
msgstr "直线交错"

msgid "Base pattern spacing"
msgstr "基础图案间距"

msgid "Spacing between support lines."
msgstr "支撑线之间的间距。"

msgid "Normal Support expansion"
msgstr "普通支撑扩展"

msgid "Expand (+) or shrink (-) the horizontal span of normal support."
msgstr "扩大（+）或缩小（-）普通支撑的水平范围。"

msgid "Speed of support."
msgstr "支撑的速度。"

msgid ""
"Style and shape of the support. For normal support, projecting the supports "
"into a regular grid will create more stable supports (default), while snug "
"support towers will save material and reduce object scarring.\n"
"For tree support, slim and organic style will merge branches more "
"aggressively and save a lot of material (default organic), while hybrid "
"style will create similar structure to normal support under large flat "
"overhangs."
msgstr ""
"支撑的样式和形状。对于普通支撑，将支撑投影到规则网格中可创建更稳定的支撑（默认），"
"而贴合支撑柱可节省材料并减少物体表面疤痕。\n"
"对于树状支撑，纤细有机风格会更积极地合并分支并节省大量材料（默认为有机），"
"而混合风格会在大型平坦悬垂下创建类似于普通支撑的结构。"

msgid "Default (Grid/Organic)"
msgstr "默认（网格/有机）"

msgid "Snug"
msgstr "贴合"

msgid "Organic"
msgstr "有机"

msgid "Tree Slim"
msgstr "树状纤细"

msgid "Tree Strong"
msgstr "树状强健"

msgid "Tree Hybrid"
msgstr "树状混合"

msgid "Independent support layer height"
msgstr "独立支撑层高"

msgid ""
"Support layer uses layer height independent with object layer. This is to "
"support customizing z-gap and save print time. This option will be invalid "
"when the prime tower is enabled."
msgstr ""
"支撑层使用与物体层独立的层高。这是为了支持自定义Z间隙并节省打印时间。"
"当启用净化塔时，此选项将无效。"

msgid "Threshold angle"
msgstr "临界角度"

msgid ""
"Support will be generated for overhangs whose slope angle is below the "
"threshold."
msgstr ""
"将为倾斜角度低于临界值的悬垂生成支撑。"

msgid "Threshold overlap"
msgstr "临界重叠"

msgid ""
"If threshold angle is zero, support will be generated for overhangs whose "
"overlap is below the threshold. The smaller this value is, the steeper the "
"overhang that can be printed without support."
msgstr ""
"如果临界角度为零，将为重叠度低于临界值的悬垂生成支撑。"
"此值越小，无需支撑即可打印的悬垂越陡。"

msgid "Tree support branch angle"
msgstr "树状支撑分支角度"

msgid ""
"This setting determines the maximum overhang angle that the branches of tree "
"support are allowed to make. If the angle is increased, the branches can be "
"printed more horizontally, allowing them to reach farther."
msgstr ""
"此设置确定树状支撑分支允许的最大悬垂角度。"
"如果增加角度，分支可以更水平地打印，使它们能够延伸得更远。"

msgid "Preferred Branch Angle"
msgstr "首选分支角度"

#. TRN PrintSettings: "Organic supports" > "Preferred Branch Angle"

msgid ""
"The preferred angle of the branches, when they do not have to avoid the "
"model. Use a lower angle to make them more vertical and more stable. Use a "
"higher angle for branches to merge faster."
msgstr ""
"分支的首选角度，当它们不必避开模型时使用。"
"使用较低的角度使它们更垂直、更稳定。使用较高的角度使分支更快合并。"

msgid "Tree support branch distance"
msgstr "树状支撑分支距离"

msgid ""
"This setting determines the distance between neighboring tree support nodes."
msgstr ""
"此设置确定相邻树状支撑节点之间的距离。"

msgid "Branch Density"
msgstr "分支密度"

#. TRN PrintSettings: "Organic supports" > "Branch Density"

msgid ""
"Adjusts the density of the support structure used to generate the tips of "
"the branches. A higher value results in better overhangs but the supports "
"are harder to remove, thus it is recommended to enable top support "
"interfaces instead of a high branch density value if dense interfaces are "
"needed."
msgstr ""
"调整用于生成树枝尖端的支撑结构密度。较高的值可获得更好的悬垂效果，"
"但支撑更难移除，因此如果需要致密界面，建议启用顶部支撑界面而不是高分支密度值。"

msgid "Adaptive layer height"
msgstr "自适应层高"

msgid ""
"Enabling this option means the height of tree support layer except the first "
"will be automatically calculated."
msgstr ""
"启用此选项意味着除第一层外的树支撑层高度将自动计算。"

msgid "Auto brim width"
msgstr "自动底边宽度"

msgid ""
"Enabling this option means the width of the brim for tree support will be "
"automatically calculated."
msgstr ""
"启用此选项意味着树支撑的底边宽度将自动计算。"

msgid "Tree support brim width"
msgstr "树支撑底边宽度"

msgid "Distance from tree branch to the outermost brim line."
msgstr "从树分支到最外侧底边线的距离。"

msgid "Tip Diameter"
msgstr "尖端直径"

#. TRN PrintSettings: "Organic supports" > "Tip Diameter"

msgid "Branch tip diameter for organic supports."
msgstr "树状支撑的树枝尖端直径。"

msgid "Tree support branch diameter"
msgstr "树支撑分支直径"

msgid "This setting determines the initial diameter of support nodes."
msgstr "此设置决定支撑节点的初始直径。"

#. TRN PrintSettings: #lmFIXME

msgid "Branch Diameter Angle"
msgstr "分支直径角度"

#. TRN PrintSettings: "Organic supports" > "Branch Diameter Angle"

msgid ""
"The angle of the branches' diameter as they gradually become thicker towards "
"the bottom. An angle of 0 will cause the branches to have uniform thickness "
"over their length. A bit of an angle can increase stability of the organic "
"support."
msgstr ""
"分支直径的角度，随着向底部逐渐变粗。角度为0将导致分支在其长度上具有均匀的厚度。"
"稍微增加角度可以增加树状支撑的稳定性。"

msgid "Support wall loops"
msgstr "支撑壁环数"

msgid ""
"This setting specifies the count of support walls in the range of [0,2]. 0 "
"means auto."
msgstr ""
"此设置指定支撑壁的数量，范围为[0,2]。0表示自动。"

msgid "Tree support with infill"
msgstr "树支撑带填充"

msgid ""
"This setting specifies whether to add infill inside large hollows of tree "
"support."
msgstr ""
"此设置指定是否在树支撑的大型空洞内添加填充。"

msgid "Ironing Support Interface"
msgstr "熨烫支撑界面"

msgid ""
"Ironing is using small flow to print on same height of support interface "
"again to make it more smooth. This setting controls whether support "
"interface being ironed. When enabled, support interface will be extruded as "
"solid too."
msgstr ""
"熨烫是在支撑界面的同一高度使用小流量再次打印以使其更光滑。此设置控制是否熨烫支撑界面。"
"启用时，支撑界面也将以实心方式挤出。"

msgid "Support Ironing Pattern"
msgstr "支撑熨烫图案"

msgid "Support Ironing flow"
msgstr "支撑熨烫流量"

msgid ""
"The amount of material to extrude during ironing. Relative to flow of normal "
"support interface layer height. Too high value results in overextrusion on "
"the surface."
msgstr ""
"熨烫期间挤出的材料量。相对于正常支撑界面层高的流量。过高的值会导致表面过度挤出。"

msgid "Support Ironing line spacing"
msgstr "支撑熨烫线间距"

msgid "Activate temperature control"
msgstr "激活温度控制"

msgid ""
"Enable this option for automated chamber temperature control. This option "
"activates the emitting of an M191 command before the "
"\"machine_start_gcode\"\n"
" which sets the chamber temperature and waits until it is reached. In "
"addition, it emits an M141 command at the end of the print to turn off the "
"chamber heater, if present.\n"
"\n"
"This option relies on the firmware supporting the M191 and M141 commands "
"either via macros or natively and is usually used when an active chamber "
"heater is installed."
msgstr ""
"启用此选项以自动控制腔室温度。此选项会在"
"\"machine_start_gcode\"之前触发M191命令，"
"该命令设置腔室温度并等待达到目标温度。此外，在打印结束时触发M141命令以关闭腔室加热器（如果已安装）。\n"
"\n"
"此选项依赖于固件通过宏或原生方式支持M191和M141命令，通常在安装了主动腔室加热器时使用。"

msgid "Chamber temperature"
msgstr "腔室温度"

msgid ""
"For high-temperature materials like ABS, ASA, PC, and PA, a higher chamber "
"temperature can help suppress or reduce warping and potentially lead to "
"higher interlayer bonding strength. However, at the same time, a higher "
"chamber temperature will reduce the efficiency of air filtration for ABS and "
"ASA.\n"
"\n"
"For PLA, PETG, TPU, PVA, and other low-temperature materials, this option "
"should be disabled (set to 0) as the chamber temperature should be low to "
"avoid extruder clogging caused by material softening at the heat break.\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, this parameter also sets a G-code variable named "
"chamber_temperature, which can be used to pass the desired chamber "
"temperature to your print start macro, or a heat soak macro like this: "
"PRINT_START (other variables) CHAMBER_TEMP=[chamber_temperature]. This may "
"be useful if your printer does not support M141/M191 commands, or if you "
"desire to handle heat soaking in the print start macro if no active chamber "
"heater is installed."
msgstr ""
"对于ABS、ASA、PC和PA等高温材料，较高的腔室温度有助于抑制或减少翘曲，"
"并可能提高层间粘合强度。但同时，较高的腔室温度会降低ABS和ASA的空气过滤效率。\n"
"\n"
"对于PLA、PETG、TPU、PVA和其他低温材料，应禁用此选项（设置为0），"
"因为腔室温度应较低，以避免材料在喉管处软化导致挤出机堵塞。\n"
"\n"
"如果启用，此参数还会设置一个名为chamber_temperature的G代码变量，"
"可用于将所需腔室温度传递给打印开始宏或热浸泡宏，例如："
"PRINT_START (other variables) CHAMBER_TEMP=[chamber_temperature]。"
"如果您的打印机不支持M141/M191命令，或者您希望在未安装主动腔室加热器的情况下"
"在打印开始宏中处理热浸泡，这可能很有用。"

msgid "Nozzle temperature for layers after the initial one."
msgstr "初始层之后的喷嘴温度"

msgid "Detect thin wall"
msgstr "检测薄壁"

msgid ""
"Detect thin wall which can't contain two line width. And use single line to "
"print. Maybe printed not very well, because it's not closed loop."
msgstr ""
"检测无法容纳两条线宽的薄壁，并使用单线打印。由于不是闭合回路，打印效果可能不佳。"

msgid ""
"This G-code is inserted when filament is changed, including T commands to "
"trigger tool change."
msgstr ""
"此G代码在更换耗材时插入，包括触发工具更换的T命令。"

msgid "This G-code is inserted when the extrusion role is changed."
msgstr "此G代码在挤出角色改变时插入。"

msgid ""
"Line width for top surfaces. If expressed as a %, it will be computed over "
"the nozzle diameter."
msgstr ""
"顶部表面的线宽。如果以%表示，将根据喷嘴直径计算。"

msgid "Speed of top surface infill which is solid."
msgstr "实心顶部表面填充的速度。"

msgid "Top shell layers"
msgstr "顶部壳层数"

msgid ""
"This is the number of solid layers of top shell, including the top surface "
"layer. When the thickness calculated by this value is thinner than top shell "
"thickness, the top shell layers will be increased."
msgstr ""
"这是顶部壳的实心层数，包括顶部表面层。当由此值计算的厚度薄于顶部壳厚度时，"
"顶部壳层数将增加。"

msgid "Top solid layers"
msgstr "顶部实心层"

msgid "Top shell thickness"
msgstr "顶部壳厚度"

msgid ""
"The number of top solid layers is increased when slicing if the thickness "
"calculated by top shell layers is thinner than this value. This can avoid "
"having too thin shell when layer height is small. 0 means that this setting "
"is disabled and thickness of top shell is absolutely determined by top shell "
"layers."
msgstr ""
"如果由顶部壳层数计算的厚度薄于此值，则在切片时增加顶部实心层数。"
"这可以避免在层高较小时壳过薄。0表示禁用此设置，顶部壳的厚度完全由顶部壳层数决定。"

msgid "Top surface density"
msgstr "顶部表面密度"

msgid ""
"Density of top surface layer. A value of 100% creates a fully solid, smooth "
"top layer. Reducing this value results in a textured top surface, according "
"to the chosen top surface pattern. A value of 0% will result in only the "
"walls on the top layer being created. Intended for aesthetic or functional "
"purposes, not to fix issues such as over-extrusion."
msgstr ""
"顶部表面层的密度。100%的值创建完全实心光滑的顶层。降低此值会根据所选顶部表面图案"
"产生纹理化的顶部表面。0%的值将导致仅创建顶层的壁。"
"用于美观或功能目的，而非修复过度挤出等问题。"

msgid "Bottom surface density"
msgstr "底部表面密度"

msgid ""
"Density of the bottom surface layer. Intended for aesthetic or functional "
"purposes, not to fix issues such as over-extrusion.\n"
"WARNING: Lowering this value may negatively affect bed adhesion."
msgstr ""
"底部表面层的密度。用于美观或功能目的，而非修复过度挤出等问题。\n"
"警告：降低此值可能会对热床附着力产生负面影响。"

msgid "Speed of travel which is faster and without extrusion."
msgstr "移动速度，更快且不进行挤出的移动速度。"

msgid "Wipe while retracting"
msgstr "回抽时擦拭"

msgid ""
"Move nozzle along the last extrusion path when retracting to clean any "
"leaked material on the nozzle. This can minimize blobs when printing a new "
"part after traveling."
msgstr ""
"回抽时沿着最后的挤出路径移动喷嘴，清理喷嘴上泄漏的材料。这可以减"
"少移动后打印新部件时产生的凸点。"

msgid "Wipe Distance"
msgstr "擦拭距离"

msgid ""
"Describe how long the nozzle will move along the last path when retracting.\n"
"\n"
"Depending on how long the wipe operation lasts, how fast and long the "
"extruder/filament retraction settings are, a retraction move may be needed "
"to retract the remaining filament.\n"
"\n"
"Setting a value in the retract amount before wipe setting below will perform "
"any excess retraction before the wipe, else it will be performed after."
msgstr ""
"描述回抽时喷嘴沿最后路径移动的距离。\n"
"\n"
"根据擦拭操作的持续时间、挤出机/耗材回抽设置的速度和长度，可能需要进行额"
"外的回抽动作来收回剩余的耗材。\n"
"\n"
"在下方"擦拭前回抽量"设置中设置一个值，将在擦拭前执行多余的回抽，否则将在擦"
"拭后执行。"

msgid ""
"The wiping tower can be used to clean up the residue on the nozzle and "
"stabilize the chamber pressure inside the nozzle, in order to avoid "
"appearance defects when printing objects."
msgstr ""
"擦拭塔可用于清理喷嘴上的残留物并稳定喷嘴内部腔室压力，以避免打印"
"物体时出现外观缺陷。"

msgid "Purging volumes"
msgstr "清洗体积"

msgid "Flush multiplier"
msgstr "清洗倍率"

msgid ""
"The actual flushing volumes is equal to the flush multiplier multiplied by "
"the flushing volumes in the table."
msgstr ""
"实际清洗体积等于清洗倍率乘以表格中的清洗体积。"

msgid "Prime volume"
msgstr "预填充体积"

msgid "The volume of material to prime extruder on tower."
msgstr "在塔上预填充挤出机的材料体积。"

msgid "Width of the prime tower."
msgstr "预填充塔的宽度。"

msgid "Wipe tower rotation angle"
msgstr "擦拭塔旋转角度"

msgid "Wipe tower rotation angle with respect to X axis."
msgstr "擦拭塔相对于X轴的旋转角度。"

msgid "Width of the brim."
msgstr "底边宽度。"

msgid "Stabilization cone apex angle"
msgstr "稳定锥顶角"

msgid ""
"Angle at the apex of the cone that is used to stabilize the wipe tower. "
"Larger angle means wider base."
msgstr ""
"用于稳定擦拭塔的锥体顶角角度。角度越大，底部越宽。"

msgid "Maximum wipe tower print speed"
msgstr "擦拭塔最大打印速度"

msgid ""
"The maximum print speed when purging in the wipe tower and printing the wipe "
"tower sparse layers. When purging, if the sparse infill speed or calculated "
"speed from the filament max volumetric speed is lower, the lowest will be "
"used instead.\n"
"\n"
"When printing the sparse layers, if the internal perimeter speed or "
"calculated speed from the filament max volumetric speed is lower, the lowest "
"will be used instead.\n"
"\n"
"Increasing this speed may affect the tower's stability as well as increase "
"the force with which the nozzle collides with any blobs that may have formed "
"on the wipe tower.\n"
"\n"
"Before increasing this parameter beyond the default of 90 mm/s, make sure "
"your printer can reliably bridge at the increased speeds and that ooze when "
"tool changing is well controlled.\n"
"\n"
"For the wipe tower external perimeters the internal perimeter speed is used "
"regardless of this setting."
msgstr ""
"在擦拭塔中清洗和打印擦拭塔稀疏层时的最大打印速度。清洗时，如果稀疏"
"填充速度或根据耗材最大体积速度计算的速度较低，则使用最低值。\n"
"\n"
"打印稀疏层时，如果内部外壳速度或根据耗材最大体积速度计算的速度较"
"低，则使用最低值。\n"
"\n"
"提高此速度可能会影响塔的稳定性，并增加喷嘴与可能在擦拭塔上形成的"
"任何凸点碰撞的力。\n"
"\n"
"在将此参数提高到默认值90mm/s以上之前，请确保您的打印机能够在提高的"
"速度下可靠地搭桥，并且换刀时的渗漏得到良好控制。\n"
"\n"
"对于擦拭塔的外部轮廓，无论此设置如何，都使用内部外壳速度。"

msgid "Wall type"
msgstr "壁类型"

msgid ""
"Wipe tower outer wall type.\n"
"1. Rectangle: The default wall type, a rectangle with fixed width and "
"height.\n"
"2. Cone: A cone with a fillet at the bottom to help stabilize the wipe "
"tower.\n"
"3. Rib: Adds four ribs to the tower wall for enhanced stability."
msgstr ""
"擦拭塔外壁类型。\n"
"1. 矩形：默认壁类型，固定宽度和高度的矩形。\n"
"2. 锥形：底部带圆角的锥体，有助于稳定擦拭塔。\n"
"3. 肋条：在塔壁添加四个肋条以增强稳定性。"

msgid "Extra rib length"
msgstr "额外肋条长度"

msgid ""
"Positive values can increase the size of the rib wall, while negative values "
"can reduce the size. However, the size of the rib wall can not be smaller "
"than that determined by the cleaning volume."
msgstr ""
"正值可增大肋壁尺寸，负值可减小尺寸。但是，肋壁的尺寸不能小于由清洗"
"体积确定的尺寸。"

msgid "Rib width"
msgstr "肋条宽度"

msgid "Rib width."
msgstr "肋条宽度。"

msgid "Fillet wall"
msgstr "圆角壁"

msgid "The wall of prime tower will fillet."
msgstr "预填充塔的壁将进行倒圆角。"

msgid ""
"The extruder to use when printing perimeter of the wipe tower. Set to 0 to "
"use the one that is available (non-soluble would be preferred)."
msgstr ""
"打印擦拭塔轮廓时使用的挤出机。设置为0以使用可用的挤出机"
"（优先使用非可溶性耗材）。"

msgid "Purging volumes - load/unload volumes"
msgstr "清洗体积 - 加载/卸载体积"

msgid ""
"This vector saves required volumes to change from/to each tool used on the "
"wipe tower. These values are used to simplify creation of the full purging "
"volumes below."
msgstr ""
"此数组保存擦拭塔上使用的每个工具之间切换所需的体积。这些值用于简"
"化下方完整清洗体积的创建。"

msgid ""
"Purging after filament change will be done inside objects' infills. This may "
"lower the amount of waste and decrease the print time. If the walls are "
"printed with transparent filament, the mixed color infill will be seen "
"outside. It will not take effect, unless the prime tower is enabled."
msgstr ""
"换料后的清洗将在物体填充内部进行。这可以减少浪费并缩短打印时间。"
"如果壁使用透明耗材打印，混合颜色的填充将在外部可见。除非启用预填"
"充塔，否则此设置不会生效。"

msgid ""
"Purging after filament change will be done inside objects' support. This may "
"lower the amount of waste and decrease the print time. It will not take "
"effect, unless the prime tower is enabled."
msgstr ""
"换料后的清洗将在物体支撑内部进行。这可以减少浪费并缩短打印时间。"
"除非启用预填充塔，否则此设置不会生效。"

msgid ""
"This object will be used to purge the nozzle after a filament change to save "
"filament and decrease the print time. Colors of the objects will be mixed as "
"a result. It will not take effect unless the prime tower is enabled."
msgstr ""
"该物体将用于在换料后清洗喷嘴，以节省耗材并缩短打印时间。物体的颜"
"色将因此混合。除非启用预填充塔，否则此设置不会生效。"

msgid "Maximal bridging distance"
msgstr "最大搭桥距离"

msgid "Maximal distance between supports on sparse infill sections."
msgstr "稀疏填充段上支撑之间的最大距离。"

msgid "Wipe tower purge lines spacing"
msgstr "擦拭塔清洗线间距"

msgid "Spacing of purge lines on the wipe tower."
msgstr "擦拭塔上清洗线的间距。"

msgid "Extra flow for purging"
msgstr "额外清洗流量"

msgid ""
"Extra flow used for the purging lines on the wipe tower. This makes the "
"purging lines thicker or narrower than they normally would be. The spacing "
"is adjusted automatically."
msgstr ""
"用于擦拭塔上清洗线的额外流量。这使得清洗线比正常情况下更粗或更"
"细。间距会自动调整。"

msgid "Idle temperature"
msgstr "待机温度"

msgid ""
"Nozzle temperature when the tool is currently not used in multi-tool setups. "
"This is only used when 'Ooze prevention' is active in Print Settings. Set to "
"0 to disable."
msgstr ""
"在多工具设置中当前工具未使用时的喷嘴温度。仅在打印设置中启用"
""防渗漏"时使用。设置为0以禁用。"

msgid "X-Y hole compensation"
msgstr "XY孔补偿"

msgid ""
"Holes in objects will expand or contract in the XY plane by the configured "
"value. Positive values make holes bigger, negative values make holes "
"smaller. This function is used to adjust sizes slightly when the objects "
"have assembling issues."
msgstr ""
"物体中的孔将在XY平面上按设置的值扩大或收缩。正值使孔变大，负值使"
"孔变小。此功能用于在物体存在装配问题时微调尺寸。"

msgid "X-Y contour compensation"
msgstr "XY轮廓补偿"

msgid ""
"Contours of objects will expand or contract in the XY plane by the "
"configured value. Positive values make contours bigger, negative values make "
"contours smaller. This function is used to adjust sizes slightly when the "
"objects have assembling issues."
msgstr ""
"对象轮廓将在XY平面上按设定值扩大或缩小。正值使轮廓变大，负值使轮廓变小。"
"此功能用于在对象存在装配问题时微调尺寸。"

msgid "Convert holes to polyholes"
msgstr "将孔转换为多边形孔"

msgid ""
"Search for almost-circular holes that span more than one layer and convert "
"the geometry to polyholes. Use the nozzle size and the (biggest) diameter to "
"compute the polyhole.\n"
"See http://hydraraptor.blogspot.com/2011/02/polyholes.html"
msgstr ""
"搜索跨越多个层的近似圆形孔，并将其几何形状转换为多边形孔。"
"使用喷嘴尺寸和（最大）直径来计算多边形孔。\n"
"参见 http://hydraraptor.blogspot.com/2011/02/polyholes.html"

msgid "Polyhole detection margin"
msgstr "多边形孔检测容差"

#, no-c-format, no-boost-format

msgid ""
"Maximum defection of a point to the estimated radius of the circle.\n"
"As cylinders are often exported as triangles of varying size, points may not "
"be on the circle circumference. This setting allows you some leeway to "
"broaden the detection.\n"
"In mm or in % of the radius."
msgstr ""
"点到预估圆半径的最大偏差。\n"
"由于圆柱体通常以不同大小的三角形导出，点可能不在圆周上。"
"此设置允许一定的余量来扩大检测范围。\n"
"以毫米或半径百分比表示。"

msgid "Polyhole twist"
msgstr "多边形孔扭转"

msgid "Rotate the polyhole every layer."
msgstr "每层旋转多边形孔。"

msgid "G-code thumbnails"
msgstr "G代码缩略图"

msgid ""
"Picture sizes to be stored into a .gcode and .sl1 / .sl1s files, in the "
"following format: \"XxY, XxY, ...\""
msgstr ""
"存储到.gcode和.sl1/.sl1s文件中的图片尺寸，格式如下：\"XxY, XxY, ...\""

msgid "Format of G-code thumbnails"
msgstr "G代码缩略图格式"

msgid ""
"Format of G-code thumbnails: PNG for best quality, JPG for smallest size, "
"QOI for low memory firmware."
msgstr ""
"G代码缩略图格式：PNG最佳质量，JPG最小体积，QOI适用于低内存固件。"

msgid "Use relative E distances"
msgstr "使用相对E轴距离"

msgid ""
"Relative extrusion is recommended when using \"label_objects\" option. Some "
"extruders work better with this option unchecked (absolute extrusion mode). "
"Wipe tower is only compatible with relative mode. It is recommended on most "
"printers. Default is checked."
msgstr ""
"使用\"label_objects\"选项时建议使用相对挤出。某些挤出机在取消此选项（绝对挤出模式）"
"时工作效果更好。擦拭塔仅兼容相对模式。在大多数打印机上推荐开启。默认启用。"

msgid ""
"Classic wall generator produces walls with constant extrusion width and for "
"very thin areas is used gap-fill. Arachne engine produces walls with "
"variable extrusion width."
msgstr ""
"经典壁生成器生成恒定挤出宽度的壁，对于非常薄的区域使用间隙填充。"
"Arachne引擎生成可变挤出宽度的壁。"

msgid "Arachne"
msgstr "Arachne"

msgid "Wall transition length"
msgstr "壁过渡长度"

msgid ""
"When transitioning between different numbers of walls as the part becomes "
"thinner, a certain amount of space is allotted to split or join the wall "
"segments. It's expressed as a percentage over nozzle diameter."
msgstr ""
"当零件变薄时，在不同数量的壁之间过渡，会分配一定空间来分割或合并壁段。"
"以喷嘴直径的百分比表示。"

msgid "Wall transitioning filter margin"
msgstr "壁过渡过滤容差"

msgid ""
"Prevent transitioning back and forth between one extra wall and one less. "
"This margin extends the range of extrusion widths which follow to [Minimum "
"wall width - margin, 2 * Minimum wall width + margin]. Increasing this "
"margin reduces the number of transitions, which reduces the number of "
"extrusion starts/stops and travel time. However, large extrusion width "
"variation can lead to under- or overextrusion problems. It's expressed as a "
"percentage over nozzle diameter."
msgstr ""
"防止在增加一面壁和减少一面壁之间反复切换。此容差将挤出宽度范围扩展为"
"[最小壁宽 - 容差, 2 * 最小壁宽 + 容差]。增加此容差可减少过渡次数，"
"从而减少挤出启动/停止次数和移动时间。然而，大幅的挤出宽度变化可能导致"
"挤出不足或过度挤出问题。以喷嘴直径的百分比表示。"

msgid "Wall transitioning threshold angle"
msgstr "壁过渡阈值角度"

msgid ""
"When to create transitions between even and odd numbers of walls. A wedge "
"shape with an angle greater than this setting will not have transitions and "
"no walls will be printed in the center to fill the remaining space. Reducing "
"this setting reduces the number and length of these center walls, but may "
"leave gaps or overextrude."
msgstr ""
"控制何时在奇偶数量的壁之间创建过渡。角度大于此设置的楔形将不会产生过渡，"
"也不会在中心打印壁来填充剩余空间。减小此设置可减少中心壁的数量和长度，"
"但可能导致间隙或过度挤出。"

msgid "Wall distribution count"
msgstr "壁分布计数"

msgid ""
"The number of walls, counted from the center, over which the variation needs "
"to be spread. Lower values mean that the outer walls don't change in width."
msgstr ""
"从中心开始计数的壁数量，变化需要分布在这些壁上。"
"数值越低表示外壁宽度不变。"

msgid "Minimum feature size"
msgstr "最小特征尺寸"

msgid ""
"Minimum thickness of thin features. Model features that are thinner than "
"this value will not be printed, while features thicker than than this value "
"will be widened to the minimum wall width. It's expressed as a percentage "
"over nozzle diameter."
msgstr ""
"薄特征的最小厚度。薄于此值的模型特征将不会被打印，"
"而厚于此值的特征将被加宽到最小壁宽。以喷嘴直径的百分比表示。"

msgid "Minimum wall length"
msgstr "最小壁长"

msgid ""
"Adjust this value to prevent short, unclosed walls from being printed, which "
"could increase print time. Higher values remove more and longer walls.\n"
"\n"
"NOTE: Bottom and top surfaces will not be affected by this value to prevent "
"visual gaps on the outside of the model. Adjust 'One wall threshold' in the "
"Advanced settings below to adjust the sensitivity of what is considered a "
"top-surface. 'One wall threshold' is only visible if this setting is set "
"above the default value of 0.5, or if single-wall top surfaces is enabled."
msgstr ""
"调整此值可防止打印短小未闭合的壁，这些壁可能会增加打印时间。"
"数值越高，移除的壁越多越长。\n"
"\n"
"注意：底部和顶部表面不受此值影响，以防止模型外部出现视觉间隙。"
"请调整下方高级设置中的\"单壁阈值\"来调整被视为顶面的灵敏度。"
"\"单壁阈值\"仅当此设置值高于默认值0.5或启用了单壁顶面时可见。"

msgid "First layer minimum wall width"
msgstr "第一层最小壁宽"

msgid ""
"The minimum wall width that should be used for the first layer is "
"recommended to be set to the same size as the nozzle. This adjustment is "
"expected to enhance adhesion."
msgstr ""
"第一层应使用的最小壁宽，建议设置为与喷嘴相同的大小。"
"此调整预期可以增强附着力。"

msgid "Minimum wall width"
msgstr "最小壁宽"

msgid ""
"Width of the wall that will replace thin features (according to the Minimum "
"feature size) of the model. If the Minimum wall width is thinner than the "
"thickness of the feature, the wall will become as thick as the feature "
"itself. It's expressed as a percentage over nozzle diameter."
msgstr ""
"将替换模型薄特征（根据最小特征尺寸）的壁宽。"
"如果最小壁宽薄于特征厚度，则壁将变得与特征本身一样厚。"
"以喷嘴直径的百分比表示。"

msgid "Detect narrow internal solid infill"
msgstr "检测狭窄内部实体填充"

msgid ""
"This option will auto-detect narrow internal solid infill areas. If enabled, "
"the concentric pattern will be used for the area to speed up printing. "
"Otherwise, the rectilinear pattern will be used by default."
msgstr ""
"此选项将自动检测狭窄的内部实体填充区域。如果启用，"
"将对该区域使用同心图案以加快打印速度。否则，默认使用直线图案。"

