msgstr ""
"打印中使用的第一个挤出机的从零开始的索引。与initial_tool相同。"

msgid "Initial tool"
msgstr "初始工具"

msgid ""
"Zero-based index of the first extruder used in the print. Same as "
"initial_extruder."
msgstr ""
"打印中使用的第一个挤出机的从零开始的索引。与initial_extruder相同。"

msgid "Is extruder used?"
msgstr "挤出机是否被使用？"

msgid ""
"Vector of booleans stating whether a given extruder is used in the print."
msgstr "指示打印中是否使用了指定挤出机的布尔值向量。"

msgid "Has single extruder MM priming"
msgstr "有单挤出机多材料预填充"

