#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:Precise wall]

msgid ""
"Precise wall\n"
"Did you know that turning on precise wall can improve precision and layer "
"consistency?"
msgstr ""
"精确外壳\n"
"您是否知道开启精确外壳可以提高精度和层一致性？"

#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:Sandwich mode]

msgid ""
"Sandwich mode\n"
"Did you know that you can use sandwich mode (inner-outer-inner) to improve "
"precision and layer consistency if your model doesn't have very steep "
"overhangs?"
msgstr ""
"三明治模式\n"
"您是否知道，如果您的模型没有非常陡峭的悬垂，您可以使用三明治模式（内-外-内）来提高精度和层一致性？"

#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:Chamber temperature]

msgid ""
"Chamber temperature\n"
"Did you know that Snapmaker Orca supports chamber temperature?"
msgstr ""
"腔室温度\n"
"您是否知道 Snapmaker Orca 支持腔室温度控制？"

#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:Calibration]

msgid ""
"Calibration\n"
"Did you know that calibrating your printer can do wonders? Check out our "
"beloved calibration solution in Snapmaker Orca."
msgstr ""
"校准\n"
"您是否知道校准打印机可以带来意想不到的效果？请查看 Snapmaker Orca 中备受青睐的校准方案。"

#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:Auxiliary fan]

msgid ""
"Auxiliary fan\n"
"Did you know that Snapmaker Orca supports Auxiliary part cooling fan?"
msgstr ""
"辅助风扇\n"
"您是否知道 Snapmaker Orca 支持辅助模型冷却风扇？"

#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:Air filtration]

msgid ""
"Air filtration/Exhaust Fan\n"
"Did you know that Snapmaker Orca can support Air filtration/Exhaust Fan?"
msgstr ""
"空气过滤/排气风扇\n"
"您是否知道 Snapmaker Orca 支持空气过滤/排气风扇？"

#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:G-code window]

msgid ""
"G-code window\n"
"You can turn on/off the G-code window by pressing the <b>C</b> key."
msgstr ""
"G代码窗口\n"
"您可以通过按 <b>C</b> 键来打开或关闭 G代码窗口。"

#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:Switch workspaces]

msgid ""
"Switch workspaces\n"
"You can switch between <b>Prepare</b> and <b>Preview</b> workspaces by "
"pressing the <b>Tab</b> key."
msgstr ""
"切换工作区\n"
"您可以通过按 <b>Tab</b> 键在<b>准备</b>和<b>预览</b>工作区之间切换。"

#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:How to use keyboard shortcuts]

msgid ""
"How to use keyboard shortcuts\n"
"Did you know that Snapmaker Orca offers a wide range of keyboard shortcuts and "
"3D scene operations?"
msgstr ""
"如何使用快捷键\n"
"您是否知道 Snapmaker Orca 提供丰富的快捷键和3D场景操作？"

#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:Reverse on odd]

msgid ""
"Reverse on odd\n"
"Did you know that <b>Reverse on odd</b> feature can significantly improve "
"the surface quality of your overhangs?"
msgstr ""
"奇数层反向\n"
"您是否知道<b>奇数层反向</b>功能可以显著改善悬垂的表面质量？"

#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:Cut Tool]

msgid ""
"Cut Tool\n"
"Did you know that you can cut a model at any angle and position with the "
"cutting tool?"
msgstr ""
"切割工具\n"
"您是否知道您可以使用切割工具以任意角度和位置切割模型？"

#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:Fix Model]

msgid ""
"Fix Model\n"
"Did you know that you can fix a corrupted 3D model to avoid a lot of slicing "
"problems on the Windows system?"
msgstr ""
"修复模型\n"
"您是否知道在 Windows 系统上修复损坏的3D模型可以避免许多切片问题？"

#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:Timelapse]

msgid ""
"Timelapse\n"
"Did you know that you can generate a timelapse video during each print?"
msgstr ""
"延时摄影\n"
"您是否知道您可以在每次打印过程中生成延时摄影视频？"

#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:Auto-Arrange]

msgid ""
"Auto-Arrange\n"
"Did you know that you can auto-arrange all the objects in your project?"
msgstr ""
"自动排列\n"
"您是否知道您可以自动排列项目中的所有对象？"

#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:Auto-Orient]

msgid ""
"Auto-Orient\n"
"Did you know that you can rotate objects to an optimal orientation for "
"printing with a simple click?"
msgstr ""
"自动定向\n"
"您是否知道您只需点击一下即可将对象旋转到最佳打印方向？"

#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:Lay on Face]

msgid ""
"Lay on Face\n"
"Did you know that you can quickly orient a model so that one of its faces "
"sits on the print bed? Select the \"Place on face\" function or press the "
"<b>F</b> key."
msgstr ""
"贴面放置\n"
"您是否知道您可以快速将模型定向使其某个面位于打印平台上？选择\"贴面放置\"功能或按 <b>F</b> 键。"

#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:Object List]

msgid ""
"Object List\n"
"Did you know that you can view all objects/parts in a list and change "
"settings for each object/part?"
msgstr ""
"对象列表\n"
"您是否知道您可以在列表中查看所有对象/部件并为每个对象/部件更改设置？"

#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:Search Functionality]

msgid ""
"Search Functionality\n"
"Did you know that you use the Search tool to quickly find a specific Orca "
"Slicer setting?"
msgstr ""
"搜索功能\n"
"您是否知道您可以使用搜索工具快速找到特定的 Orca Slicer 设置？"

#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:Simplify Model]

msgid ""
"Simplify Model\n"
"Did you know that you can reduce the number of triangles in a mesh using the "
"Simplify mesh feature? Right-click the model and select Simplify model."
msgstr ""
"简化模型\n"
"您是否知道您可以使用简化网格功能减少网格中的三角形数量？右键单击模型并选择简化模型。"

#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:Slicing Parameter Table]

msgid ""
"Slicing Parameter Table\n"
"Did you know that you can view all objects/parts on a table and change "
"settings for each object/part?"
msgstr ""
"切片参数表\n"
"您是否知道您可以在表格中查看所有对象/部件并为每个对象/部件更改设置？"

#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:Split to Objects/Parts]

msgid ""
"Split to Objects/Parts\n"
"Did you know that you can split a big object into small ones for easy "
"colorizing or printing?"
msgstr ""
"分割为对象/部件\n"
"您是否知道您可以将大对象分割成小对象以便于轻松着色或打印？"

#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:Subtract a Part]

msgid ""
"Subtract a Part\n"
"Did you know that you can subtract one mesh from another using the Negative "
"part modifier? That way you can, for example, create easily resizable holes "
"directly in Snapmaker Orca."
msgstr ""
"减去部件\n"
"您是否知道您可以使用负部件修改器从一个网格中减去另一个网格？这样您就可以直接在 Snapmaker Orca 中创建易于调整大小的孔洞。"

#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:STEP]

msgid ""
"STEP\n"
"Did you know that you can improve your print quality by slicing a STEP file "
"instead of an STL?\n"
"Snapmaker Orca supports slicing STEP files, providing smoother results than a "
"lower resolution STL. Give it a try!"
msgstr ""
"STEP\n"
"您是否知道通过切片 STEP 文件而不是 STL 文件可以提高打印质量？\n"
"Snapmaker Orca 支持切片 STEP 文件，提供比低分辨率 STL 更平滑的结果。试试吧！"

#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:Z seam location]

msgid ""
"Z seam location\n"
"Did you know that you can customize the location of the Z seam, and even "
"paint it on your print, to have it in a less visible location? This improves "
"the overall look of your model. Check it out!"
msgstr ""
"Z 接缝位置\n"
"您是否知道您可以自定义 Z 接缝的位置，甚至可以将其涂抹在打印件上，使其位于不太显眼的位置？这可以改善模型的整体外观。试试吧！"

#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:Fine-tuning for flow rate]

msgid ""
"Fine-tuning for flow rate\n"
"Did you know that flow rate can be fine-tuned for even better-looking "
"prints? Depending on the material, you can improve the overall finish of the "
"printed model by doing some fine-tuning."
msgstr ""
"微调流量\n"
"您是否知道可以微调流量以获得更美观的打印效果？根据材料的不同，通过一些微调可以改善打印模型的整体表面质量。"

#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:Split your prints into plates]

msgid ""
"Split your prints into plates\n"
"Did you know that you can split a model that has a lot of parts into "
"individual plates ready to print? This will simplify the process of keeping "
"track of all the parts."
msgstr ""
"将打印件拆分到打印板\n"
"您是否知道您可以将具有多个部件的模型拆分到各个打印板上准备打印？这将简化跟踪所有部件的过程。"

#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:Speed up your print with Adaptive Layer
#: Height]

msgid ""
"Speed up your print with Adaptive Layer Height\n"
"Did you know that you can print a model even faster, by using the Adaptive "
"Layer Height option? Check it out!"
msgstr ""
"使用自适应层高加速打印\n"
"您是否知道您可以通过使用自适应层高选项来更快地打印模型？试试吧！"

#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:Support painting]

msgid ""
"Support painting\n"
"Did you know that you can paint the location of your supports? This feature "
"makes it easy to place the support material only on the sections of the "
"model that actually need it."
msgstr ""
"支撑涂抹\n"
"您是否知道您可以涂抹支撑的位置？此功能使您可以轻松地将支撑材料仅放置在模型实际需要的位置。"

#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:Different types of supports]

msgid ""
"Different types of supports\n"
"Did you know that you can choose from multiple types of supports? Tree "
"supports work great for organic models, while saving filament and improving "
"print speed. Check them out!"
msgstr ""
"不同类型的支撑\n"
"您是否知道您可以从多种类型的支撑中进行选择？树状支撑非常适合有机模型，同时节省耗材并提高打印速度。试试吧！"

#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:Printing Silk Filament]

msgid ""
"Printing Silk Filament\n"
"Did you know that Silk filament needs special consideration to print it "
"successfully? Higher temperature and lower speed are always recommended for "
"the best results."
msgstr ""
"打印丝绸耗材\n"
"您是否知道丝绸耗材需要特殊考虑才能成功打印？建议使用更高的温度和更低的速度以获得最佳效果。"

#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:Brim for better adhesion]

msgid ""
"Brim for better adhesion\n"
"Did you know that when printed models have a small contact interface with "
"the printing surface, it's recommended to use a brim?"
msgstr ""
"使用底边获得更好的附着\n"
"您是否知道当打印模型与打印表面的接触面较小时，建议使用底边？"

#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:Set parameters for multiple objects]

msgid ""
"Set parameters for multiple objects\n"
"Did you know that you can set slicing parameters for all selected objects at "
"once?"
msgstr ""
"为多个对象设置参数\n"
"您是否知道您可以同时为所有选中的对象设置切片参数？"

#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:Stack objects]

msgid ""
"Stack objects\n"
"Did you know that you can stack objects as a whole one?"
msgstr ""
"堆叠对象\n"
"您是否知道您可以将对象堆叠为一个整体？"

#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:Flush into support/objects/infill]

msgid ""
"Flush into support/objects/infill\n"
"Did you know that you can save wasted filament by flushing it into support/"
"objects/infill during filament change?"
msgstr ""
"冲洗到支撑/对象/填充中\n"
"您是否知道您可以在更换耗材时将废弃的耗材冲洗到支撑/对象/填充中以减少浪费？"

#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:Improve strength]

msgid ""
"Improve strength\n"
"Did you know that you can use more wall loops and higher sparse infill "
"density to improve the strength of the model?"
msgstr ""
"提高强度\n"
"您是否知道您可以使用更多的外壳环数和更高的稀疏填充密度来提高模型的强度？"

#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:When do you need to print with the printer
#: door opened]

msgid ""
"When do you need to print with the printer door opened?\n"
"Did you know that opening the printer door can reduce the probability of "
"extruder/hotend clogging when printing lower temperature filament with a "
"higher enclosure temperature? More info about this in the Wiki."
msgstr ""
"何时需要打开打印机门打印？\n"
"您是否知道在打印较低温度的耗材且箱体温度较高时，打开打印机门可以降低挤出机/热端堵塞的概率？更多信息请查看 Wiki。"

#: resources/data/hints.ini: [hint:Avoid warping]

msgid ""
"Avoid warping\n"
"Did you know that when printing materials that are prone to warping such as "
"ABS, appropriately increasing the heatbed temperature can reduce the "
"probability of warping?"
msgstr ""
"避免翘曲\n"
"您是否知道当打印易翘曲的材料（如 ABS）时，适当提高热床温度可以减少翘曲的概率？"

